\id DEU
\h Aɛawed n Ccariɛa
\toc1 Aɛawed n Ccariɛa
\toc2 Aɛawed n Ccariɛa
\toc3 Aɛwd.
\mt1 Aɛawed n Ccariɛa
\c 1
\s1 Awař n Musa
\m 
\v 1 Ina d awařen nni issiweř Musa i marra Israil x ujemmaḍ n L’Urdun, di řexřa, di Řewḍa arendad n Ṣuf, jar Faran d Tufal d Laban d Ḥaḍayrut d Di-Dahab.
\v 2 Zi Ḥurib x webrid n idurar n Saɛir ař Qadac-Barniɛ aqa-tt d ict n ticti n ḥiṭac n wussan.
\v 3 Imsar deg useggʷas wiss arebɛin, deg uyur wiss ḥiṭac, deg \add wass\add* amezwaru n uyur, issiweř Musa ak-d ayt n Israil ɛlaḥsab marra min d as iweṣṣa SIDI zi jjihet nsen,
\v 4 awarni umi iɣřeb di Idraɛi x Siḥun, ajeǧid n Imuriyyen wenni tuɣa izeddɣen di Ḥacbun, u x Ɛuj, ajeǧid n Bacan, wenni tuɣa izeddɣen di Ɛactarut. \x ◘ \xo 1:4 \xt Řxř. 21:24,33\x*
\v 5 X ujemmaḍ n L’Urdun, di temmurt n Mu’ab, ibda Musa ad ifessar Ccariɛa-ya, inna:
\b
\m 
\v 6 “SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ, issiweř akidneɣ ɣar Ḥurib, inna: ‘Kenniw teqqimen aṭṭas ɣar wedrar-a, aqa d aṭṭas.
\v 7 Dewřem, kksem iqiḍan nwem uca adfem ɣar idurar n Imuriyyen u ɣar marra \add imucan\add* yudsen di Řewḍa, di Temmurt n Idurar, di Temmurt Iwaṭan, di \add Temmurt n\add* Ljanub u ɣar tma n řebḥar, tammurt n ayt n Kenɛan, d Lubnan ař iɣzar ameqqran, iɣzar n Lfuraṭ.
\v 8 Xzar, Necc wciɣ awem tammurt i iǧan zzat i wudem nwem. Adfem ɣares, tᵉṭṭfem tammurt nni x ijjuǧ SIDI ad tt iwc i řejdud nwem, i Ibrahim, Isḥaq d Yaɛqub, u i zzariɛet nsen awarni asen.’ \x ◘ \xo 1:8 \xt Amz. 15:18; 17:7, 8\x*
\v 9 Di řweqt nni ssiwřeɣ necc akidwem, nniɣ: ‘Necc waha war zemmareɣ ad arbuɣ \add amnus i kenniw\add*. \x ◘ \xo 1:9 \xt Uf. 18:18\x*
\v 10 SIDI, AREBBI nwem, igga kenniw d aṭṭas, uca xzar, kenniw řexxu d aṭṭas am yitran n ujenna.
\v 11 Ad taf ad daywem immarni SIDI, AREBBI n řejdud nwem, am mammec kenniw \add teǧam řexxu\add* ařef n twařawin uca ad taf ad kenniw ibarek am mammec tuɣa ɣarwem dd-issiweř.
\v 12 Mammec zemmareɣ necc weḥḥdi waha ad arbuɣ isḥessifen nwem d ddquřat nwem d imcubbecen nwem?
\v 13 Ksim zi jar teqbič nwem iryazen imiɣisen, ifehhmen, inni ittwassnen \add icnan\add*, ḥima ad ten ggeɣ d izeǧifen xawem.’
\v 14 \add Xenni\add* kenniw tarrim-dd xafi, tennam ayi: ‘Awař i tessiwřed, aqa iban-dd icna, ḥima ad \add t\add* negg.’
\v 15 Uca ksiɣ izeǧifen n teqbič nwem, iryazen imiɣisen, ifehhmen, inni ittwassnen icnan, uca ggiɣ ten d izeǧifen xawem, \add am\add* imeqqranen x wařef, imeqqranen x mya, imeqqranen x xemsin d imeqqranen x ɛecra, u \add am\add* imeḥḍayen x tqebbař nwem.
\v 16 Di řweqt nni umureɣ i řquḍat nwem uca nniɣ: ‘Sřem ɣar aytmatwem uca ḥekmem s yijj n řḥukm iseggden jar weryaz d umas d ubarrani \add nni\add* kides \add iǧan\add*. \f ◼ \fr 1:16 \fk řquḍat\ft - niɣ ‘imᵉzurfa.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 1:16 \xt Yḥ. 7:24\x*
\v 17 War tteggem s wudmawen di řeḥkam. Ad tesřem ɣar umeẓyan d umeqqran. War teggʷdem zeg wudem n ca n yijjen, minzi řeḥkam ɣar AREBBI. Tamesřact nni tewɛar xawem, awyem tt-i-dd ɣari uca necc ad tt sřeɣ.’ \x ◘ \xo 1:17 \xt Lawi 19:15; 1 Ṣm. 16:7; Awřn. 24:23; Yaɛ. 2:1\x*
\v 18 \add Ammu\add* i kenniw umureɣ di řweqt nni marra timesřayin nni xawem ad tent teggem.”
\b
\m 
\v 19 “\add Xenni\add* nefsi iqiḍan nneɣ \add uca neffeɣ\add* zi Ḥurib uca neẓwa marra řexřa ameqqran issaggʷaden nni teẓrim, \add nuyur\add* deg webrid n idurar n Imuriyyen am mammec d aneɣ yumur SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ, uca niweḍ ɣar Qadac-Barniɛ.
\v 20 \add Xenni\add* nniɣ awem: ‘Aqa tiwḍem ɣar idurar n Imuriyyen nni i d aneɣ ɣa iwc SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ.
\v 21 Xzar, SIDI, AREBBI nnec, aqa iwca \add as\add* tammurt i din iǧan zzat i wudem nnec. Geɛɛed, ṭṭef i-tt, am mammec ɣarek issiweř SIDI, AREBBI n řejdud nwem. War tteggʷed u war ttejji ad iɛgez wuř nnec.’
\v 22 Tusim-dd ɣari marra kenniw, tennam: ‘Ejj aneɣ ad nessekk iryazen zzat i wudem nneɣ ḥima ad bergagen tammurt maḥend ad aneɣ xebbaren x man abrid i zi ɣa ngeɛɛed di \add tammurt\add* u mammec \add ǧant\add* tneddam i ɣar dd ɣa nas.’
\v 23 Tuɣa awař-a d lemliḥ i necc uca ksiɣ tenɛac n yeryazen zi \add řwest\add* nwem, zi \add kuř\add* taqbič ijj n weryaz. \x ◘ \xo 1:23 \xt Řxř. 13:2-38.\x*
\v 24 Nnḍen nitni uca uyuren x webrid ɣar idurar uca usin-dd ɣar teɣzurt n Ickul uca bergagen temmurt. \x ◘ \xo 1:24 \xt Řxř. 13:23\x*
\v 25 Ksin s ifassen nsen řɣiǧet n temmurt uca hwan-dd ɣarneɣ. Iwyen aneɣ-dd řexbar, nnan: ‘Tammurt i d aneɣ ɣa iwc SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ, teṣbeḥ.’”
\m 
\v 26 “Qaɛ amenni, war texsem ad tgeɛɛdem uca tɣewwɣem ḍidd i řumur n SIDI, AREBBI nwem. \x ◘ \xo 1:26 \xt Řxř. 14:2\x*
\v 27 Uca tnedqem-dd deg iqiḍan nwem, tennam: ‘Deg weqřab nnes xaneɣ, aqa issuffeɣ aneɣ SIDI zi temmurt n Miṣra maḥend ad aneɣ yarr ɣar ifassen n Imuriyyen maḥend ad aneɣ yareddeǧ. \f ◼ \fr 1:27 \fk ɣar ifassen\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘ɣar ufus’.\f*
\v 28 Mani \add xenni\add* i ɣa ngeɛɛed? Aytmatneɣ ssfessyen uřawen nneɣ, nnan: Řgens imɣar uca zzugaren xaneɣ. Tineddam mɣarent uca ttwafaryent ař ajenna uca neẓra din uřa d ayt n Ɛanaq.’ \x ◘ \xo 1:28 \xt Řxř. 13:28\x*
\v 29 Necc nniɣ awem: ‘War tarjijem ca u war zzaysen tteggʷdem.
\v 30 SIDI, AREBBI nwem, wenni igguren zzatwem, ad immneɣ di ṭṭweɛ nwem, ammu nican am mammec igga zzat i tiṭṭawin nwem di ṭṭweɛ nwem di Miṣra
\v 31 uřa di rexřa, mani teẓrid mammec tuɣa cek yarebbu SIDI, AREBBI nnec, marra abrid nni tuyured, am yijj n weryaz yarebbun mmis, ařami dd-tiwḍem ɣar wemcan-a.’
\v 32 \add Maca\add* kenniw ɛad war tuminem ca s wawař-a di SIDI, AREBBI nwem,
\v 33 wenni tuɣa igguren zzat i wudem nwem deg webrid, ḥima ad awem yarzu mani ɣa tewtem iqiḍan nwem, \add u wenni tuɣa igguren\add*, s ǧiřet di tmessi, maḥend ad awem isscen abrid mani kenniw ittxeṣṣa ad tuyurem, u s uziř deg ijj n useynu. \x ◘ \xo 1:33 \xt Uf. 13:21\x*
\v 34 SIDI isřa \add řḥess n\add* wawařen nwem uca ijja aɣḍab nnes ad idduqqez, ijjuǧ, inna:
\v 35 ‘Uřa d ijj zeg yeryazen-a n jjiř-a aɛeffan war iẓarr tammurt icnan nni x jjuǧeɣ maḥend ad tt wceɣ i řejdud nwem, \x ◘ \xo 1:35 \xt Řxř. 14:22, 23; Izhd. 95:11\x*
\v 36 mɣir Kalib, mmis n Yafunni, netta ad tt iẓar uca i netta d iḥenjiren nnes ad wceɣ tammurt nni x igga iḍaren nnes, minzi netta tuɣa iḍeffar SIDI nican.’
\v 37 Isɛar xafi SIDI di ssibbet nwem, inna: ‘Uřa d cek war \add ɣares\add* ttidfed ca! \x ◘ \xo 1:37 \xt Řxř. 20:12; 27:14; Aɛwd. 3:26; 4:21; 34:4\x*
\v 38 Yacuwa, mmis n Nun, wenni ibedden zzat i wudem nnec, ad ɣares yadef. Sjehd i-t, minzi netta d wenni tt ɣa iwcen d řwart i Israil.
\v 39 Uca tarwa nwem i x tennam: Ad dewřen d teymart!, iḥenjiren nwem nni war ssinen \add ɛad\add* řxar niɣ řɣar, nitni ad ɣares adfen uca Necc ad asen tt-i-dd-wceɣ uca nitni ad tt warten.
\v 40 \add Maca\add* kenniw ad dd-tdewřem, ad tekksem iqiḍan nwem ssa \add uca ad tuyurem\add* ɣar řexřa ɣar Řebḥar n Telga.’
\v 41 Kenniw tarrim-dd, tennam ayi: ‘Aqa nexḍa ak-d SIDI. Ad ngeɛɛed uca ad nemmneɣ qaɛ am mammec d aneɣ yumur SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ.’ \add Xenni\add* tbeysem, kuř ijj s řesnaḥ nnes n garra u kenniw s zzɛamet nwem tbeddem ad tgeɛɛdem ɣar wedrar.
\v 42 \add Xenni\add* inna ayi SIDI: ‘Ini asen: War ttgeɛɛdem, war ttmenɣim, minzi Necc war ǧiɣ di řwesṭ nwem, ḥima war txeṣṣarem zzat i wudem n řɛedyan nwem.’
\v 43 \add Ammu\add* i kiwem ssiwřeɣ, \add maca\add* kenniw war ttesřim uca tɣewwɣem ḍidd i řumur n SIDI uca teggim s tuffet, tgeɛɛdem ɣar idurar.
\v 44 Uca ffɣen Imuriyyen nni tuɣa izeddɣen deg idurar uca uẓẓřen xawem, am tteggent tzizwa, uca řebzen kenniw di Ṣaɛir ař Ḥurma.
\v 45 Tdewřem-dd, tessɣuyem zzat i wudem n SIDI. SIDI war isři i tmijja nwem, war d awem iwci amezzuɣ,
\v 46 uca teqqimem di Qadac ict n řweqt d azirar, ussan aṭṭas i dinni teqqimem.”
\b
\b
\c 2
\m 
\v 1 “\add Xenni\add* nedweř-dd uca nefsi iqiḍan \add uca nuyur\add* ɣar řexřa, deg webrid ɣar Řebḥar n Telga, am mammec d ayi inna SIDI uca nenneḍ aṭṭas n wussan i idurar n Saɛir.
\v 2 \add Xenni\add* issiweř SIDI akidi, inna:
\v 3 ‘Aṭṭas i tennḍem i wedrar-a, aqa cfa. Arrem \add azeǧif\add* ɣar ccamal
\v 4 uca umur řgens, ini: Ad tekkem kenniw x weymir n aytmatwem, ayt n Ɛisu, inni izeddɣen di Saɛir. Nitni ad zzaywem ggʷeden, \add maca\add* ittxeṣṣa kenniw ad teḥḍam ixef nwem aṭṭas. \f ◼ \fr 2:4 \fk ad teḥḍam ixef nwem aṭṭas\ft - niɣ ‘ad tiřim tfaqem’.\f*
\v 5 War kisen ttemɛařam, minzi war d awem tticeɣ uřa d ijj n cbar zi temmurt nsen, minzi Necc wciɣ idurar n Saɛir d řwart i Ɛisu. \f ◼ \fr 2:5 \fk ijj n cbar\ft - niɣ ‘ij n uṣurf n uḍar’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 2:5 \xt Amz. 36:8\x*
\v 6 Ad xasen tesɣem řeɛweč s nnuqart ḥima \add ad tzemmarem\add* ad teccem u ad xasen tesɣem ɛawed aman s nnuqart ḥima ad teswem.
\v 7 Minzi SIDI, AREBBI nnec, tuɣa ibarek i cek di marra řxedmet n ifassen nnec. Netta issen ticři nnec di řexřa-ya ameqqran. \add Marra\add* arebɛin n iseggʷusa-ya tuɣa SIDI, AREBBI nnec, akidek uca war d ac ixeṣṣi walu.’”
\m 
\v 8 “\add Umi\add* nekka x yaytmatneɣ, ayt n Ɛisu nni tuɣa izeddɣen di Saɛir, x webrid n Řewḍa n Ilat d Ɛiṣyun-Jabir, nedweř-dd uca nekka x webrid n řexřa n Mu’ab.
\v 9 \add Xenni\add* issiweř akidi SIDI: ‘War ssaggʷad Mu’ab u war kisen ttmenɣam, minzi Necc war d awem tticeɣ walu d řwart zi temmurt nsen, minzi Necc wciɣ Ɛar d řwart i ayt n Luṭ.’
\m 
\v 10 \qt Tuɣa zeddɣen din Imiyyen, ijj n řgens d ameqqran d aṭṭas uca nitni d iziraren am Iɛanaqiyyen.\qt*
\v 11 \qt Nitni ttwaḥesben d Irafawiyyen am Iɛanaqiyyen uca ayt n Mu’ab qqaren as Imiyyen.\qt*\f ◼ \fr 2:11 \fk Irafawiyyen\ft - niɣ ‘jjwaheř’.\f*
\v 12 \qt \tl Uřa d\tl* Ixuriyyen tuɣa zeddɣen qbeř di Saɛir, maca ayt n Ɛisu ksin řwart nsen uca teḥḥan ten zzat i wudem nsen uca ggin zeddɣen \tl din\tl* deg wemcan nsen, am mammec tuɣa ittegg Israil s temmurt n řwart nnes, tenni i d asen iwca SIDI.\qt*
\m 
\v 13 ‘Kkarem řexxu, teẓwam teɣzurt n Zarad!’ Uca neẓwa teɣzurt n Zarad.
\v 14 Tmenya u-třatin n iseggʷusa i nuyur zi Qadac-Barniɛ ařami neẓwa taɣzurt n Zarad, ařami iqḍa jjiř nni n iɛeskariyyen inni issnen amenɣi zi řwesṭ n řmargeḥ n řɛeskar, am mammec tuɣa d asen ijjuǧ SIDI.
\v 15 Ammu i xasen tuɣa afus n SIDI, \add ḥima\add* ad ten iteḥḥa zi řwesṭ n řmargeḥ n řɛeskar ařami qḍan marra.
\m 
\v 16 Umi qḍan u mmuten marra iɛeskariyyen inni issnen amenɣi zi řwesṭ n řgens, imsar
\v 17 aqa issiweř akidi SIDI, inna:
\m 
\v 18 ‘Ass-a ad teẓwid aymir n \add temmurt n\add* Mu’ab, ɣar \add tendint n\add* Ɛar.
\v 19 Ad dd-tqarrbed ɣar urendad n ayt n Ɛammun. War ten ttessiggʷid ca, war xasen ttɛeddid ca, minzi war d awem tticeɣ řwart zi temmurt n ayt n Ɛammun, minzi wciɣ tt d řwart i ayt n Luṭ.’
\m 
\v 20 \qt Tᵉttwaḥseb uřa d Ɛammun d ict n temmurt n Irafawiyyen. Tuɣa Irafawiyyen zeddɣen din qbeř u Iɛamuniyyen qqaren asen Izamzumiyyen.\qt*
\v 21 \qt Tuɣa-ten d ijj n řgens imɣar aṭṭas, d azirar \tl n waddud\tl* am Iɛanaqiyyen. Tuɣa yareddeǧ i-ten SIDI zzat i wudem nnes u nitni ksin řwart nsen uca zeddɣen deg wemcan nsen.\qt*
\v 22 \qt Tuɣa Netta igga ammu ɛawed i ayt n Ɛisu, inni tuɣa izedɣen di Saɛir, maɣar iteḥḥa Ixuriyyen zzatsen uca nitni ksin řwart nsen uca zeddɣen din ař ass-a.\qt*
\v 23 \qt Uca Ikafturiyyen nni tuɣa iffɣen zi Kaftur, teḥḥan Iɛawiyyen, inni tuɣa izeddɣen di dcurat ař Ɣazza, uca nitni ggin ad \tl din\tl* zedɣen ař ass-a.\qt*
\m 
\v 24 ‘Kkarem, fesyem \add iqiḍan nwem\add* uca ẓwam taɣzurt \add n teɣzart\add* n Arnun. Xzar, wciɣ Siḥun, ajeǧid n Ḥacbun, Amuri, d temmurt nnes deg ifassen nwem. Bda ad tt teksid uca tadfed akides ɣar garra.
\v 25 Ass-a ad bdiɣ ad arreɣ tiggʷudi d řɛurret zzayek x \add marra\add* řegnus sadu ajenna marra, inni i xak ɣa isřen řexbar uca ad arjijen u ad qdiddsen zzatek.’
\v 26 \add Xenni\add* ssekkeɣ ireqqasen zi řexřa n Qadimut ɣar Siḥun, ajeǧid n Ḥacbun s wawařen n řehna, nniɣ: \x ◘ \xo 2:26 \xt Řxř. 21:21; Řqḍ. 11:19\x*
\v 27 ‘Ad kkeɣ x temmurt nnec d abrid, x webrid ad raḥeɣ. War heyyḍeɣ x \add webrid\add* \add ɣar\add* yefus uřa \add ɣar\add* uzeřmaḍ. \x ◘ \xo 2:27 \xt Řxř. 21:21, 22\x*
\v 28 Ad ayi tezzenzed macca i nnuqart ḥima ad cceɣ, aman ad ayi ten tewced i nnuqart ḥima ad sweɣ. Ad ẓwiɣ x iḍaren inu waha
\v 29 - am mammec d ayi sarrḥen ayt n Ɛisu nni izeddɣen di Saɛir d ayt n Mu’ab nni izeddɣen di Ɛar - ařami ɣa ẓwiɣ L’Urdun ɣar temmurt i d aneɣ ɣa iwc SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ.’
\m 
\v 30 \add Maca\add* Siḥun, ajeǧid n Ḥacbun war ixs ad aneɣ yejj ad tt neẓwa, minzi SIDI, AREBBI nnec, isseqsaḥ buḥbeř nnes, u isseqsaḥ uř nnes ḥima ad t isellem deg ifassen nnec, am \add teǧa\add* ass-a.
\v 31 Uca inna ayi SIDI: ‘Xzar, Necc bdiɣ ad sellmeɣ Siḥun d temmurt nnes ɣarek. Bda ad tt teksid ḥima ad twarted tammurt nnes.’
\v 32 \add Xenni\add* iffeɣ-dd Siḥun ɣar umsagar akidneɣ, netta ak-d marra řgens nnes, i garra di Yahaṣ. \x ◘ \xo 2:32 \xt Řxř. 21:23\x*
\v 33 SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ, isellem aneɣ t uca narni t, netta d iḥenjiren nnes d marra řgens nnes. \x ◘ \xo 2:33 \xt Aɛwd. 29:6\x*
\v 34 Neksi marra tineddam nnes uca nḥarrem kuř tandint \add i uteḥḥi\add*, iryazen d temɣarin d iḥenjiren, war nejji ad iqqim uřa d ijj n umarweř.
\v 35 Mɣir řebhayem d min ittwakeccḍen zi tneddam aqa neksi aya d tkeccaḍt i yixef nneɣ.
\v 36 Zi Aruɛir nni yeǧan ɣar tma n teɣzart n Arnun, u \add zi\add* tendint nni \add yeǧan\add* di teɣzurt ař Jilɛad, war din tuɣi uřa d ict n tendint tuɛřa xaneɣ ɛad. SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ, isellem aneɣ marra. \x ◘ \xo 2:36 \xt Řxř. 21:5; Yac. 13:9, 16; 2 Ṣm. 24:5\x*
\v 37 Maca cek war dd-tqarrbed ca ɣar temmurt n ayt n Ɛammun, marra min tuɣa ɣar tma n teɣzart n Yabbuq d tneddam x idurar, u war dd-tqarrbed ca ɣar uřa d ict n \add temmurt\add* i d aneɣ iḥarrem SIDI.”
\b
\b
\c 3
\m 
\v 1 “\add Xenni\add* nedweř-dd uca ngeɛɛed abrid n Bacan. Iffeɣ-dd Ɛuj, ajeǧid n Bacan, i umsagar akidneɣ, netta d marra řgens nnes, i garra di Idraɛi. \x ◘ \xo 3:1 \xt Řxř. 21:33; Aɛwd. 29:6\x*
\v 2 \add Xenni\add* inna ayi SIDI: ‘War zzayes tteggʷed ca, minzi sellmeɣ t, netta d marra řgens nnes d temmurt nnes, ɣar ifassen nnec uca ad zzayes tegged am mammec teggid s Siḥun, ajeǧid n Imuriyyen nni tuɣa izeddɣen di Ḥacbun.’ \x ◘ \xo 3:2 \xt Řxř. 21:34\x*
\v 3 Uca SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ, isellem Ɛuj, ajeǧid n Bacan d marra řgens nnes ɣar ifassen nneɣ uca narniy t ař mani war nejji ad iqqim uřa d ijj n umarweř.
\v 4 Di řweqt nni neṭṭef marra tineddam. War din tuɣi uřa d ict n tendint war zzaysen tt neṭṭif: settin n tneddam d marra jjihet n Arjub, tageldit n Ɛuj di Bacan.
\v 5 Marra tineddam nni ttwafaryent s řeḥyuḍ d tiwwura d iɛumad i ubelleɛ. Sennej i uya \add tuɣa din\add* aṭṭas n tneddam deg iyyaren.
\v 6 Uca nḥarrem i-tent \add i uteḥḥi\add*, am mammec negga zi Siḥun, ajeǧid n Ḥacbun. Di kuř tandint aqa nḥarrem iryazen d temɣarin d iḥenjiren \add i uteḥḥi\add*.
\v 7 \add Maca\add* neksi i yixef nneɣ marra řebhayem d min iqqimen d takeccaḍt zi tineddam.
\v 8 Ammu i neṭṭef di řweqt nni tammurt zi tnayen n ijeǧiden n Imuriyyen nni iǧan x ujemmaḍ n L’Urdun, zi teɣzart n Arnun ař adrar n Ḥarmun
\v 9 - tenni umi qqaren Iṣayduniyyen s yisem n Hirmun Siryun u Imuriyyen qqaren as Sinir -
\v 10 marra tineddam n řwaṭa \add yuɛřan\add* d marra Jilɛad d marra Bacan ař Salxa d Idraɛi, \add marra\add* tineddam n tgeldit n Ɛuj di Bacan.
\v 11 Minzi mɣir Ɛuj, ajeǧid n Bacan, tuɣa iqqim zi min iqqimen n Irafawiyyen. Xzar, qama nnes d ict n qama n wuzzař, ma war iǧi di Rabba n ayt n Ɛammun? Tuzzeggart nnes tesɛa n iɣaǧen u tiru nnes arebɛa n n iɣaǧen, \add ɛbaren tt\add* s uɣiř n ijj n weryaz.
\v 12 Di řweqt nni neṭṭef tammurt-a d řwart, zi \add tendint n\add* Ɛaruɛir, nni iǧan ɣar teɣzart n Arnun, uřa d azyen n idurar n Jilɛad ak-d tneddam nnes, uca wciɣ tt i Irubiniyyen d Ijadiyyen. \x ◘ \xo 3:12 \xt Řxř. 32:33\x*
\v 13 Min iqqimen n Jilɛad d marra Bacan, tageldit n Ɛuj, wciɣ tt i wezyen n teqbič n Manassa. Marra jjihet n Arjub ak-d marra Bacan qqaren as tammurt n Irafawiyyen.
\v 14 Ya’ir, mmis n Manassa, iṭṭef marra tammurt n Arjub ař weymir i iǧan ak-d Ijacuriyyen d Imaɛkiyyen uca iřaɣa jjwayeh nni s yisem nnes: \add jjihet n\add* Bacan, dcurat n Ya’ir. D wa \add d isem nsen ař\add* ass-a.”
\m 
\v 15 “I Makir wciɣ as Jilɛad.
\v 16 I Irubiniyyen d Ijadiyyen wciɣ asen \add min iqqimen\add* n Jilɛad ař teɣzart n Arnun, \add ař\add* řwesṭ n iɣzar \add nni iǧan\add* d aymir, ař tiɣzart n Yabbuq \add nni iǧan\add* d aymir ak-d ayt n Ɛammun.
\v 17 \add Ɛawed wciɣ asen\add* Řewḍa d L’Urdun \add nni iǧan\add* d aymir zi Kinnarat ař řebḥar n Řewḍa, Řebḥar Ameǧah, wadday n teysarin \add n wedrar n\add* Fisja, ɣar uɣezdis n ccarq.” \f ◼ \fr 3:17 \fk Řebḥar Ameǧaḥ\ft - niɣ ‘Ill Ameǧaḥ’.\f*
\b
\m 
\v 18 “Di řweqt nni weṣṣiɣ kenniw, nniɣ: ‘SIDI, AREBBI nwem, iwca awem tammurt-a, ḥima ad tt tᵉṭṭfem d řwart. Ittxeṣṣa ad teẓwam twejdem i umenɣi zzat i aytmatwem, ayt n Israil, marra ayt n umenɣi. \x ◘ \xo 3:18 \xt Řxř. 32:20\x*
\v 19 Iɛeddeř ad qqimen di tneddam nwem, tenni d awem wciɣ necc, mɣir temɣarin nwem d iḥenjiren nwem d řebhayem nwem - aqa ssneɣ belli ɣarwem aṭṭas n řebhayem -
\v 20 ař ɣa iwc SIDI arraḥet i aytmatwem am mammec i d awem iwca, uca uřa d nitni ad ksin tammurt nni i d asen ɣa iwc SIDI, AREBBI nwem, d řwart x ujemmaḍ n \add yeɣzar n\add* L’Urdun. Xenni iɛeddeř ad dd-tdewřem, kuř ijj ɣar tesɣart i d awem wciɣ necc \add i kuř ijjen zzaywem\add*.’
\v 21 Di řweqt nni weṣṣiɣ i Yacuwa, nniɣ: ‘Tiṭṭawin nnec ẓrint marra min igga SIDI, AREBBI nwem, s tnayen n ijeǧiden-a. Ammu i ɣa yegg SIDI s marra tigeldiwin i ɣar ɣa teẓwid. \x ◘ \xo 3:21 \xt Řxř. 27:18\x*
\v 22 War zzaysen teggʷdem, minzi SIDI, AREBBI nwem, ad immneɣ di ṭṭweɛ nwem.’
\m 
\v 23 Uca ẓuǧeɣ ɣar SIDI di řweqt nni, nniɣ:
\v 24 ‘Sidi inu, SIDI! Cek tebdid ad tessecned i umsexxar nnec řemɣaret nnec d ufus nnec ijehden, minzi man arebbi i din deg ujenna niɣ di temmurt izemmar ad yegg řexdayem d jjehd am mammec ten tᵉttegged Cek? \x ◘ \xo 3:24 \xt 1 Ṣm. 2:2; Izhd. 89:7, 8, 9\x*
\v 25 Ejj ayi ad ẓwiɣ, zawgeɣ Cek, uca ad ẓarɣ tammurt icnan, tenni iǧan x ujemmaḍ n L’Urdun, aqa idurar nni icnan d Lubnan!’
\v 26 Maca SIDI iṣxeḍ xafi \add afugem nnes\add* di ṭṭweɛ nwem uca war d ayi isři. Inna ayi SIDI: ‘Cfa min d ayi tᵉttared, aqa d aṭṭas. War kidi ssiwiř ɛad x tmesřact-a. \x ◘ \xo 3:26 \xt Aɛwd. 1:37; 31:2; 34:4\x*
\v 27 Aři ɣar tqiccat n Fisja uca sgeɛɛed tamuɣři nnec ɣar řɣarb, ɣar ccamal, ɛar ljanub u ɣar ccarq u xzar \add i tt\add* s ixef n tiṭṭawin nnec, minzi war tẓekkʷwid ca L’Urdun-a.
\v 28 Sellem \add řumur\add* i Yacuwa, egg dayes uř u sejhed i-t, minzi netta ad iẓwa zzat i wudem n řgens-a uca netta ad ten yarr ad warten tammurt i ɣa tẓared \add x wedrar Fisja\add*.’
\v 29 Uca neqqim di teɣzurt zzat i Bayt-Faɣur.”
\b
\b
\c 4
\s1 Řɛahd ak-d SIDI AREBBI
\m 
\v 1 “Xenni řexxu, \add a\add* Israil, seř ɣar tweṣṣa d lfarayiḍ nni d awem sseřmadeɣ, maḥend ad \add tent\add* teggem ḥima ad teddarem uca ad tadfem ɣar temmurt nni i d awem ɣa iwc SIDI, AREBBI n řejdud nwem, uca ad tt twartem. \x ◘ \xo 4:1 \xt Lawi 19:37; 20:8; 22:31\x*
\v 2 War arennyem ɣar wawař i d awem ɣa umureɣ u war zzayes ttekksem, ḥima ad tiřim tᵉttᵉṭṭfem di tweṣṣa n SIDI, AREBBI nwem, tinni zi d awem ttumureɣ. \x ◘ \xo 4:2 \xt Aɛwd. 13:1; Awřn. 30:6; Asa. 22:18\x*
\v 3 Tiṭṭawin nwem ẓrint min igga SIDI ak-d Baɛl-Faɣur, minzi \add marra\add* aryaz nni iḍeffaren Baɛl-Faɣur, aqa iteḥḥa i-t SIDI, AREBBI nwem, zi řwesṭ nwem. \x ◘ \xo 4:3 \xt Řxř. 25:4; Yac. 22:17\x*
\v 4 \add Maca\add* kenniw, inni iřessqen ɣar SIDI, AREBBI nwem, aqa kenniw marra teddarem \add ɛad\add* ass-a.
\v 5 Xzarem, necc ssřemdeɣ awem tiweṣṣa d lfarayiḍ am mammec d ayi yumur SIDI, AREBBI inu, ḥima ad \add zzaysent\add* teggem di temmurt i ɣar ɣa tadfem maḥend ad tt twartem.
\v 6 Ṭṭfem \add daysent\add* u ggem \add tent\add*, minzi ta ad tiři tiɣit nwem d řeɛqeř nwem zzat i tiṭṭawin n řegnus nni i ɣa isřen marra tiweṣṣa-ya. \add Xenni\add* ad inin nitni: ‘Řgens-a ameqqran wanita d tidett d ijj n řgens d amiɣis u s řeɛqeř!’ \f ◼ \fr 4:6 \fk Ṭṭfem ... ggem\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘Ṭṭef ... egg’, amecnaw issawař Netta i yijj weryaz.\f*
\v 7 Minzi man řgens imɣaren i da iǧan, aqa ɣares arebbi yudsen am SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ, řebda xmi xas nettřaɣa? \x ◘ \xo 4:7 \xt Aɛwd. 26:19\x*
\v 8 U man řgens da iǧan imɣar, aqa ɣares tiweṣṣa d lfarayiḍ iseggmen am marra Ccariɛa-ya nni d awem ɣa wceɣ ass-a?
\m 
\v 9 Maca ḥḍa x yixef nnec uca ṭṭef nican acbar x řeɛmur nnec ḥima war tᵉttud min ẓrint tiṭṭawin nnec u ḥima \add timesřayin-a\add* war dd-tteffiɣent ca zeg wuřawen nnec. Ittxeṣṣa ad tent tessargbed i iḥenjiren nnec u i iḥenjiren n iḥenjiren nnec. \x ◘ \xo 4:9 \xt Aɛwd. 6:7; 11:19\x*
\m 
\v 10 Ass min di tuɣa tbedded ɣar \add wedrar n\add* Ḥurib zzat i wudem n SIDI, AREBBI nnec, řami d ayi inna SIDI: ‘Smun ɣari řgens-a, \add xenni\add* Necc ad ten arreɣ ad sřen awařen inu maḥend ad ten ssřemden ḥima ad zzayi ggʷeden marra ussan nni iddaren di temmurt uca \add ḥima\add* ad \add ten\add* ssřemden i iḥenjiren nsen.’
\v 11 \add Xenni\add* tqarrbem-dd kenniw uca tbeddem ɣar iḍaren n wedrar uca adrar yarɣa ařami timessi nnes \add tiweḍ\add* ɣar řwesṭ n ujenna, \add uca aqa din\add* taǧest d iseynuten d yijj n useynu ibbumbes. \f ◼ \fr 4:11 \fk ɣar iḍaren\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘sadu’. \fk ɣar řwest\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘ɣar wuř’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 4:11 \xt Uf. 19:18\x*
\m 
\v 12 \add Xenni\add* issiweř akidwem SIDI zi řwesṭ n tmessi. Kenniw tesřim i řḥess n wawařen, \add maca\add* war teẓrim ca addud \add nnes\add*, mɣir ict n tmijja \add umi tesřim\add* waha.
\v 13 Netta issargeb kenniw x Řɛahd nnes, wenni yumur ad t teggem, ɛecra n wawařen. Yura ten di tnayen n teřwiḥin n weẓru.
\v 14 I necc \add ɛawed\add* yumur SIDI di řweqt nni maḥend ad kenniw ssřemdeɣ tiweṣṣa d lfarayiḍ maḥend ad zzaysent teggem di temmurt i ɣar ɣa teẓwam ḥima ad tt twartem.”
\m 
\v 15 “Ḥḍam nican x řeɛmur nwem, minzi kenniw war teẓrim uřa d ijj n waddud deg wass umi akidwem issiweř SIDI \add x wedrar n\add* Ḥurib zi řwesṭ n tmessi!
\v 16 War ttessefsadem \add ixef nwem\add* umi ɣa teggem i yixef nwem ijj n řexyař ineqcen, addud n ca n ijj n ṣṣanam, addud n ca n ijj n wewtem niɣ n ict n tewtemt,
\v 17 ijj n řexyař n ca n ijj n umuddar nni \add iǧan\add* x temmurt, \add niɣ\add* ijj n řexyař n ca n ijj n wejḍiḍ s wefriwen i iṭṭawen deg ujenna,
\v 18 \add niɣ\add* ijj n řexyař n ca n ijj \add n umuddar\add* nni ittbuɛen x temmurt, \add niɣ\add* ijj n řexyař n ca n ijj n wesřem nni iǧan deg waman sadu temmurt.
\v 19 Ɣarek ad tessgeɛɛded tamuɣři nnec ɣar ujenna uca \add xenni\add* ad tẓared tafuct d uyur d itran, marra řɛeskar n ujenna, uca \add xenni\add* ad ttwaɛarrned ad asen tbendqed uca ad asen tɛebded i nitni, inni ibḍa SIDI, AREBBI nnec, i marra řegnus sadu marra ajenna.
\v 20 SIDI aqa iqbeř i kenniw uca issuffeɣ i kenniw-dd zeg ufarran n wuzzař, zi Miṣra, ḥima ad as tiřim d řgens nnes i iwart, am \add teǧa\add* ass-a. \x ◘ \xo 4:20 \xt Uf. 19:5\x*
\v 21 Ɛawed isɛar xafi SIDI di ssibbet n wawařen nwem uca ijjuǧ belli war ẓekkʷwiɣ ca L’Urdun u war ttidfeɣ ɣar temmurt iṣebḥen nni i d ac ɣa iwc SIDI, AREBBI nnec, d řwart, \x ◘ \xo 4:21 \xt Aɛwd. 1:37; 3:26; 31:2; 34:4\x*
\v 22 minzi necc ad mmteɣ di temmurt-a, war ẓekkʷiɣ ca L’Urdun. Kenniw ad teẓwam uca ad tᵉṭṭfem tammurt-a icnan.
\v 23 Ḥḍam war tᵉttum Řɛahd n SIDI, AREBBI nwem, wenni igga akidwem uca \add ḥḍam\add* war tteggem i yixef nwem ijj n řexyař ineqcen zi ca n \add n řḥajjet\add* i d ac iḥarrem SIDI, AREBBI nnec.
\v 24 Minzi SIDI, AREBBI nnec, aqa-t d ict n tmessi ittetten, d ijj n Arebbi ittasmen. \x ◘ \xo 4:24 \xt Uf. 20:5; 34:14; Aɛwd. 5:9; 6:15; 9:3; Ɛbr.12:29 \x*
\m 
\v 25 Xmi ɣa tarwem arraw d ayyawen uca ad tewsarem di temmurt uca \add xenni\add* ad tdeǧmem \add ixef nwem\add*, ad teggem ijj n řexyař ineqcen, ṣṣiffet n ca n řḥajjet uca ad teggem řɣar di tiṭṭawin n SIDI, AREBBI nwem umi t ɣa tesɛarem \add ammu\add*,
\v 26 \add xenni\add* necc ass-a ad řaɣiɣ x ujenna d temmurt d řechud xawem, aqa kenniw ad tᵉttwahellkem deɣya s tidett di temmurt i ɣar ɣa teẓwam x L’Urdun maḥend ad tt teksim d řwart. War dayes tᵉttɣimim kenniw ca n wussan ktar ɛad, minzi ad tᵉttwateḥḥam qaɛ.
\v 27 SIDI ad kenniw ibezzeɛ jar řegnus uca ad zzaywem iqqim ijj n wuru n yeryazen \add waha\add* jar řegnus mani kenniw ɣa indeh SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 4:27 \xt Aɛwd. 28:62, 64\x*
\v 28 Din ad tsexxarem irebbiten nni ittwaggen s ifassen n bnadem s ukeccuḍ d weẓru, inni war ittwařin, war ittesřin, war ittetten u war ittcemman.”\x ◘ \xo 4:28 \xt Izhd. 115:4; 135:15\x*
\m 
\v 29 “Ad tarzum ssenni SIDI, AREBBI nnec, u cek ad t tafed, mařa tarezzud xas s marra uř nnec d marra řeɛmar nnec. \f ◼ \fr 4:29 \fk ssenni\ft - niɣ ‘zi senni’.\f*
\v 30 Mařa cek di řeḥṣaret uca ad ɣarek dd-asen marra awařen-a deg uneggar n wussan, \add xenni\add* ad dd-tdewřed ɣar SIDI, AREBBI nnec, u ad tesřed i tmijja nnes,
\v 31 minzi SIDI, AREBBI nnec, d ijj n Arebbi yareḥḥmen, war cek ittejji u war cek ittareddeǧ. War ittettu Řɛahd n řejdud nnec, wenni d asen ijjuǧ.
\v 32 Seqsa xenni x wussan iɛdun, inni iǧan qbeř i cek, zeg wass min di igga AREBBI bnadem x temmurt, \add seqsa\add* zi ṭṭarf n ujenna ɣar ṭṭarf nneɣni n ujenna, ma \add ɛemmarṣ\add* temsar ca n řḥajjet temɣar anect n tanita niɣ ittwaseř \add ca\add* am man aya?
\v 33 Ma \add ɛemmarṣ\add* isřa ca n řgens tmijja n AREBBI tessiweř zi řwesṭ n tmessi am mammec tt ttesřid cek uca \add xenni iqqim\add* iddar?
\v 34 Niɣ ma iqeǧeb \add ɛemmarṣ\add* ijj n arebbi ad dd-yas maḥend ad iksi i yixef nnes ijj n řgens zi řwesṭ n ijj n řgens \add nneɣni\add* s tjarribin, s řeɛřamat, s lmuɛjizat, s umenɣi, s ufus ijehden, s uɣiř isswiẓẓḍen u s tmegga ssiggʷident mɣarent, am marra min igga SIDI, AREBBI nwem, zzat i tiṭṭawin nwem di Miṣra?
\v 35 Aqa i cek umi dd-ittwassban aya, ḥima ad tessned belli SIDI d AREBBI \add i iǧa\add*. War din ca nneɣni mɣir Netta.\x ◘ \xo 4:35 \xt Aɛwd. 32:39; Ica. 45:5, 18, 22; Mk.12:29,32\x*
\v 36 Zeg ujenna igga ad tesřed i tmijja nnes ḥima ad cek inebbeh u x temmurt aqa isscen ac timessi nnes imɣaren u aqa tesřid awařen nnes zi řwesṭ n tmessi.
\v 37 Minzi Netta tuɣa ixs řejdud nnec, u ifarz zzariɛet nnes awarni as, aqa issuffeɣ i cek-dd s Yixef nnes zi Miṣra s jjehd nnes imɣaren \x ◘ \xo 4:37 \xt Uf. 13:3, 9, 14\x*
\v 38 ḥima ad yaẓẓeř zzat i wudem nnec x řegnus imɣaren d yinni xak ijehden zi teṣɣart nsen, u \add ḥima\add* ad dayes issidef cek u ad ac iwc tammurt nsen d řwart, am mammec \add i teǧa\add* ass-a.
\v 39 \add Xenni\add* ssen ass-a uca xarreṣ \add x man aya\add* deg wuř nnec belli SIDI d AREBBI i yeǧa, sennej deg ujenna u swadday di temmurt, war din ḥed nneɣni!
\v 40 Ṭṭef di tweṣṣa nnes u di řumurat nnes, tinni d ac umureɣ ass-a ḥima ad iffeɣ umeddur mliḥ i cek u i iḥenjiren nnec awarni ac uca ad zzugarten ussan di temmurt i d ac ɣa iwc SIDI, AREBBI nnec, i řebda.”
\m 
\v 41 Xenni ifarz Musa \bd třata n tneddam \bdit n tarewřa\bdit* x ujemmaḍ n L’Urdun\bd* manis dd-tneqqar tfuct, \x ◘ \xo 4:41 \xt Řxř. 35:6, 14\x*
\v 42 ḥima ad din yařwer uqettař nni inɣin, břa ma ad as igg řeḥsab, jjar nnes, wenni umi war icarrhen ɛemmarṣ \add iḍennaḍ uřa d fariḍennaḍ\add*. Wanita izemmar ad yarweř ɣar ict zi tneddam-a ařami \add iqqim\add* iddar netta.
\v 43 Baṣir di řexřa, di řwaṭa \add yuɛřan\add*, i Rubiniyyen, u Ramut di Jilɛad i Ijadiyyen u Julan d Bacan i Imanassiyyen. \x ◘ \xo 4:43 \xt Yac. 20:8\x*
\m 
\v 44 Ta d Ccariɛa nni igga Musa zzat i ayt n Israil.
\v 45 Ina d cchadat d tiweṣṣa d lfarayiḍ nni issiweř Musa ɣar ayt n Israil umi dd-ffɣen zi Miṣra.
\v 46 \add Aya tuɣa\add* x ujemmaḍ n L’Urdun, di teɣzurt arendad n Bayt-Faɣur, di temmurt n Siḥun, ajeǧid n Imuriyyen, wenni tuɣa izeddɣen di Ḥacbun, wenni x iɣřeb Musa ak-d ayt n Israil umi dd-ffɣen zi Miṣra. \x ◘ \xo 4:46 \xt Řxř. 21:24; Aɛwd. 1:4 \x*
\v 47 \add Aqa\add* ksin tammurt nnes am řwart uřa d tammurt n Ɛuj, ajeǧid n Bacan, \add timmura n\add* tnayen n ijeǧiden n Imuriyyen nni \add tuɣa zeddɣen\add* x ujemmaḍ n L’Urdun manis dd-tneqqar tfuct, \x ◘ \xo 4:47 \xt Řxř. 21:33; Aɛwd. 3:3\x*
\v 48 zi Ɛaruɛir nni iǧan ɣar tma n teɣzart n Arnun ař wedrar n Siyun nni iǧan d \add wedrar n\add* Ḥirmun,
\v 49 d marra řewḍa x ujemmaḍ n L’Urdun, ɣar ccarq, ař Řebḥar n Řewḍa nni \add iǧan\add* wadday n teysarin \add n wedrar n\add* Fisja.
\b
\b
\c 5
\m 
\v 1 Iřaɣa Musa i marra Israil uca inna asen: “Sřem, a Israil, i tweṣṣa d lfarayiḍ, tinni i xef ssiwřeɣ necc ass-a deg imezzuɣen nwem, ḥima ad tent třemdem u ad tent teḥḍam maḥend ad zzaysent teggem.
\v 2 SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ, igga ijj n Řɛahd akidneɣ di Ḥurib. \x ◘ \xo 5:2 \xt Uf. 19:5\x*
\v 3 War iǧi ak-d řejdud nneɣ i igga AREBBI Řɛahd-a, maca akidneɣ, neccin, inni da \add ibedden\add* ddaren marra ass-a.
\v 4 Udem ak-d wudem issiweř akidwem SIDI x wedrar, zi řwesṭ n tmessi.
\v 5 Tuɣa ayi di řweqt nni beddeɣ jar SIDI d kenniw ḥima ad kenniw ssaregbeɣ x wawař n SIDI, minzi tuɣa kenniw teggʷdem zi tmessi u war tgeɛɛadem ca ɣar wedrar. \add Uca\add* Netta inna: \x ◘ \xo 5:5 \xt Uf. 19:16; 20:18\x*
\b
\m 
\v 6 ‘Necc d SIDI, AREBBI nnec, wenni cek-dd issuffɣen zi temmurt n Miṣra, zi taddart n tesmuɣi. \x ◘ \xo 5:6 \xt Uf. 20:2-21; Izhd. 81:11\x*
\v 7 \bd War ɣarek ttiřin ca irebbiten nneɣni\bd* zzat i wudem inu.
\m 
\v 8 War ttegg i yixef nnec ijj n řexyař ineqcen \add niɣ\add* min ma řexyař n min \add din iǧan\add* sennej deg ujenna niɣ swadday x temmurt niɣ deg waman sadu temmurt.
\v 9 War d asen ttbendeq u ad asen tɛebded, minzi Necc, SIDI, AREBBI nnec, d ijj n Arebbi ittasmen, wenni dd-yarezfen řmuɛṣiyyet n ibabaten deg iḥenjiren ař \add jjiř\add* wiss třata u wiss arebɛa n yinni d ayi icarrhen, \x ◘ \xo 5:9 \xt Uf. 20:5; 34:7, 14; Irm. 32:18\x*
\v 10 \add maca\add* wenni issecnen tamexsiwt icewwaren i řuřuf n yinni d ayi ittexsen u ḥeṭṭan tiweṣṣa inu.
\m 
\v 11 \bd War neṭṭeq s Yisem n SIDI, AREBBI nnec, di řbaṭeř,\bd* minzi SIDI war ittbarri wenni i ɣa ineṭqen s Yisem nnes di řbaṭeř. \x ◘ \xo 5:11 \xt Lawi 19:12; Mt. 5:33\x*
\m 
\v 12 \bd Ḥḍa ass n ssebt\bd* ḥima ad t tessqeddsed am mammec d ac yumur SIDI, AREBBI nnec. \x ◘ \xo 5:12 \xt Amz. 2:2; Uf. 23:12; 35:2; Lawi 23:3; Ḥiz. 20:12; Ɛbr. 4:4 \x*
\v 13 Setta n wussan ad txedmed, ad tegged marra řxedmet nnec,
\v 14 maca ass wiss sebɛa d ass n ssebt n SIDI, AREBBI nnec. War \add dayes\add* tᵉttegged uřa d ict n řxedmet, cek \add lla\add* uřa d mmic d yeǧic d yismeɣ nnec d tayya nnec d ufunas nnec d weɣyuř nnec d řebhayem nnec uřa d abarrani nni \add akik\add* iǧan daxeř i tewwura nnec \add lla\add*, ḥima ismeɣ nnec d tayya nnec ad areyyḥen am cek.
\v 15 Ad tɛeqřem belli tuɣa cek d ismeɣ di temmurt n Miṣra u SIDI, AREBBI nnec, aqa issuffeɣ i cek-dd ssenni s yijj n ufus ijehden d ijj n uɣiř isswiẓẓḍen. X uya yumur cek SIDI, AREBBI nnec, ad teḥḍid ass n ssebt.
\m 
\v 16 \bd Weqqar babac d yemmac\bd*, am mammec i d ak yumur SIDI, AREBBI nnec maḥend ussan \add n tudart\add* nnec \add zemmaren\add* ad zzuggarten uca ad iffeɣ umeddur nnec mliḥ x wudem \add n temmurt\add* i d ac ɣa iwc SIDI, AREBBI nnec. \x ◘ \xo 5:16 \xt Lawi 19:3; Mt. 15:4; Lk. 18:20; Afa. 6:2, 3\x*
\m 
\v 17 \bd War neqq.\bd* \x ◘ \xo 5:17 \xt Mt. 5:21; Lk. 18:20; Rum. 13:9 \x*
\m 
\v 18 \bd War zenna.\bd* \x ◘ \xo 5:18 \xt Lk. 18:20\x*
\m 
\v 19 \bd War ttacar.\bd*
\m 
\v 20 \bd War cehhed s ẓur\bd* ḍidd i jjar nnec.
\m 
\v 21 \bd War ttegg meẓri di temɣart n jjar nnec\bd* u war ḍemmeɛ di taddart n jjar nnec, niɣ deg iyyar nnes, niɣ deg yismeɣ nnes, niɣ di tayya nnes, niɣ deg ufunas nnes, niɣ deg weɣyuř nnes, niɣ di ca zi marra min iǧan ɣar jjar nnec.’ \x ◘ \xo 5:21 \xt Rum. 7:7\x*
\b
\m 
\v 22 Issiweř SIDI awařen-a ak-d marra agraw nwem \add n řgens\add* s ict n tmijja ijehden x wedrar, zi řwesṭ n tmessi, zeg iseynuten u zeg useynu ibbumbes u war immarni ca ktar. Yuri ten x tnayen n teřwiḥin n weẓru uca iwca i-tent i necc. \x ◘ \xo 5:22 \xt Aɛwd. 9:10, 11\x*
\v 23 Uca imsar, umi tesřim kenniw i tmijja zi řwesṭ n taǧest uca adrar icemmeḍ s tmessi, aqa tqarrbem-dd ɣari, marra izeǧifen n tqebbař nwem d imɣaren nwem,
\v 24 tennam ayi: ‘Xzar, SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ, isscen aneɣ-dd aɛuǧi nnes d řemɣaret nnes uca nesřa i tmijja nnes zi řwesṭ n tmessi. Ass-a neẓra belli SIDI issiweř ak-d bnadem uca wa \add iqqim\add* iddar.
\v 25 Řexxu \add xenni\add*, mayemmi ɣa nemmet? Minzi timessi-ya imɣaren ad aneɣ tecc. Mařa neqqim nᵉttesřa i tmijja n SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ, ad nemmet.
\v 26 Minzi man wen \add i din yeǧan\add* jar marra min ɣares arrimet, wenni isřan i tmijja n AREBBI iddaren tessiweř-dd zi řwesṭ n tmessi am neccin, d wenni iddaren \add ɛad\add*? \x ◘ \xo 5:26 \xt Aɛwd. 4:33; Řqḍ. 13:22\x*
\v 27 Ad dd-tqarrbed cek u ad tesřed ɣar marra min ɣa yini SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ, uca \add xenni\add* ad tessiwřed akidneɣ x marra min d ac ɣa yini SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ, u neccin ad \add as\add* nseř uca ad \add zzayes\add* negg.’ \x ◘ \xo 5:27 \xt Uf. 20:19; Ɛbr. 12:19\x*
\m 
\v 28 Isřa SIDI i tmijja n wawařen nwem umi kidi tessiwřem uca inna ayi SIDI: ‘Sřiɣ i tmijja n wawařen n řgens-a, \add awařen\add* nni kik ssiwřen. Aqa mliḥ, marra kik ssiwřen nitni.
\v 29 Iři ad asen immewc ijj n wuř maḥend ad ayi ggʷeden uca ad ḥḍan tiweṣṣa inu marra ussan qaɛ ḥima nitni d tarwa nsen ad iřin mliḥ i řebda!
\v 30 Ruḥ, tinid asen: Dewřem-dd ɣar iqiḍan nwem!
\v 31 Uca cek, bedd da kidi, ḥima ad akidek ssiwřeɣ tiweṣṣa d lfarayiḍ nni i d asen ɣa tessřemded ḥima ad zzaysent ggen di temmurt nni i d asen ɣa wceɣ d řwart.’
\v 32 Ḥḍam ḥima ad teggem am mammec i d awem yumur SIDI, AREBBI nwem, war ttḥeyydem \add x man aya\add*, war iǧi \add ɣar\add* yefus uřa \add ɣar\add* uzeřmaḍ.
\v 33 Ad tuyurem marra abrid nni d awem yumur SIDI, AREBBI nwem, ḥima ad teddarem uca ad tiřim mliḥ u ḥima ad zzuggarten ussan nwem di temmurt nni i ɣa teksim d řwart.”
\b
\b
\c 6
\m 
\v 1 “Tina d tiweṣṣa d lfarayiḍ nni yumur SIDI, AREBBI nwem, maḥend ad awem tent ssřemdeɣ, ḥima ad zzaysent teggem di temmurt i ɣar ɣa teẓwam maḥend ad tt teksim d řwart,
\v 2 ḥima ad teggʷded SIDI, AREBBI nnec, uca ad teḥḍid marra tiweṣṣa nnes d řumurat nnes nni i d ac umureɣ, cek d mmic d mmis n mmic, marra ussan n tudart nnec, ḥima ussan \add n tudart\add* nnec ad zzuggarten.
\v 3 Seř, a Israil, ḥḍa ad \add zzaysent\add* tegged, ḥima ad tiřid mliḥ u ḥima kenniw ad temmarnim s waṭṭas di temmurt ifeyyḍen s uɣi d tamment, am mammec tuɣa inna SIDI, AREBBI n řejdud nnec.”
\b
\m 
\v 4 “Seř, a Israil, SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ, SIDI d Ijj. \x ◘ \xo 6:4 \xt Aɛwd. 4:35; Mk. 12:29; Yḥ. 17:3; 1 Kur. 8:4, 6\x*
\v 5 Ad texsed SIDI, AREBBI nnec, s marra wuř nnec u s marra řeɛmar nnec u s marra jjehd nnec.\x ◘ \xo 6:5 \xt Aɛwd. 10:12; Mt. 22:37; Mk. 12:20, 33; Lk. 10:27\x*
\b
\m 
\v 6 Awařen-a nni i d ac umureɣ ass-a, ad iřin deg wuř nnec.
\v 7 Ad ten tessiggzed i iḥenjiren nnec uca ad xasent tessiwřed xmi ɣa teqqimed di taddart nnec u xmi ɣa tuyured deg webrid u xmi ɣa tᵉṭṭṣed u xmi ɣa tekkared.\x ◘ \xo 6:7 \xt Aɛwd. 4:9; 11:19\x*
\v 8 Ad ten tbeysed am yict n řeɛřamet deg ufus nnec, ad iřint am yijj n ufiřu n useggem jar tiṭṭawin nnec.
\v 9 Uca ad ten tarid x řeḍruf \add ɣar uɣezdis n tewwart\add* n taddart nnec u di tewwura nnec.”
\b
\m 
\v 10 “Uca ad imsar, xmi SIDI, AREBBI nnec, ad cek yawi di temmurt i x ijjuǧ i řejdud nwem, i Ibrahim d Isḥaq d Yaɛqub, maḥend ad ac tt iwc, \add s\add* tneddam imɣaren icnan, tinni war tebnid cek
\v 11 u s tudrin iccuren \add s\add* marra řxar i zi war \add tent\add* teccured cek, u \add s\add* teɣzin nni cek war teɣzid, u \add s\add* tzayarin d tzemmurin nni war teẓẓud cek. Uca xmi ɣa tecced u ad tejjiwned, \x ◘ \xo 6:11 \xt Aɛwd. 8:9, 10\x*
\v 12 ḥḍa \add xenni\add* maḥend war ttᵉttud SIDI wenni cek dd-issuffɣen zi temmurt n Miṣra, zi taddart n tesmuɣi.
\m 
\v 13 Ad teggʷded SIDI, AREBBI nnec, ad t tɛebded u s Yisem nnes ad tejjaǧed.\x ◘ \xo 6:13 \xt Aɛwd. 10:20; Mt. 4:10; Lk. 4:8\x*
\v 14 War ggurem awarni i irebbiten nneɣni zi irebbiten n řegnus i d awem dd-innḍen
\v 15 - minzi SIDI, AREBBI nwem d ijj n Arebbi ittasmen di řwesṭ nnec - ḥima war xak yareqq weɣḍab n SIDI, AREBBI nnec, uca ad cek iteḥḥa zeg \add wudem n\add* temmurt.
\m 
\v 16 War ttqeǧabem ca SIDI, AREBBI nwem, am mammec \add t\add* tqeǧbem di Massa. \x ◘ \xo 6:16 \xt Uf. 17:2; Řxř. 20:3; Mt. 4:7; Lk. 4:12 \x*
\v 17 Ad teḥḍid nican řumurat n SIDI, AREBBI nwem uřa d cchadat nnes d tweṣṣa nnes nni i d ac yumur.
\v 18 Egg min iǧan iseggden d min icnan di tiṭṭawin n SIDI, ḥima ad tiřid mliḥ u ḥima ad tadfed ɣar temmurt icnan i zi ijjuǧ SIDI i řejdud nnec, \add ḥima ad asen tt iwc\add*.
\v 19 ḥima ad taẓẓřed x marra řɛedyan zzat i wudem nnec, am mammec issiweř SIDI.”
\b
\m 
\v 20 “Xmi cek ɣa isseqsa mmic, ad yini: ‘Min teɛna cchadat d tweṣṣa d lfarayiḍ nni d awem yumur SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ?’,
\v 21 \add xenni\add* ad tinid i mmic: ‘Neccin tuɣa aneɣ d isemɣan n firɛun di Miṣra, \add maca\add* SIDI issuffeɣ aneɣ-dd zi Miṣra s ufus ijehden.
\v 22 SIDI igga, qibač i tiṭṭawin nneɣ, řeɛřamat d lmuɛjizat imɣaren d issiggʷden di Miṣra, ɣar firɛun u ɣar marra taddart nnes.
\v 23 Uca issuffeɣ aneɣ-dd ssenni ḥima ad aneɣ issidef maḥend ad aneɣ yewc tammurt nni x ijjuǧ i řejdud nneɣ,\add ḥima ad asen tt iwc\add*.
\v 24 SIDI yumur aneɣ ad negg ɛlaḥsab marra tiweṣṣa-ya, ad neggʷed zi SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ, i řebda, di ṭṭweɛ n tizi nneɣ ḥima ad neddar am \add teǧa\add* ass-a.
\v 25 Man aya ad yiři d tasegda nneɣ xmi ɣa neḥḍa maḥend ad negg marra řumurat-a zzat i wudem n SIDI, am mammec d aneɣ yumur Netta.”
\b
\b
\c 7
\s1 Israil d imezdaɣ n Kenɛan
\m 
\v 1 “Xmi SIDI, AREBBI nnec, ad cek issidef di temmurt mani ɣa traḥed maḥend ad tt teksid d řwart, uca Netta ad yaẓẓeř zi zzatek aṭṭas n řegnus: Iḥittiyyen d Ijirjaciyyen d Imuriyyen d ayt n Kenɛan d Ifiriziyyen d Iḥiwiyyen d Iyabusiyyen, sebɛa n řegnus mɣaren u jehden xak aṭṭas, \x ◘ \xo 7:1 \xt Aɛwd. 31:3\x*
\v 2 uca SIDI, AREBBI nnec, ad ten isellem zzat i wudem nnec u cek ad ten tɣeřbed, \add xenni\add* ittxeṣṣa ad ten tḥarrmed qaɛ i uteḥḥi. War kisen ttegg řɛahd u war d asen sscen řeḥnunect nnec. \x ◘ \xo 7:2 \xt Uf. 23:32; 34:15; Řxř. 33:52; Yac. 11:11 \x*
\v 3 War teddikkwiřem d iḍeggʷařen ɛawed akidsen. War ttic yeǧic i mmis u war dd-ttawi yeǧis i mmic, \x ◘ \xo 7:3 \xt Uf. 34:16; 1 Ij. 11:2; Ɛiz. 9:12\x*
\v 4 minzi aya ad yarr mmic ad dd-idweř zi ḍeffar inu uca ad isexxar i irebbiten nneɣni uca \add ammu\add* ad xawem yareɣ weɣḍab n SIDI uca ad kenniw iteḥḥa deɣya.
\v 5 Ammu \add maca\add* i ittxeṣṣa ad kisen teggem: ad thedmem iɛalṭaren nsen, ad tarẓam imayḍuten nsen \add iqeddsen\add* u ad thedmen tirebbin nsen n cwarti uca ad tesscemḍem řexyařat nsen ineqcen n ukeccuḍ s tmessi. \x ◘ \xo 7:5 \xt Uf. 23:24; 34:13; Aɛwd. 12:2, 3\x*
\v 6 Minzi cek d ijj n řgens iqeddes i SIDI, AREBBI nnec. SIDI, AREBBI nnec, wenni cek ifarzen ḥima ad as tiřid d ijj n řgens iɣřan x marra řegnus \add nni yeǧan\add* x wudem n temmurt. \x ◘ \xo 7:6 \xt Uf. 19:5; Aɛwd. 4:20; 14:21; 26:18; 28:9; 1 Bṭ. 2:9\x*
\v 7 SIDI war ɣarwem iqqen u war kenniw ixḍar umi tuɣa kenniw d aṭṭas zi marra řegnus, minzi tuɣa kenniw teswam qell jar marra řegnus,
\v 8 maca tayri n SIDI i kenniw d uḥeṭṭu nnes x tjaǧit nni ijjuǧ i řejdud nwem, \add tajaǧit\add* i zi kenniw dd-issuffeɣ SIDI s ufus ijehden d \add i zi\add* cek issenjem zi taddart n tesmuɣi, zeg ufus n firɛun, ajeǧid n Miṣra. \x ◘ \xo 7:8 \xt Aɛwd. 10:15\x*
\v 9 Ssen xenni, belli SIDI, AREBBI nnec, d AREBBI, aqa Netta d Arebbi amtiqqi, wenni iḥeṭṭan Řɛahd d tmexsiwt icewwaren zi jjihet n yinni t ittexsen uca ḥeṭṭan řumurat nnes, ař jjiř wiss ařef, \x ◘ \xo 7:9 \xt Uf. 20:5; Aɛwd. 5:9\x*
\v 10 \add maca\add* marra wi t icarrhen deg uɣembub nnes, aqa Netta ad zzaysen tt ixřef am ten i ɣa yareddeǧ. War ittriji, maḥend ad ixeǧeṣ wenni t icarrhen deg uɣembub nnes. \x ◘ \xo 7:10 \xt Nḥm. 1:2\x*
\m 
\v 11 Ḥḍa xenni řumurat d tweṣṣa d lfarayiḍ nni d ac umureɣ necc ass-a maḥend ad zzaysent tegged.”
\m 
\v 12 “Ad imsar, umi tesřim i lfarayiḍ-a u kenniw ad tent teḥḍam u ad zzaysent teggem, aqa SIDI, AREBBI nnec, ad ac ibedd x Řɛahd d tamexsiwt icewwaren i tuɣa ijjuǧ i řejdud nnec. \x ◘ \xo 7:12 \xt Lawi 26:3; Aɛwd. 28:1\x*
\v 13 Netta ad cek ixs, ad cek ibarek u ad cek yarr deg waṭṭas. Ad ibarek řɣiǧet n uɛeddis nnec d řɣiǧet n temmurt nnec, irden nnec, binu nnec n jdid, zzect nnec \add n ṭṭri\add*, tarrawt n tfunasin nnec d imeẓyanen iɛizzen n wuǧi nnec, di temmurt nni tuɣa ijjuǧ i řejdud nnek ad ac tt-i-dd-iwc.
\v 14 Aqa cek tᵉttwabarked jar řegnus! War dayek ittɣimi \add ɛad\add* ḥed i war dd-ittejjin uřa d tenni war ittiriwen, uca ammu uřa di řebhayem nnec. \x ◘ \xo 7:14 \xt Uf. 23:26\x*
\v 15 Ad zzayek ikkes SIDI marra řehřac u war cek iřeqqef uřa s ca n řehřacat tiɛeffanint i ɣarek ittwassnen zi Miṣra, \add maca\add* Netta ad tent issiweḍ x marra inni i cek icarrhen.
\v 16 Ad tecced marra řegnus nni d ac ɣa iwc SIDI, AREBBI nnec. Tiṭṭ nnec war xasen tᵉttḥinni u irebbiten nsen war ten tsexxared, minzi aya ad yiři d řfex i cek.
\v 17 Mařa tennid deg wuř nnec: Řegnus-a mɣaren xafi, mammec ɣa zemmareɣ ad zzaysen kkseɣ \add ɛemmarṣ\add* řwart nsen?
\v 18 \add Xenni\add* war zzaysen tteggʷed. Xarreṣ mliḥ di min igga SIDI, AREBBI nnec, ak-d firɛun u ak-d marra Imiṣriyyen,
\v 19 \add xarreṣ di\add* tqeǧabin imɣaren, tinni teẓrid s tiṭṭawin nnec u \add di\add* řeɛřamat d lmuɛjizat d ufus ijehden d uɣiř isswiẓẓḍen ak-d wi cek dd-issuffeɣ SIDI, AREBBI nnec. Ammu i ɣa yegg SIDI, AREBBI nnec, s marra řegnus i zi tteggʷeded. \x ◘ \xo 7:19 \xt Aɛwd. 4:34; 29:3\x*
\v 20 SIDI, AREBBI nnec, ad issekk irezzan iḍarɣařen jar asen, ař ɣa ttwahellken inni iqqimen, inni ittwassnuffaren zzatek. \x ◘ \xo 7:20 \xt Uf. 23:28; Yac. 24:12\x*
\v 21 War tteggʷed zzat i wudem nsen, minzi SIDI, AREBBI nnec, aqa-t di řwesṭ nnec, aqa-t d Arebbi imɣaren u issaggʷaden.
\v 22 SIDI, AREBBI nnec, ad issuffeɣ řegnus-a zzatek cwayt cwayt. War izemmar ad xasen teqḍid deɣya, mařa lla ad mmarenyen řewḥuc deg iyyar aṭṭas xak.
\v 23 SIDI, AREBBI nnec, ad ten isellem zzat i wudem nnec u ad ten issxarweḍ s yijj n uxarweḍ imɣar ař ɣa ttwateḥḥan.
\v 24 Ad isellem ijeǧiden nsen deg ufus nnec uca ad temḥid isem nsen zi sadu ujenna. Uřa d ijj n weryaz war izemmar ad ibedd zzat i wudem nnec ař ten ɣa tᵉteḥḥid.
\v 25 Řexyařat ineqcen ad tent tesscemḍed s tmessi. Nnuqart d wureɣ i xasent iǧan war dayes ɛecceq u war t kessi i yixef nnec, ḥima war zzayes tᵉttxarwiḍed, minzi aya d ict n jjɛifect i SIDI, AREBBI nnec.
\v 26 War ttiwi ict n jjɛifect \add am ta\add* ɣar taddart nnec, mařa lla ad tᵉttwaḥarrmed \add i uteḥḥi\add* am netta. Ad zzayes tɛiffed aṭṭas u ad ac tiři d tamennɛit, minzi aqa-tt d ict n řqecɛet n řeḥram.”
\b
\b
\c 8
\s1 Sřem i SIDI AREBBI uca ṭṭfem di Řɛahd nnes
\m 
\v 1 “Ad teḥḍam marra řumurat i zi d awem umureɣ ass-a, maḥend ad tent teggem, ḥima ad teddarem u ad temmarenyem uca ad tadfem ɣar temmurt, tenni ijjuǧ SIDI i řejdud nwem, uca ad tt teksim d řwart.
\v 2 Ad tidared marra abrid x mani cek igewwed SIDI, AREBBI nnec, arebɛin n iseggʷusa di řexřa ḥima ad cek isswaḍeɛ u ad cek iqeǧeb maḥend ad issen min \add din\add* deg wuř nnec, ma ad teḥḍid řumurat nnes niɣ lla.
\v 3 Netta isswaḍeɛ i cek u issřaẓ i cek u iwca ac ‘manna’ d macca, tenni war tessined ca cek uřa d řejdud nnec war tt ssinen ca, ḥima ad ac isscen belli bnadem war iddar s weɣrum waha, maca aqa bnadem iddar s marra min dd-iffɣen zeg uqemmum n SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 8:3 \xt Uf. 16:14, 15; Mt. 4:4; Lk. 4:4\x*
\v 4 Arruḍ nnec \add ɛemmarṣ\add* war xak iwsar uřa d aḍar nnec war yuff ca di \add marra\add* arebɛin n iseggʷusa-ya.\x ◘ \xo 8:4 \xt Aɛwd. 29:6; Naḥ. 9:21\x*
\v 5 Sen deg wuř nnec, belli SIDI, AREBBI nnec, aqa yarebba i cek, am mammec yarebba aryaz mmis
\v 6 uca ḥḍa řumurat n SIDI, AREBBI nnec, ařami teǧid deg ibriden nnes u ařami zzayes tteggʷeded.”
\b
\m 
\v 7 “Minzi SIDI, AREBBI nnec,
\m ad cek issidef
\m deg ict n temmurt icnan,
\m ict n temmurt n tɣezratin
\m d řɛunṣarat d \add waman\add* ihewřen,
\m inni dd-iffɣen zi teysart d wedrar,
\m 
\v 8 ict n temmurt n irden
\m d imendi d tzayarin
\m d wartan n tazart d iremmamen,
\m ict n temmurt \add teccur\add*
\m s zzect n tzitunt u n tamment,
\m 
\v 9 ict n temmurt mani ɣa tecced aɣrum
\m umi war din řexṣeṣ
\m u war cek ittxeṣṣi ca dayes,
\m ict n temmurt, iẓra nnes
\m \add ccuren\add* s wuzzař
\m u zeg idurar nnes ad tneqced nnḥas.
\m 
\v 10 Mařa teccid u tejjiwned,
\m ad tbarked SIDI, AREBBI nnec,
\m x temmurt icnan, tenni d ac iwca.” \x ◘ \xo 8:10 \xt Aɛwd. 6:11, 12\x*
\b
\m 
\v 11 “Ḥḍa ixef nnec, ḥima war tᵉttud SIDI, AREBBI nnec, ařami war teḥḍid řumurat nnes, lfarayiḍ nnes d tweṣṣa nnes, tinni d ac umureɣ ass-a,
\v 12 ḥima war ittiři - mařa teccid u tejjiwned uca aqa tebnid tudrin icnan, tinni i di teggid ad \add daysent\add* tzedɣed,
\v 13 uca ifunasen d tfunasin nnec d wuǧi nnec ttwammarnin u nnuqart d wureɣ nni ɣarek aqa ttwammarnin, u marra min ɣarek aqa ittwammarni -
\v 14 ad tessgeɛɛded uř nnec, ad tᵉttud SIDI, AREBBI nnec, wenni cek dd-issuffɣen zi temmurt n Miṣra, zi taddart n tesmuɣi ...
\b
\m 
\v 15 \bdit d Wenni\bdit* i cek dd-inedhen di řexřa imɣaren u issaggʷaden mani tuɣa ifiɣran yarɣin d tɣarḍmiwin uřa di tammurt ittfadan břa aman,
\m \bdit d Wenni\bdit* dd-issuffɣen aman zeg weẓru n sseǧaḥ, \x ◘ \xo 8:15 \xt Uf. 17:6; Řxř. 20:11; Izhd. 78:15; 114:8\x*
\m 
\v 16 \bdit d Wenni\bdit* d ac iwcin ‘manna’ i macca di řexřa, \add manna\add* nni war ssinen řejdud nwem, ḥima ad cek isswaḍeɛ u ḥima ad cek iqeǧeb u ḥima ad ac igg tcuni ɣar uneggar, \x ◘ \xo 8:16 \xt Uf. 16:14, 15\x*
\b
\m 
\v 17 uca \add xenni\add* ad tinid deg wuř nnec: ‘\add S\add* tzemmar inu d jjehd n ufus inu ṭṭfeɣ marra řeksibet-a i yixef inu.’
\v 18 Idar SIDI, AREBBI nnec aqa Netta i d ac iwcin jjehd ḥima ad tkesbed ict n řeksibet temɣar maḥend ad imten \add ammu\add* Řɛahd nnes nni tuɣa ijjuǧ i řejdud nnec, am \add teǧa\add* ass-a.
\v 19 Mařa tiwḍed ad tᵉttud SIDI, AREBBI nnec, uca ad tuyured awarni i irebbiten nneɣni, ad asen tɛebded u ad asen tbendqed, necc ass-a barrḥeɣ ac-dd, aqa ad tᵉttwahellkem s ttidet.
\v 20 Ad tᵉttwahellkem am řegnus nni x yuẓẓeř SIDI zzat i wudem nwem, minzi war tesřim i tmijja n SIDI, AREBBI nwem.”
\b
\b
\c 9
\s1 Tnayen n teřwiḥin timezwura n weẓru
\m 
\v 1 “Seř, Israil, ass-a ad teẓwid L’Urdun, maḥend ad tadfed \add ɣar temmurt\add*, ḥima ad tekksed řwart n řegnus imɣaren u zeg inni xak ijehden, \add inni ɣarsen\add* tineddam timeqqranin nni ttwafaryent ař ajenna,
\v 2 ijj n řgens \add n iwdan\add* izzugarten, ayt n Iɛanaqiyyen inni tessned \add ɛad\add* u x yinni tesřid \add qqaren\add*: ‘Wi ɣa ibedd zzat i wudem n ayt n Iɛanaqiyyen?’ \x ◘ \xo 9:2 \xt Řxř. 13:32,33 \x*
\v 3 Ssen xenni, aqa SIDI, AREBBI nnec, d wenni izwaren zzat i wudem nnec. Netta d ict n tmessi ittetten, Netta ad ten iteḥḥa u ad ten isswaḍeɛ zzat i wudem nnec uca cek ad zzaysen tekksed řwart nsen u ad ten taredǧed deɣya am mammec ɣarek dd-issiweř SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 9:3 \xt Aɛwd. 4:24; Ɛbr. 12:29 \x*
\v 4 Řami SIDI, AREBBI nnec, xasen yuẓẓeř zzatek, \add xenni\add* war qqar deg wuř nnec, ad tinid: ‘SIDI issidef ayi-dd di ssibbet n tsegda inu maḥend ad ksiɣ tammurt-a d řwart’. \add Minzi\add* di ssibbet n tuɛeffna n řegnus-a ad zzaysen ikkes SIDI řwart nsen zzat i wudem nnec.
\v 5 War iǧi di ssibbet n tsegda nnec, war iǧi di ssibbet n řeṣfayet n wuř nnec, ad din traḥed ḥima ad teksid tammurt nsen d řwart, maca di ssibbet n tuɛeffna n řegnus-a u ḥima ad iḥḍa awař nni zi ijjuǧ SIDI, AREBBI nnec, i řejdud nnec, i Ibrahim d Isḥaq d Yaɛqub, ad zzaysen ikkes SIDI, AREBBI nnec, řwart nsen zzat i wudem nnec.” \x ◘ \xo 9:5 \xt Amz. 12:7; 13:15; 15:7; 17:8; 26:4; 28:13 \x*
\b
\m 
\v 6 “S uya i ɣa tessned, belli war iǧi di ssibbet n tsegda nnec i d ac iwca SIDI, AREBBI nnec, tammurt-a icnan maḥend ad tt teksid d řwart, minzi kenniw d ijj n řgens d aɣennan.
\v 7 Idar, war ttᵉttu, belli teggid ad idduqqez weɣḍab n SIDI, AREBBI nnec, di řexřa. Zeg wass nni di teffɣed zi temmurt n Miṣra ařami dd-tudfed ɣar wemcan-a, tuɣa tɣewwɣem kenniw x SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 9:7 \xt Uf. 14:11; 16:2; 17:2; Řxř. 11:4 \x*
\v 8 Minzi di Hurib teggim ad idduqqez weɣḍab n SIDI, ařami xawem isɛar SIDI ařami ixs ad kenniw iteḥḥa. \x ◘ \xo 9:8 \xt Uf. 32:4; Izhd. 106:19\x*
\v 9 Řami uřyeɣ ɣar wedrar ḥima ad ṭṭfeɣ tiřwiḥin n weẓru, tiřwiḥin n Řɛahd nni akidwem igga SIDI, qqimeɣ arebɛin n wussan d ǧyaři deg wedrar. Aɣrum war t cciɣ, aman war ten swiɣ. \x ◘ \xo 9:9 \xt Uf. 24:18; 34:28\x*
\v 10 Iwc ayi SIDI tnayen n teřwiḥin n weẓru urint s uḍaḍ n AREBBI u daysent marra awařen nni tuɣa kiwem issiweř SIDI deg wedrar zi řwesṭ n tmessi deg wass n wegraw \add n řgens\add*. \x ◘ \xo 9:10 \xt Uf. 31:18\x*
\v 11 Imsar ɣar uneggar n arebɛin n wussan d arebɛin n ǧiyaři, řami d ayi iwca SIDI tnayen n teřwiḥin n weẓru, tiřwiḥin n Řɛahd,
\v 12 inna ayi SIDI: ‘Kkar, hwa deɣya ssa, minzi řgens nnec, wenni tnedhed zi Miṣra, aqa iḍeyyeɛ i-t. Weddaren deɣya abrid nni i x ten weṣṣiɣ. Ggin i yixef nsen ijj n řexyař ifesyen.’
\v 13 Issiweř akidi SIDI ɛawed, inna: ‘Necc ẓriɣ řgens-a, uca xzar, netta d ijj n řgens iqseḥ. \x ◘ \xo 9:13 \xt Uf. 32:9; 33:3; 34:9; Aɛwd. 10:16; 31:27; 2 Ij. 17:14\x*
\v 14 Ejj ayi ad ten teḥḥiɣ u ad mḥiɣ isem nsen zi swadday n ujenna, ad cek ggeɣ d ijj n řgens ijehden u imɣar x wanita.’”\x ◘ \xo 9:14 \xt Uf. 32:10; Izhd. 106:23\x*
\m 
\v 15 “Uca dewřeɣ-dd, hwiɣ-dd zeg wedrar. Tuɣa adrar yareqq s tmessi u tuɣa ɣari tnayen n teřwiḥin n Řɛahd di tnayen n ifassen inu.
\v 16 Ẓriɣ, aqa da, kenniw texḍam ak-d SIDI, AREBBI nwem. Teggim i yixef nwem ijj n uɛejmi ifesyen. Kenniw tiggʷejem deɣya x webrid nni x d awem yumur SIDI. \f ◼ \fr 9:16 \fk aɛejmi\ft - niɣ ‘amwa’, ‘ayenduz’ niɣ ‘yuggu’. Uřa di ayet 21.\f*
\v 17 \add Xenni\add* ṭṭfeɣ tnayen n teřwiḥin, nḍareɣ tent zi tnayen n ifassen inu, arẓiɣ tent zzat i tiṭṭawin nwem.
\v 18 Wḍiɣ \add ɣar temmurt\add* zzat i wudem n SIDI am umur amezwaru, arebɛin n wussan d arebɛin n ǧyaři war cciɣ aɣrum u war swiɣ aman di ssibbet n ddnub i teggim umi teggim min iǧan d řɣar di tiṭṭawin n SIDI u umi t tesɛarem.
\v 19 Minzi ggʷedeɣ zeg weɣḍab d wesɛar i zi xawem tuɣa SIDI iffugem u tuɣa ixs ad kenniw iteḥḥa. \add Maca\add* SIDI isřa ayi ɛad twařa-ya.
\v 20 Tuɣa SIDI ɛawed isɛar aṭṭas x Harun ařami tuɣa ixs ad t iteḥḥa. Ẓẓuǧeɣ ɛawed di ṭṭweɛ n Harun di řweqt nni d ijjen.
\v 21 Ddenb nwem, wenni d aɛejmi nni teggim, ksiɣ t uca sscemḍeɣ t di tmessi, ceǧqeɣ t, haryeɣ t mliḥ, ařami idweř d ifsus am tɛejjajt uca nḍareɣ taɛejjact nnes di teɣzart nni dd-ihekkwan zeg wedrar. \x ◘ \xo 9:21 \xt Uf. 32:20\x*
\v 22 Tanya di Tabɛira, di Massa u di Qabarut-Hata’awat tessffugmem SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 9:22 \xt Uf. 17:7; Řxř. 11:1,4,34\x*
\v 23 Uca umi kenniw issekk SIDI zi Qadac-Barniɛ, inna: ‘Ařyem u ṭṭfem tammurt d řwart, \add tammurt\add* nni i d awem wciɣ Necc!’, tuɣa kenniw \add ɛawed\add* tɣewwɣem x \add řumur zeg\add* uqemmum n SIDI, AREBBI nwem, war tuminem, war tesřim i tmijja nnes. \x ◘ \xo 9:23 \xt Řxř. 13:3; 14:1\x*
\v 24 Tuɣa kenniw tɣewwɣem x SIDI zeg wass nni kenniw ssneɣ.
\b
\s1 Taẓaǧit n Musa
\m 
\v 25 Ɣenseɣ ixef inu zzat i wudem n SIDI, \add marra\add* arebɛin n wussan d arebɛin n ǧyaři nni, tuɣa ayi \add din\add* ɣenseɣ zzat i wudem n SIDI, minzi SIDI inna, belli Netta ad kenniw iteḥḥa.
\v 26 Ẓuǧeɣ i SIDI uca nniɣ: ‘\add A\add* Sidi inu, SIDI, war tthellak řgens d řwart nnec, wenni tfekked s řemɣaret nnec, aqa Cek tnedhed ten zi Miṣra s ufus nnec ijehden.\x ◘ \xo 9:26 \xt Uf. 32:11; Řxř. 14:13\x*
\v 27 Idar imsexxaren nnec, Ibrahim, Isḥaq d Yaɛqub, war xezzar ɣar tɣennant n řgens-a uřa ɣar tuɛeffna nnes d ddenb nnes,
\v 28 ḥima, inni \add di\add* temmurt i zi d aneɣ dd-tessuffɣed, war qqaren: Minzi SIDI war izemmar ad ten issidef di temmurt i x tuɣa kisen issawař, u minzi icarh i-ten, aqa issuffeɣ i-ten-dd maḥend ad ten ineɣ di řexřa. \x ◘ \xo 9:28 \xt Uf. 32:12; Řxř. 14:16\x*
\v 29 Aqa nitni d řgens nnec d řwart nnec, wenni dd-tessuffɣed s tzemmar nnec tameqqrant u s uɣiř nnec isswiẓẓḍen!’”
\b
\b
\c 10
\s1 Tnayen n teřwiḥin nneɣni n weẓru
\m 
\v 1 “Di řweqt nni d ijjen inna ayi SIDI: ‘Nqec tnayen n teřwiḥin n weẓru am tinni timezwura uca geɛɛed-dd ɣari ɣar wedrar uca egg i cek ict n Ttabut n ukeccuḍ. \x ◘ \xo 10:1 \xt Uf. 34:1\x*
\v 2 Ad ariɣ di teřwiḥin awařen nni tuɣa di teřwiḥin timezwura nni tarẓid uca ad tent tessarsed di Ttabut.
\v 3 Necc ggiɣ ict n Ttabut n ukeccuḍ n ukasiya uca neqceɣ tnayen n teřwiḥin n weẓru am tmezwura. Geɛɛdeɣ ɣar wedrar s tnayen n teřwiḥin deg ufus inu.
\v 4 Yura x teřwiḥin, anect n tira tamezwarut, ɛecra n wawařen nni tuɣa issiweř SIDI deg wass n wegraw \add n řgens\add* x wedrar zi řwesṭ n tmessi uca iwca i-tent ayi-dd SIDI.
\v 5 Dewřeɣ-dd u hwiɣ-dd zeg wedrar uca ssarseɣ tiřwiḥin di Ttabut nni ggiɣ uca diha i ǧant \add ɛad\add*, am mammec d ayi yumur SIDI.”
\b
\m 
\v 6 Fesyen ayt n Israil iqiḍan nsen zi Biɛrut-Bani-Yaɛqan, ffɣen ɣar Musira. Dinni immut Harun uca ittwanḍeř din. Mmis Aliɛazar idweř d akehhan deg wemcan nnes. \x ◘ \xo 10:6 \xt Řxř. 20:28; 33:30,38\x*
\v 7 Ssenni mmuṭṭiyen ɣar Judjud u zi Judjud ɣar Yuṭbata, tammurt n tɣezratin n waman. \x ◘ \xo 10:7 \xt Řxř. 33:32,33\x*
\v 8 Di řweqt nni d ijjen iḥuzz SIDI taqbič n Lawi ḥima ad arbun Ttabut n Řɛahd n SIDI maḥend ad bedden zzat i wudem n SIDI, ad as sexxaren u ad barken deg Yisem nnes, ař ass-a.
\v 9 X uya Lawi war ɣares tuɣi ca n tesɣart, uřa d ca n řwart ak-d aytmas. SIDI d řwart nnes, am mammec d as inna SIDI, AREBBI nnec. \x ◘ \xo 10:9 \xt Řxř. 18:20-32.; Aɛwd. 18:1; Ḥiz. 44:28 \x*
\b
\m 
\v 10 “Uca necc qqimeɣ x wedrar, am wussan imezwura, arebɛin n ussan d arebɛin n ǧyaři uca isřa ayi SIDI ɛawed twařa-ya, aqa SIDI tuɣa war ixs ad kenniw issexsar. \x ◘ \xo 10:10 \xt Aɛwd. 9:18, 19\x*
\v 11 Inna ayi SIDI: ‘Kkar, uyur deg webrid zzat i wudem n řgens, ḥima ad adfen ɣar temmurt, tenni jjuǧeɣ i řejdud nsen ad asen tt-i-dd-wceɣ, ad tt ksin d řwart.’
\v 12 Řexxu xenni, \add a\add* Israil! Min zzayek ittar SIDI, AREBBI nnec, mɣir ad teggʷeded SIDI, AREBBI nnec, ad tuyured deg ibriden nnes u ad t texsed uca ad tsexxared i SIDI, AREBBI nnec s marra uř nnec u s marra řeɛmar nnec, \x ◘ \xo 10:12 \xt Aɛwd. 6:5; Mt. 22:37; Lk. 10:27\x*
\v 13 uca ad teḥḍid řumurat n SIDI d tweṣṣa nni necc xak carḍeɣ ass-a i tizi nnec.
\v 14 Xzar, ajenna d ujenna n ijenwan d marra min dayes i SIDI, AREBBI nnec i iǧan. \x ◘ \xo 10:14 \xt Amz. 14:19; Izhd. 24:1; 115:16\x*
\v 15 Mɣir ɣar řejdud nnec waha i iqqen SIDI Ixef nnes ḥima ad ten ixs u Netta ixḍar zzariɛet nsen awarni asen, aqa d kenniw, zi marra řegnus, am \add teǧa\add* ass-a.
\v 16 Xetnem xenni i řeɛdařyet n wuř nwem, war sqessiḥem ca ɛad ktar uřawen nwem, \x ◘ \xo 10:16 \xt Uf. 32:9; 33:3; 34:9; Aɛwd. 9:13; 30:6; Irm. 4:4 \x*
\v 17 minzi SIDI, AREBBI nwem, d AREBBI x \add marra\add* irebbiten d Sidi x \add marra\add* isiditen, ijj n Arebbi imɣar d ajebbar d ameggʷed, wenni war itteggen řfarz deg iwdan niɣ ikessi ccarḍ, \x ◘ \xo 10:17 \xt 2 Im. 19:6, 7; Ayub 34:19; Řex. 10:34; Rum. 2:11; Gal. 2:6; Afa. 6:9; Kul. 3:25; 1 Bṭ. 1:17; Asa. 17:14\x*
\v 18 wenni itteggen tasegda i uyujiř d tajjač, wenni ittexsen abarrani u iwca as aɣrum d arruḍ.
\v 19 Ittxeṣṣa ad texsem abarrani, minzi tuɣa kenniw d ibarraniyyen di temmurt n Miṣra.
\v 20 Ad teggʷeded SIDI, AREBBI nnec, ad as tsexxared uca ad as třeṣqed u s Yisem nnes ad tejjaǧed. \x ◘ \xo 10:20 \xt Aɛwd. 6:13; 13:4; Mt. 4:10; Lk. 4:8\x*
\v 21 Aqa Netta d asebbaḥ nnec, uca Netta d AREBBI nnec, wenni ɣarek iggin řxedmet-a d tameqqrant uřa d \add marra\add* timesřayin-a issaggʷaden tinni ẓrint tiṭṭawin nnec.
\v 22 Řejdud nwem hwan-dd s sebɛin n řeɛmur ɣar Miṣra uca řexxu igga i-c SIDI, AREBBI nnec, aṭṭas am yitran n ujenna.” \x ◘ \xo 10:22 \xt Amz. 15:5; 46:27; Uf. 1:5; Řex. 7:14\x*
\b
\b
\c 11
\s1 Řɣiǧet n ṭṭaɛet d řɣiǧet n řmuɛṣiyyet
\m 
\v 1 “Ad texsed SIDI, AREBBI nnec uca ad teḥḍid min \add d ac\add* yumur Netta, tiweṣṣa nnes d lfarayiḍ nnes d řumurat nnes, marra ussan.
\v 2 Ittxeṣṣa ad tessnem ass-a, necc war ssiwřeɣ ak-d iḥenjiren nwem, inni war tt issinen u war ẓrin ttarbiyyet n SIDI, AREBBI nwem, d řemɣaret nnes d ufus nnes ijehden d uɣiř nnes isswiẓẓḍen
\v 3 d řeɛřamat nnes d timegga nnes, tinni igga di řwesṭ n Miṣra, zzat i firɛun, ajeǧid n Miṣra, u zzat i marra tammurt nnes,
\b
\m 
\v 4 ... min igga ak-d řɛeskar n Imiṣriyyen d iysan nsen d ikarruten nsen, mammec d yarra aman n Řebḥar n Telga ad feyyḍen x izeǧifen nsen umi kenniw ḍfaren. Aqa ihellek i-ten SIDI, ař ass-a,
\m 
\v 5 ... d min akidwem igga di řexřa ařami tiwḍem ɣar wemcan-a,
\m 
\v 6 ... d min igga ak-d Datan d Abiram, iḥenjiren n Iliyab, mmis n Rubin, mammec tarzem temmurt aqemmum nnes uca tsarḍ i-ten ak-d raǧ nsen d iqiḍan nsen u ak-d marra inni \add din\add* ibedden, inni ten dd-iḍfaren deg iṣuraf nsen, di řwesṭ n marra Israil. \x ◘ \xo 11:6 \xt Řxř. 16:31; 27:3; Izhd. 106:17\x*
\b
\m 
\v 7 Aqa tiṭṭawin nwem ẓrint marra timegga timeqqranin n SIDI nni tuɣa igga Netta.”
\v 8 \add Xenni\add* ḥḍam marra tiweṣṣa nni i d awem umureɣ ass-a, ḥima ad zzaysent tjehdem uca ad tadfem ɣar temmurt i ɣar ɣa teẓwam, maḥend ad tt tᵉṭṭfem d řwart, uca \add xenni\add* ad tt tᵉṭṭfem d řwart, \x ◘ \xo 11:8 \xt Ɛiz. 9:12\x*
\v 9 u ḥima ad zzugarten wussan nwem x wudem \add n temmurt\add* nni ijjuǧ SIDI i řejdud nwem ad asen tt-i-dd-iwc u i zzariɛet nsen, ict n temmurt ifeyyḍen s uɣi d tamment.
\v 10 Minzi tammurt nni mani tᵉttraḥed ḥima ad tt tᵉṭṭfed d řwart, war teǧi am temmurt n Miṣra manis dd-teffɣem, mani tzarɛed zzariɛet nnec u tenni tesswed s iḍaren nnec am yict n teḥwict tazizawt.
\v 11 Tammurt i ɣar ɣa teẓwam maḥend ad tt tᵉṭṭfem d řwart, aqa-tt d ict n temmurt n idurar d teysarin, tenni isessen aman n wenẓar zeg ujenna,
\v 12 ict n temmurt i x iḥeṭṭa SIDI, AREBBI nnec, i x ǧant řebda tiṭṭawin n SIDI, AREBBI nnec, zi beddu n useggʷas ař aneggar n useggʷas.
\v 13 Mařa tesřim nican i tweṣṣa inu, tinni d awem umureɣ ass-a, ḥima ad texsem SIDI, AREBBI nwem, uca ad as tsexxarem s marra uř nwem u s marra řeɛmar nwem, \add xenni\add* ad imsar,
\v 14 aqa Necc ad wceɣ anẓar di temmurt nwem di řweqt nnes, \add anẓar\add* n zic d uneggar, ḥima ad tessmuned irden nnec d binu nnec n jdid d zzect nnec \add n ṭṭri\add*
\v 15 uca Necc ad ac wceɣ arbiɛ deg iyyar nnec i řebhayem nnec uca cek ad tecced u ad tejjiwned.”
\b
\m 
\v 16 “Ḥḍam war ittwassɣekkʷi wuř nwem uca ad teffɣem \add zeg webrid\add*, ad tɛebdem i irebbiten nneɣni, ad asen tbendqem. \x ◘ \xo 11:16 \xt Aɛwd. 8:19\x*
\v 17 Iři \add xenni\add* ad xawem yareɣ weɣḍab n SIDI uca ad iqqen ijenwan maḥend war iccit wenẓar \add ɛad\add* u war tᵉttic temmurt \add ɛad\add* ṣṣabet nnes u kenniw ad ttwaredǧem deɣya zi temmurt icnan, tenni i d awem ɣa iwc SIDI.
\v 18 S uya ḥḍam awařen-a inu deg wuřawen nwem u di řeɛmar nwem u ad ten tbeysem am yict n řeɛřamet x ufus nwem, ad iřin d ifiřan n useggem x tiṭṭawin nwem \x ◘ \xo 11:18 \xt Aɛwd. 6:6, 8\x*
\v 19 uca sřemdem ten i iḥenjiren nwem am xasen tessawařem xmi ɣa tiřim di tudrin nwem u xmi ɣa tiřid deg webrid u deg yiḍeṣ nnec u xmi ɣa tiřid tfaqed, \x ◘ \xo 11:19 \xt Aɛwd. 4:9; 6:7\x*
\v 20 u arim ten x řeḍruf \add ɣar uɣezdis n tewwart\add* n taddart nnec u x tewwura nnec
\v 21 ḥima ad ktaren wussan nwem d wussan n iḥenjiren nwem x temmurt, tenni min xef ijjuǧ SIDI i řejdud nwem ad asen ten-i-dd-iwc, am wussan n ujenna \add qqimen ktaren\add* sennej i temmurt.
\v 22 Minzi mařa teḥḍam nican marra tawṣeyyet-a nni d awem umureɣ ass-a maḥend ad tt teggem u maḥend ad texsem SIDI, AREBBI nwem, ad tuyurem deg ibriden nnes marra u ad ɣares dd-třeṣqem,
\v 23 \add xenni\add* SIDI ad issuffeɣ marra řegnus-a zzat i wudem nwem uca \add ammu i\add* ɣa twartem tasɣart n řegnus imɣaren d ijehden xawem.
\v 24 Marra amcan nni i ɣa teɛjen třeqqa n uḍar nwem ad yiři nwem. Zi řexřa u zi Lubnan, u zeg iɣzar, iɣzar n Lfuraṭ, ař řebḥar di řɣarb, ad yiři weymir \add n temmurt\add* nnec. \x ◘ \xo 11:24 \xt Yac. 1:3; 14:9\x*
\v 25 War izemmar uřa d ijj ad iqqim ibedd zzat i wudem nwem. SIDI, AREBBI nwem, ad igg tiggʷudi d řɛurret zzaywem x marra tammurt nni i x ɣa tɛejnem, am mammec tuɣa akidwem issiweř.” \x ◘ \xo 11:25 \xt Uf. 23:27\x*
\b
\m 
\v 26 “Xzar, necc ad ggeɣ ass-a \bd lbaraka d nneɛřet\bd* zzat i wudem nwem:
\b
\m 
\v 27 ... lbaraka, mařa ad tesřem i tweṣṣa n SIDI, AREBBI nwem, tinni x d awem umureɣ ass-a,
\m 
\v 28 ... d nneɛřet, mařa war tesřim i tweṣṣa n SIDI, AREBBI nwem, uca ad teggʷejem x webrid i x d awem umureɣ ass-a, x minni i ɣa teḍfarem irebbiten nneɣni i war tessinem ca.
\b
\m 
\v 29 Xmi SIDI, AREBBI nnec, ad cek issidef di temmurt nni i ɣar ɣa traḥed ḥima ad tt tᵉṭṭfed d řwart, \add xenni\add* ad tegged lbaraka x wedrar n Jirizim d nneɛřet x wedrar n Ɛibal. \f ◼ \fr 11:29 \fk ad tegged\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘ad tewcid’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 11:29 \xt Aɛwd. 27:12, 13; Yac. 8:33\x*
\v 30 Ma war ǧin \add idurar nni\add* x ujemmaḍ n L’Urdun, awarni i webrid, manis dd-tneqqar tfuct, di temmurt n ayt n Kenɛan nni izeddɣen di Řewḍa, arendad n Jiljal, zzat i tcejjura n yigg n Mura?
\v 31 Minzi kenniw ad teẓwam L’Urdun ḥima ad \add din\add* tadfem u ḥima ad tᵉṭṭfem tammurt, tenni i d awem ɣa iwc SIDI, d řwart u kenniw ad tt twartem u ad dayes tzedɣem.
\v 32 Ḥḍam \add xenni\add* marra tiweṣṣa d lfarayiḍ nni i d awem ssecneɣ ass-a.”
\b
\b
\c 12
\s1 Amcan iqeddsen
\m 
\v 1 “D tina d tiweṣṣa d lfarayiḍ nni i ɣa teḥḍam maḥend ad tent teggem di temmurt nni i d ac iwca SIDI, AREBBI n řejdud nnec, ḥima ad tt teksid d řwart, marra ussan nni i ɣa teddarem kenniw x wudem n temmurt.
\m 
\v 2 Ad tareddǧem qaɛ marra imucan mani tuɣa sexxaren řegnus i irebbiten nsen, \add marra imucan\add* nni i ɣa teṭṭfem d řwart: x idurar yuɛřan, x tewririn u sadu kuř tacejjart tazizawt. \f ◼ \fr 12:2 \fk tacejjart\ft - niɣ ‘addag’ (‘iddagen’).\f*  \x ◘ \xo 12:2 \xt Uf. 34:12, 13; Aɛwd. 7:5\x*
\v 3 Ad tenḍarem iɛalṭaren nsen, ad tarẓem imayḍuten nsen \add iqeddsen\add* u tirebbin nsen n cwarti ad tent tesscemḍem s tmessi uca ad thedmem řexyařat ineqcen n irebbiten nsen uca ad temḥam isem nsen zeg wemcan nni. \x ◘ \xo 12:3 \xt Řqḍ. 2:2\x*
\v 4 \add Minzi ammu\add* war tɛebbdem i SIDI, AREBBI nwem am \add tteggen nitni\add*,
\v 5 maca ad tarzum x wemcan nni i ɣa yixḍar SIDI, AREBBI nwem, zi jar marra tiqebbař nwem, ḥima ad din igg Isem nnes, \add wah,\add* ɣar Tzeddiɣt nnes i ɣa tarzum u din i ɣa tawḍem \x ◘ \xo 12:5 \xt 2 Im. 7:12\x*
\v 6 uca dinni i ɣa tawyem tiɣarṣa nwem n wecmaḍ d tɣarṣa nwem d řeɛcur nwem d tewhibt nni issgeɛɛed ufus nwem d tewhibin nwem s řxaḍar d imenza n ifunasen d tfunasin nwem d \add imenza\add* n wuǧi nwem,
\v 7 uca dinni i ɣa teccem zzat i wudem n SIDI, AREBBI nwem, ad tfarḥem, kenniw d \add řaǧ n\add* tudrin nwem, zi marra min igga ufus nwem u zi min di kenniw ibarek SIDI, AREBBI nnec.
\v 8 War tteggem am marra min nᵉttegg neccin da ass-a: kuř aryaz \add ittegg\add* min d as ittwařa nican di tiṭṭawin nnes.
\v 9 Minzi aqa \add ɛad\add* řexxu war tudifem ca ɣar arraḥet u ɣar řwart nni d awem iwca SIDI, AREBBI nnec.
\v 10 Xmi ɣa teẓwam L’Urdun uca ad tzedɣem di temmurt nni d awem ɣa iwc SIDI, AREBBI nwem, d řwart, Netta ad awem iwc arraḥet zi marra řɛedyan nwem i d awem dd-innḍen uca ad tzedɣem di řaman.
\v 11 Din i ɣa yiři wemcan nni i ɣa yixḍar SIDI, AREBBI nwem, ḥima ad issezdeɣ din Isem nnes uca dinni i ɣa tawyem marra min x cek umureɣ: tiɣarṣa n wecmaḍ nwem, tiɣarṣa nwem, řeɛcur nwem, tiwhibin n usgeɛɛed n ufus nwem d marra \add tiwhibin\add* n lwaɛd nni i ɣa tweɛdem i SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 12:11 \xt 1 Ij. 8:29\x*
\v 12 Ad tfarḥem zzat i wudem n SIDI, AREBBI nwem, kenniw d iḥenjiren nwem d tḥenjirin nwem d isemɣan nwem d tiyya nwem d Ulawi nni izeddɣen daxeř i tewwura nwem, minzi war ɣares tasɣart niɣ řwart akidwem. \x ◘ \xo 12:12 \xt Řxř. 18:20; Aɛwd. 10:9; 18:1\x*
\v 13 Ḥḍa war ssbexxara tiɣarṣa nnec n wecmaḍ di min ma amcan nni twařid,
\v 14 maca \add waha\add* deg wemcan nni i ɣa yixḍar SIDI deg icten zi tqebbař nnec, dinni \add waha\add* i ɣa tessbexxared tiɣarṣa n wecmaḍ uca dinni i ɣa tegged marra min d ac umureɣ.
\b
\s1 Tawṣeyyet x idammen u ḍidd i weɛbed n l’aṣnam n řegnus
\m 
\v 15 S marra tzemmared ad tɣarṣed daxeř i tewwura nnec marra min immeẓri wuř nnec uca ad \add zzayes\add* tecced ɛlaḥsab lbaraka nni d ac ɣa iwc SIDI, AREBBI nnec, daxeř i tewwura nnec. Amexmuj d umezdag zemmaren ad zzayes ccen, axmi \add ttetten zeg\add* iɣayḍ n wezɣar u \add zeg\add* udad.
\v 16 Mɣir idammen war ten tᵉttetted. Ad ten tneɣřed x temmurt am waman. \x ◘ \xo 12:16 \xt Amz. 9:4; Lawi 7:26; 17:10; Aɛwd. 15:23\x*
\v 17 War iɛeddeř ad tecced daxeř i tewwura nnec zi řeɛcur n irden d binu nnec n jdid d zzect nnec \add n ṭṭri\add* uřa zeg imenza n ifunasen d tfunasin d wuǧi nnec niɣ zi tewhibin n wawař i tewcid niɣ zi tewhibin s řxaḍar niɣ zi tewhibt nni issgeɛɛed ufus nnec.
\v 18 Minzi ad ten tecced zzat i wudem n SIDI, AREBBI nnec, deg wemcan nni ɣa yixḍar SIDI, AREBBI nnec, cek, mmic, yeǧic, ismeɣ nnec, tayya nnec d Ulawi nni izeddɣen daxeř i tewwura nnec uca ad tfarḥed zzat i wudem n SIDI, AREBBI nnec, di marra min ɣar ɣa isswiẓẓed ufus nnec.
\v 19 Ḥḍa, war semmeḥ \add ɣar uzeǧif nnes\add* Alawi di marra ussan nnec x temmurt nnec.”
\b
\m 
\v 20 “Xmi SIDI, AREBBI nnec, ad issiyru aymir \add n temmurt\add* nnec, am mammec d ac inna, uca ad tinid: ‘Xseɣ ad cceɣ aysum’, minzi immeẓri řeɛmar nnec ad yecc aysum, \add xenni\add* ad tecced aysum anect n marra min imeẓri řeɛmar nnec. \f ◼ \fr 12:20 \fk issiyru\ft - niɣ ‘iwesseɛ’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 12:20 \xt Amz. 9:4; Lawi 7:26; 17:10; Aɛwd. 15:23\x*
\v 21 Mařa tuɣa cek tiggʷejed x wemcan nni i ɣa yixḍar SIDI, AREBBI nnec, ḥima ad din issemten Isem nnes, \add xenni\add* tzemmared ad tɣarṣed zeg ifunasen d tfunasin nnec u zeg wuǧi nnec nni d ac iwca SIDI, am mammec cek umureɣ, uca ad zzayes tecced daxeř i tewwura nnec anect n marra min dayes immeẓri řeɛmar nnec.
\v 22 Am mammec ittwacc iɣayḍ n wezɣar d udad, amenni i zzayes ɣa tecced. Amexmuj d umezdag zemmaren ad zzayes ccen.
\v 23 Mɣir war ttᵉtt ɛemmarṣ zeg idammen, minzi idammen d řeɛmar. War ttᵉtt řeɛmar ak-d weysum.
\v 24 War ten tᵉttᵉtted, \add maca\add* ad ten tneɣřed x temmurt am waman.
\v 25 War ten tᵉttᵉtted, ḥima ad tiřid cek mliḥ d iḥenjiren nnec awarni ac, xmi ɣa tegged min iseggden zzat i tiṭṭawin n SIDI.
\v 26 Ad tawyed mɣir timesřayin nni ɣarek qeddsent d \add tɣarṣa n\add* lwaɛd nnec uca ad \add kidsent\add* dd-tased ɣar wemcan i ɣa yixḍar SIDI
\v 27 uca ad tesswejded tiɣarṣa n wecmaḍ, aysum nnes d idammen nnes, x uɛalṭar n SIDI, AREBBI nnec, uca idammen n tɣarṣa ad ttwazeǧɛen x uɛalṭar n SIDI, AREBBI nnec, \add maca\add* iɛeddeř ad tecced aysum.
\v 28 Ḥḍa, u seř i marra awařen-a nni d ac umureɣ, ḥima ad tiřid mliḥ, cek d iḥenjiren nnec awarni ac i řebda, umi ɣa tegged min icnan d min iseggden di tiṭṭawin n SIDI, AREBBI nnec.”
\b
\m 
\v 29 “Xmi ɣa iteḥḥa SIDI, AREBBI nnec, řegnus mani ɣa traḥed ḥima ad ten teksid d řwart uca \add xenni\add* cek ad ten teksid d řwart uca ad tzedɣed di temmurt nsen,
\v 30 ḥḍa maḥend war tḍeffared awarni asen di řfex d ict, awarni ma ad ttwateḥḥan zzat i wudem nnec, uca ad tarzud x irebbiten nsen, ad tinid: ‘Am mammec sexxaren nitni i irebbiten nsen, ammu i ɣa ggeɣ uřa d necc.’
\v 31 War ttegg amenni i SIDI, AREBBI nnec, minzi marra min iǧan d jjɛifect i SIDI d min icarreh Netta, aqa ggin t nitni i irebbiten nsen. Ɛad sscemḍen iḥenjiren nsen d yessitsen di tmessi i irebbiten nsen.”
\b
\b
\c 13
\s1 X inabiyyen issxarriqen u x weɛbed n l’aṣnam
\m 
\v 1 “Marra awař nni x kenniw weṣṣiɣ, ad t teḥḍam ad zzayes teggem. War ɣares arenni u war zzayes ttekkes. \x ◘ \xo 13:1 \xt Aɛwd. 4:2; Awřn. 30:6; Asa. 22:18\x*
\m 
\v 2 Mařa ikkar ijj n unabi niɣ ijj n umerji n tirja di řwesṭ nnec uca igga ca n řeɛřamet niɣ s ca n lmuɛjiza ɣarek,
\v 3 uca řeɛřamet nni niɣ lmuɛjiza nni x d ac issiweř temsar uca \add xenni\add* inna: ‘Ejj ad nuyur awarni i irebbiten nneɣni!’, inni war tessined, uca: ‘Ejj aneɣ ad asen neɛbed!’,
\v 4 \add xenni\add* war ttesři i wawařen n unabi nni niɣ n umerji n tirja nni, minzi SIDI, AREBBI nwem, ittqeǧab kenniw, ḥima ad issen ma tᵉttexsem SIDI, AREBBI nwem s marra uř nwem u s marra řeɛmar nwem.
\v 5 Ad tuyurem awarni i SIDI, AREBBI nwem, ad zzayes teggʷdem, ad tᵉṭṭfem di tweṣṣa nnes, ad tesřem i tmijja nnes, ad as tsexxarem u ad dayes třeṣqem. \x ◘ \xo 13:5 \xt Aɛwd. 10:20\x*
\v 6 Ittxeṣṣa ad ittwaneɣ unabi nni niɣ umerji nni n tirja, minzi issiweř x řaggʷajet x webrid n SIDI, AREBBI nwem - wenni kenniw issuffɣen zi temmurt n Miṣra, d wenni cek ifdin zi taddart n tesmuɣi - maḥend ad cek issuffeɣ zeg webrid nni x yumur SIDI, AREBBI nnec, ad \add dayes\add* tuyured. Ittxeṣṣa ad tekksed řɣar zi řwesṭ nnec. \f ◼ \fr 13:6 \fk ifdin\ft - xzar Izhd. 78:35.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 13:6 \xt Aɛwd. 18:20; Irm. 14:15\x*
\m 
\v 7 Mařa umac, mmis n yemmac, niɣ mmic niɣ yeǧic niɣ tamɣart n wuř nnec niɣ ameddukkeř nnec nni i iǧan am řeɛmar nnec, ad cek iɣar s tnuffra ad yini: ‘Ejj aneɣ ad nuyur ad nsexxar i irebbiten nneɣni!’ inni war tessined ca cek uřa d řejdud nnec, \x ◘ \xo 13:7 \xt Aɛwd. 17:2\x*
\v 8 inni iǧan zeg irebbiten n řegnus i d ac-dd innḍen, inni yudsen niɣ inni xak iggʷejen zi ṭṭarf n temmurt ař ṭṭarf nneɣni,
\v 9 \add xenni\add* war xas ttegg ca, war ɣares ttesři ca. War t areḥḥem ca, war d ac izziǧiz ca niɣ ad t teffared,
\v 10 maca ittxeṣṣa ad t tenɣed nican. Afus nnec ad xas yiři d amezwaru, maḥend ad t tenɣed u xenni \add ad xas yiři\add* ufus n řgens marra. \x ◘ \xo 13:10 \xt Aɛwd. 17:7\x*
\v 11 Ad t tḥejjarem s yeẓra ař ɣa immet, minzi tuɣa yarezzu ad cek issiggʷej x SIDI, AREBBI nnec, wenni i cek dd-issuffɣen zi temmurt n Miṣra, zi taddart n tesmuɣi.
\v 12 Marra Israil ad sřen uca ad ggʷeden, \add ařami\add* war dd-dikkʷiřen ad ggen řɣar-a di řwesṭ nnec.” \x ◘ \xo 13:12 \xt Aɛwd. 17:13\x*
\b
\m 
\v 13 “Mařa tesřid aqa qqaren deg icten zi tneddam nni i d awem ɣa iwc SIDI ḥima ad daysent tzedɣed:
\v 14 ‘Aqa ffɣen-dd zi řwesṭ nwem yeryazen, ayt i war isekkwin, uca ssɣekkwan imezdaɣ n tendint nsen, qqaren: Ejj ad nraḥ ad neɛbed irebbiten nneɣni, inni war tessinem!’,
\v 15 \add xenni\add* ad tarzud u ad tesseqsid mliḥ, u xzar, mařa tufid tamesřact nni tbedd x tidett, aqa jjɛifect nni tᵉttwagg di řwesṭ nnec,
\v 16 \add řexdenni\add* ad tegged ict n tecti i imezdaɣ n tendint s řeqḍeɛ n ssif. Ad tt tḥarrmed i uteḥḥi s marra min dayes, uřa d řebhayem nnes, s řeqḍeɛ n ssif.
\v 17 Ad tessmuned marra takeccaḍt nnes ɣar řwesṭ n wazzay nnes, ad tessecmeḍ tandint s tmessi ak-d marra takeccaḍt i dayes, i SIDI, AREBBI nnec, uca ad tedweř \add tendint\add* d ict n řxarbet i řebda, ɛemmarṣ ad tᵉttwabna ɛawed.
\v 18 War ttejji min ittwaḥarrmen \add i uteḥḥi\add* ad iqqim iřeṣṣeq jar ifassen nnec, ḥima SIDI ad \add xak\add* issiggʷej řḥaduq n weɣḍab nnes uca ad ac iwc arreḥmet, ad cek yarḥem ad cek yarni, am mammec ijjuǧ i řejdud nnec,
\v 19 xmi ɣa tesřed ɣar tmijja n SIDI, AREBBI nnec, ḥima ad teḥḍid marra tiweṣṣa nnes, tinni i x d ac weṣṣiɣ ass-a, u ḥima ad tegged min iseggden di tiṭṭawin n SIDI, AREBBI nnec.”
\b
\b
\c 14
\m 
\v 1 “Kenniw d iḥenjiren n SIDI, AREBBI nwem. War xebbcem ca x \add arrimet\add* nwem, war tqeccarem ca jar tiṭṭawin nwem di ssibbet n ijj n umettin. \x ◘ \xo 14:1 \xt Lawi 19:27, 28; 21:5\x*
\v 2 Minzi aqa cek d ijj n řgens iqeddes ɣar SIDI, AREBBI nnec, uca SIDI ifarz cek ḥima ad as tiřid d řgens iɣřan zi marra řegnus i iǧan x temmurt. \x ◘ \xo 14:2 \xt Aɛwd. 7:6; 26:18\x*
\s1 X macca d wagřa
\m 
\v 3 War ttett zi kuřci min iǧan d jjɛifect.
\v 4 Aqa d ina d \bd imuddaren i iɛeddeř ad ten teccem\bd*: afunas, ijjen zeg iḥuřiyyen, ijjen zeg iɣayḍen, \x ◘ \xo 14:4 \xt Lawi 11:2\x*
\v 5 udad, iɣayḍ n wezɣar, izerzer, iɣayḍ ak-d waccawen imeqqranen, amellal, afunas n řexřa d iɣayḍ n idurar. \f ◼ \fr 14:5 \fk iɣayḍ n wezɣar\ft - niɣ ‘azenkud’. \fk amellal\ft - niɣ ‘amrur’ niɣ ‘acamul’.\f*
\m 
\v 6 Iɛeddeř ad teccem marra řmař i ɣar iǧa třeqqa n \bd tecḍect immsebḍan\bd*, tacḍect immsebḍan x tnayen, \bd u\bd* \add sennej i man aya\add* \bd ttarran ifeẓ\bd* jar řmař.
\v 7 Maca zeg inni ittarran ifeẓ d yinni i ɣar teǧa tecḍect immsebḍan qaɛ x tnayen, \bd war iɛeddeř ad teccem ina\bd*: \bd ařɣem\bd*, d \bd uyarziz\bd* d \bd ukawka n teṣḍart\bd* minzi tteffẓen, \add maca\add* war ɣarsen bu tecḍect immsebḍan, u \add xenni\add* ad ɣarwem iřin xemjen.
\v 8 \add Ammu uřa d\add* \bd iřef\bd*, waxxa ɣares tacḍect immsebḍan, war ittarri ifeẓ, \add s uyenni\add* ad ɣarwem yiři ixmej. War ttᵉttem ca zeg weysum nnes, war ttḥadam ca řxecbat nsen.
\m 
\v 9 Iɛeddeř ad teccem ina zi marra min iǧan \bd deg waman: marra wi ɣar iǧa wafriwen d teqcurt\bd* iɛeddeř ad ten teccem.
\v 10 \add Maca\add* marra min war ɣar ǧin wafriwen niɣ taqcurt, war iɛeddeř ad ten teccem, ad ɣarwem iřin xemjen.
\m 
\v 11 \bd Marra ijḍaḍ izdigen iɛeddeř ad ten teccem\bd*,
\v 12 \add maca\add* \bd war iɛeddeř ad zzaysen teccem ina\bd*: agider, isɣi, agider n řebḥar,
\v 13 bu-řxeẓrat d amesɣuy \add amuqḍiɛ n tiṭṭawin\add* d bu-umeṭṭaw s tazřa ak-d marra markat nnes, \x ◘ \xo 14:13 \xt Lawi 11:14\x*
\v 14 marra markat n ubaɣeř,
\v 15 yeǧis n buheyyaf, aɛennaf, ajḍiḍ n řebḥar, řbaz ak-d markat nnes, \x ◘ \xo 14:15 \xt Lawi 11:16\x*
\v 16 \add aḥemmař n\add* řkas, bu-usuḍi \add n řmewt\add*, bu-yuntaḥ,
\v 17 bu-uɛuqqi, bu-uḥawař, bu-tcararrut,
\v 18 abellarj, bu-usuḍi iɛeffnen ak-d markat nnes, dundun d řweḍwaḍ.
\m 
\v 19 \bd Marra min ɣar iǧa wafriwen nni ittbuɛen ad ɣarwem yiři ixmej\bd*. War iɛeddeř ad ttwaccen.
\v 20 Marra ijḍaḍ izdigen iɛeddeř ad ten teccem.
\m 
\v 21 War iɛeddeř ad teccem uřa zeg ict n řxecbet. Ad tt tewced i ubarrani nni \add iǧan\add* daxeř i tewwura nnec, ḥima ad zzayes yecc, niɣ ad tt tezzenzed i ubarrani, minzi cek d ijj n řgens d amqeddas i SIDI, AREBBI nnec.”
\b
\m “War snenni iɣayḍ d ameẓyan deg uɣi n yemmas.” \x ◘ \xo 14:21 \xt Uf. 23:19; 34:26\x*
\b
\m 
\v 22 \bd Ad tɛeccared\bd* nican marra řɣiǧet n zzariɛet nni ittejja iyyar nnec zeg useggʷas ɣar useggʷas \add nneɣni\add*.
\v 23 Ad tecced řeɛcur n irden nnec, n binu nnec n jdid, n zzect nnec \add n ṭṭri\add*, uřa n imenza n řebhayem nnec u n wuǧi nnec zzat i wudem n SIDI, AREBBI nnec, deg wemcan i ɣa yixḍar Netta maḥend ad din izemmem Isem nnes, ḥima ad třemded ad teggʷeded SIDI, AREBBI nnec kuř ass. \x ◘ \xo 14:23 \xt Aɛwd. 12:17, 18\x*
\v 24 Mařa abrid izzuggart xak aṭṭas, ař ɣa tafed war tzemmared ad tawyed \add řeɛcur\add* din, minzi amcan nni yixḍar SIDI, AREBBI nnec, ḥima ad din izemm Isem nnes, iǧan iggʷej xak aṭṭas, \add uca\add* mařa \add xenni\add* SIDI, AREBBI nnec ibarek i cek,
\v 25 qřeb i-ten \add xenni\add* d \add tmenyat n\add* nnuqart uca uyur s tkemmust n tmenyat deg ufus nnec ɣar wemcan nni i ɣa yixḍar SIDI, AREBBI nnec, \f ◼ \fr 14:25 \fk takemmust\ft - niɣ ‘tacemmust’.\f*
\v 26 ad tṣarfed tmenyat nni x marra min di immeẓri wuř nnec, x ifunasen d tfunasin, x wuǧi, x binu, x ccrab niɣ x min ma ixs wuř nnec uca ad tecced din zzat i wudem n SIDI, AREBBI, ad tfarḥed, cek d \add řaǧ n\add* taddart nnec.” \x ◘ \xo 14:26 \xt Mt. 21:12\x*
\m 
\v 27 “War semmeḥ ca di Alawi nni izeddɣen ɣar daxeř i tewwura nnec, minzi war ɣares bu tasɣart niɣ řwart akidek. \x ◘ \xo 14:27 \xt Řxř. 18:20, 24; Aɛwd. 10:9; 12:12; 18:1, 2; 26:12\x*
\v 28 Ɣar uneggar n třata n iseggʷusa ad tessuffɣed marra řeɛcur n řɣiǧet deg useggʷas nni uca ad ten txezned jar daxeř n tewwura nnec.
\v 29 \add Xenni\add* Alawi ad dd-yas, minzi war ɣares teǧi tesɣart niɣ řwart akidek, uřa d abarrani d uyujiř d tajjač nni iǧan ɣar daxeř i tewwura nnec uca ad ccen, ad jjiwnen, ḥima \add xenni\add* SIDI, AREBBI nnec, ad ac ibarek di marra řxedmet i ɣa tegged s ufus nnec.”
\b
\b
\c 15
\m 
\v 1 “\bd Ɣar uneggar n sebɛa n iseggʷusa ad yiři ijj n wesmaḥ n imerwusa.\bd* \x ◘ \xo 15:1 \xt Uf. 21:2; Irm. 34:14\x*
\v 2 Ta d tamesřact n ufekki zeg imerwusa: kuř bab n umarwas, wenni yareḍřen zeg ufus nnes i jjar nnes, ad \add as\add* isemḥ i umarwas. War ittettar ca amarwas zeg jjar nnes uřa zeg umas, minzi ittwabarreḥ s ufekki n imerwusa i SIDI.
\v 3 Iɛeddeř ad třaɣid abarrani x umarwas, \add maca\add* min iǧan nnec ɣar umac, \add d man aya\add* ad dayes ismeḥ ufus nnec.
\v 4 Aqa war ittxeṣṣi ca ad ɣarek yiři uřa d ijj n umezřuḍ, minzi SIDI ad cek ibarek aṭṭas di temmurt nni i d ac ɣa iwc, SIDI, AREBBI nnec, d tasɣart i ɣa twarted,
\v 5 mařa \add xenni\add* tesřid s teynit ɣar tmijja n SIDI, AREBBI nnec, ḥima ad teḥḍid uca ad tegged marra tiweṣṣa-ya, tinni x d ac weṣṣiɣ ass-a.
\v 6 Minzi SIDI, AREBBI nnec, ad ac ibarek am mammec tuɣa d ac inna, uca aṭṭas n řegnus ad xak arḍřen s weḍman, maca cek war tareṭṭřed walu s weḍman \add x uřa d yijjen zzaysen\add*. Cek ad tḥekmed x waṭṭas n řegnus, maca nitni war xak ḥekkmen ca.”
\b
\m 
\v 7 “Xmi \add din\add* ɣarek ɣa yiři ijj n umezřuḍ, ijj zeg aytmac, ɣar daxeř i yict zi tewwura n temmurt nnec nni i d ac ɣa yewc SIDI, AREBBI nnec, \add xenni\add* war sseqsaḥ ca uř nnec u war ttzeyyar ca afus nnec x umac nni izeřḍen,
\v 8 maca ad as tarzmed afus nnec s wecrim u ad as tareḍřed s weḍman, ɛlaḥsab min iḥwaj deg uzeyyar nnes.
\v 9 Ḥḍa, war ittiři deg wuř nnec uřa d ijj n uxarriṣ baṭeř, teqqared \add deg yixef nnec\add*: ‘Aqa yudes-dd useggʷas wiss sebɛa, aseggʷas n ufekki n imerwusa!’, uca \add xenni\add* ad texzared s tiṭṭawin ixeyyqen x umac nni i di iǧa zzeřḍ uca war d as tᵉtticed walu u netta ad zzayek icetca ɣar SIDI uca ad xak yiři ddenb.
\v 10 Ittxeṣṣa ad as tewced deɣya, war ittiři uxeyyeq deg wuř nnec xmi i d as ɣa tewced, minzi x uya ad ac ibarek SIDI, AREBBI nnec, di marra řxedmet nnec u di marra mani ɣa yaweḍ ufus nnec. \x ◘ \xo 15:10 \xt Mt. 5:42; Lk. 6:35\x*
\v 11 Minzi ameẓřuḍ war ittwameḥḥi zi temmurt. X uya necc umureɣ cek, qqareɣ: Arzem afus nnec ař ṭṭarf i umac, i wenni ittwaḥṣaren u i umezřuḍ nni \add iǧan\add* di temmurt nnec.” \x ◘ \xo 15:11 \xt Mt. 26:11; Yḥ. 12:8\x*
\b
\m 
\v 12 \bd “Mařa umac\bd*, ijj n Uɛibrani niɣ ict n Tɛibranect, \bd ittwazzenz ɣarek\bd*, \add xenni\add* ad ac ixdem setta n iseggʷusa, \add maca\add* deg useggʷas wiss sebɛa ad as tsarrḥed ad as tarxud zi ɣarek s třelli. \x ◘ \xo 15:12 \xt Uf. 21:2; Irm. 34:14\x*
\v 13 Xmi i d as ɣa tsarrḥed, \add xenni\add* war t ttejji ad iraḥ s \add ifassen\add* xwan.
\v 14 \add Axmi\add* d as ɣa tegged tiseddect \add ammu i d as ɣa tegged ict n tewhibt\add* zeg wuǧi u zeg unedrar u zi tsirt \add n uḍiř\add*. S min d ac ibarek SIDI, AREBBI nnec, ad as tewced i netta.
\v 15 Ad tidared belli tuɣa cek d ismeɣ di temmurt n Miṣra uca SIDI, AREBBI nnec, aqa ifdi xak. X uya, necc umureɣ cek tiweṣṣa-ya ass-a. \f ◼ \fr 15:15 \fk ifdi\ft - xzar Izhd. 78:35.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 15:15 \xt Aɛwd. 10:19; 16:12; 24:18; 24:22; Uf. 22:20; 23:9; Lawi 19:34. \x*
\v 16 Mařa netta inna ac: ‘War xak ttaggʷjeɣ!’, minzi ittexs i cek d \add řaǧ n\add* taddart nnec, minzi aqa netta mliḥ ɣarek,
\v 17 xenni ad teksid ijj n usiyni uca ad tessnuqqeb amezzuɣ nnes uřa d tewwart uca \add ammu i\add* ɣa yiři d ismeɣ nnec i řebda u ammu i ɣa tegged \add ɛawed\add* s tayya nnec. \x ◘ \xo 15:17 \xt Uf. 21:6\x*
\v 18 War dd-ittbin iqseḥ di tiṭṭawin nnec, xmi t ɣa tessekked di třelli, minzi tuɣa isexxar i cek setta n iseggʷusa, yarebbeḥ i cek řexřaṣ n ijj n ucewwař tnayen n tseqqar. \add Ammu\add* i cek ɣa ibarek SIDI, AREBBI nnec, di marra min ɣa tegged.”
\b
\m 
\v 19 \bd “Ad tessqeddsed i SIDI, AREBBI nnec, marra imenza iwetman\bd* nni dd-ittwaxeřqen jar ifunasen d tfunasin nnec d wuǧi nnec. War iɛeddeř ad tessxedmed amenzu n ifunasen nnec uca amenzu n wuǧi nnec war t tteǧas. \x ◘ \xo 15:19 \xt Uf. 13:2; 22:29; 34:19; Lawi 27:26; Řxř. 3:13\x*
\v 20 Aseggʷas awarni i useggʷas ad ten tecced, cek d \add řaǧ n\add* taddart nnec, zzat i wudem n SIDI, AREBBI nnec, deg wemcan i ɣa yixḍar SIDI.
\v 21 Maca mařa tuɣa dayes řɛib, tuɣa-t d aqidar niɣ d adarɣař niɣ min ma řɛib aɛeffan \add i ɣares iǧan\add*, war d as ɣarreṣ ca i SIDI, AREBBI nnec.\x ◘ \xo 15:21 \xt Lawi 22:20; Aɛwd. 17:1\x*
\v 22 Daxeř i tewwura nnec ad zzayes tecced, am umexmuj am umezdag, am mammec \add i ɣa tecced\add* zeg iɣayḍ n wezɣar u zeg udad.
\v 23 Mɣir idammen nnes, war ten ttᵉtt ca, ad ten tfarrɣed x temmurt am waman.” \x ◘ \xo 15:23 \xt Aɛwd. 12:16, 23\x*
\b
\b
\c 16
\s1 Řeɛyudat
\m 
\v 1 “Ḥḍa ayur n Abib, ad tesswejded \bd \bdit Taɣarṣt\bdit* n Useɛdu\bd* i SIDI, AREBBI nnec, minzi deg uyur n Abib issuffeɣ i cek-dd SIDI, AREBBI nnec, zi temmurt n Miṣra s ǧiřet. \x ◘ \xo 16:1 \xt Uf. 12:2; Lawi 23:5; Řxř. 9:1; 28:16\x*
\v 2 Ad tɣarṣed i \add Taɣarṣt n\add* Useɛdu i SIDI, AREBBI nnec, uǧi d ifunasen d tfunasin deg wemcan nni i ɣa yixḍar SIDI, maḥend ad din issezdeɣ Isem nnes.
\v 3 War kis ttᵉtt ca s wentun. Sebɛa n wussan ad kis tecced aɣrum břa antun, aɣrum n tamara, minzi deɣya teffɣed zi temmurt n Miṣra, ḥima ad tɛeqřed x wass i dd-tteffɣed zi Miṣra marra ussan n tudart nnec. \x ◘ \xo 16:3 \xt Uf. 12:19; 34:18\x*
\v 4 War kik ittemẓar wentun di marra jjihet nnec sebɛa n wussan uca zeg weysum nni i tɣarṣed ɣar uɛecci n wass amezwaru, war ittnusi ca ař tiwecca nnes. \x ◘ \xo 16:4 \xt Uf. 12:10, 13:7, 23:18, 34:25\x*
\v 5 War iḥeǧeř ad tɣarṣed i \add Tɣarṣṭ n\add* Useɛdu ɣar daxeř i yict n tewwura \add n tneddam\add* i d ac ɣa yewc SIDI, AREBBI nnec,
\v 6 maca deg wemcan nni i ɣa yixḍar SIDI, AREBBI nnec, ḥima ad din issizdeɣ Isem nnes, din i ittxeṣṣa ad tɣarṣed i \add Tɣarṣt n\add* Useɛdu ɣar uɛecci xmi ɣa teɣři tfuct di tsaɛɛet nni di teffɣed zi Miṣra.
\v 7 Uca ad tt tessengʷed ad tt tecced deg wemcan nni i ɣa yixḍar SIDI, AREBBI nnec. Ɣar ṣṣbeḥ \add awarni as\add* ad tɛeqbed uca ad traḥed ɣar iqiḍan nnec.
\v 8 \bd Setta n wussan ad tecced aɣrum břa antun\bd* uca deg wass wiss sebɛa ad yiři ijj n umuni ifarzen i SIDI, AREBBI nnec. \add Xenni\add* war iḥeǧeř ad tegged uřa d ict n řxedmet \add i ittxeṣṣa ad tᵉttwagg\add*.”
\m 
\v 9 “Ad tḥesbed sebɛa n ssimanat i yixef nnec. Zeg wami \add i ɣa tebdid ad tegged\add* amjar deg imendi ibedden, ad tebdid ad tḥesbed sebɛa n simanat. \x ◘ \xo 16:9 \xt Uf. 23:16; Lawi 23:15; Řxř. 28:26\x*
\v 10 \add Xas uca\add* ad tegged \bd Řɛid n Ssimanat\bd* i SIDI, AREBBI nnec. Ad tewced ict n ṣṣedqet s řxaḍar zeg ufus nnec am mammec cek ibarek SIDI, AREBBI nnec.
\v 11 Ad tfarḥed zzat i wudem n SIDI, AREBBI nnec, cek, mmic, yeǧic, ismeɣ nnec, tayya nnec, Alawi nni \add ittɣiman\add* daxeř i tewwura nnec, abarrani, ayujiř d tajjač nni iǧan di řwesṭ nnec, deg wemcan nni i ɣa yixḍar SIDI, AREBBI nnec, ḥima ad din issezdeɣ Isem nnes.
\v 12 Ad tɛeqřed belli tuɣa cek d ismeɣ di Miṣra uca ittxeṣṣa ad teḥḍid tiweṣṣa-ya u ad ten tegged.”
\b
\m 
\v 13 “Ad tɛeyyded \bd Řɛid n Iɛuccuten\bd* sebɛa n wussan, xmi tkemmřed asmuni n ṣṣabet n unedrar nnec d uẓemmi n tsirt nnec \add n uḍiř\add*. \x ◘ \xo 16:13 \xt Uf. 23:16; Lawi 23:34\x*
\v 14 Uca ad tfarḥed di Řɛid nnec, cek, mmic, yeǧic, ismeɣ nnec, tayya nnec, Alawi, abarrani, ayujiř d tajjač nni \add ittɣiman\add* daxeř i tewwura nnec.
\v 15 Sebɛa n wussan ad tɛeyyded i SIDI, AREBBI nnec, deg wemcan nni i ɣa yixḍar SIDI, minzi SIDI, AREBBI nnec, ad cek ibarek di marra řɣiǧet nnec u di marra řxedmet n ifassen nnec uca ad tfarḥed s tidett!”
\b
\m 
\v 16 \bd “Třata n twařawin deg useggʷas\bd* ad dd-banen marra iwetman nnec zzat i wudem n SIDI, AREBBI nnec, deg wemcan nni i ɣa yixḍar Netta: di Řɛid n Weɣrum břa Antun, di Řɛid n Ssimanat, di Řɛid n Iɛuccuten. War dd-ittbin uřa d ijj \add s ifassen\add* xwan zzat i wudem n SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 16:16 \xt Uf. 23:15, 17;34:23\x*
\v 17 Kuř aryaz \add ad iwc\add* am mammec d as immewcen deg ufus nnes, anect n lbaraka i d ac iwca SIDI, AREBBI nnec.
\b
\s1 X řeḥkamet
\m 
\v 18 Ad tfarned řquḍat d imeḥḍayen ɣar daxeř i tewwura nni d ac ɣa iwc SIDI, AREBBI nnec, jar \add marra\add* tiqebbař nnec. Nitni ad ḥekmen \add jar\add* řgens s ict n řeḥkamet iseggden.
\v 19 War tteffeɣ ca x webrid n tidett, war ttegg s wudmawen \add xmi ɣa tḥekmed\add*. War ttᵉṭṭef ca arrecwet, minzi arrecwet tessdarɣař tiṭṭawin n yinni iḥekkmen u tessfarraɣ awařen n yinni iqqaren tidett. \x ◘ \xo 16:19 \xt Uf. 23:8; Lawi 19:15; Aɛwd. 1:17\x*
\v 20 Tasegda \add uca ɛawed\add* tasegda ad teḍfared, ḥima ad teddared uca ad twarted tammurt nni i d ac ɣa iwc SIDI, AREBBI nnec.
\b
\s1 Aɛřam ɣar řgens x weɛbed n l’aṣnam
\m 
\v 21 \bd War ttegg ca tarebbit n cwarti\bd* zi ca n tcejjart zzat i uɛalṭar n SIDI, AREBBI nnec, wenni ɣa tegged. \f ◼ \fr 16:21 \fk tacejjart\ft - niɣ ‘addag’ (‘iddagen’).\f*
\v 22 War ssgeɛɛad ameyḍa \add iqeddsen\add* i yixef nnec, minzi d man aya icarreh SIDI, AREBBI nnec.”
\b
\b
\c 17
\m 
\v 1 “\bd War ɣarreṣ ca i ufunas niɣ i yijjen zeg wuǧi i di iǧa ca n řɛib\bd*, \add niɣ\add* ca n řmař iɛeffnen, i SIDI, AREBBI nnec, minzi man aya d jjɛifect i SIDI, AREBBI nnec. \x ◘ \xo 17:1 \xt Lawi 22:20-25; Aɛwd. 15:21\x*
\m 
\v 2 Umi yufa di řwesṭ nnec, ɣar daxeř i tewwura nnec, tinni d ac iwca SIDI, AREBBI nnec, ca n weryaz niɣ ca n temɣart i iggin min iǧan d řɣar di \add tiṭṭawin n\add* SIDI, AREBBI nnec, \add uca ammu\add* i ɣa iɛeddu x Řɛahd nnes, \x ◘ \xo 17:2 \xt Aɛwd. 13:7\x*
\v 3 uca ad yuyur, ad iɛbed i irebbiten nneɣni uca ad asen ibendeq, i tfuct niɣ i yuyur niɣ i marra itran n ujenna, min war xef umureɣ necc,
\v 4 uca yiweḍ i cek-dd řexbar uca tesřid \add tt\add*, \add xenni\add* ittxeṣṣa ad tt tarzud mliḥ, u xzar, mařa d tidett uca tban belli tᵉttwagg di Israil jjɛifect tanita,
\v 5 \add xenni\add* ad tessuffɣed aryaz nni niɣ tamɣart nni i iggin řɣar-a ɣar tewwura nnec, aryaz nni niɣ tamɣart nni, uca ad ten tḥejjared s iẓra ař ɣa mmten.”
\m 
\v 6 “X \add wawař zeg\add* uqemmum n tnayen niɣ třata n řechud ad ittwaneɣ wenni ittwaḥkem s řmewt. X \add wawař zeg\add* uqemmum n ijj n ucehhad war iḥeǧeř ad ittwaneɣ. \x ◘ \xo 17:6 \xt Řxř. 35:30; Aɛwd. 19:15; Mt. 18:16; 2 Kur. 13:1; Ɛbr. 10:28\x*
\v 7 Afus n řechud ad xas wḍan d amezwaru maḥend ad t nɣen uca awarni as \add ad xas wḍan ifassen\add* n marra řgens. Ammu i ɣa tekksed řɣar zi řwesṭ nnec.”\x ◘ \xo 17:7 \xt Aɛwd. 13:10\x*
\m 
\v 8 “Xmi xak ɣa teqseḥ ca n tmesřact di lḥukm jar \add usizzeř n\add* idammen d \add usizzeř n\add* idammen \add nneɣni\add*, jar ddeɛwet d ddeɛwet, jar ticti d tecti, \add niɣ di lḥukm deg\add* imcubbac ɣar daxeř i tewwura nnec, \add xenni\add* ad tekkared, ad tgeɛɛded ɣar wemcan nni ɣa yixḍar SIDI, AREBBI nnec.\x ◘ \xo 17:8 \xt 2 Im. 19:10; Mal. 2:7\x*
\v 9 Uca ad dd-tawḍed ɣar ikehhanen, ɣar Ilawiyyen, uca \add xenni\add* ɣar řqaḍi nni din iǧan deg wussan nni, uca ad tesseqsid u nitni ad cek xebbaren x řeḥkam.
\v 10 Ad tegged am tenfuč nni i cek ɣa xebbaren deg wemcan nni i ɣa yixḍar SIDI uca ad teḥḍid marra min d ac ɣa sseɛdun.
\v 11 Ad tegged ɛlaḥsab awař n Ccariɛa nni d ac ɣa seccnen u ɛlaḥsab řeḥkam nni d ac ɣa inin. War ttḥeyyid x wawař i d ac ɣa inin \add ɣar\add* yefus uřa \add ɣar\add* uzeřmaḍ.
\v 12 Aryaz nni itteggen s tuffet u war ittesři ɣar ukehhan nni \add i din\add* ibedden, ḥima ad din isexxar SIDI, AREBBI nnec, niɣ \add war ittesři\add* ɣar řqaḍi, aqa aryaz nni ad immet. Ittxeṣṣa ad tekksed řɣar zi Israil.
\v 13 Marra řgens ittxeṣṣa asen ad sřen u ad ggʷeden u war ttuffen ɛad.”
\b
\s1 X ujeǧid
\m 
\v 14 “Xmi ɣa tadfed ɣar temmurt nni i d ac ɣa iwc SIDI, AREBBI nnec uca ad tt tᵉṭṭfed d řwart uca ad dayes tzedɣed u \add xenni\add* ad tinid: ‘Ad xafi ggeɣ \bd ijj n ujeǧid\bd* am marra řegnus i d ayi dd-innḍen!’,
\v 15 \add xenni\add* ad xak tegged d ajeǧid wenni i ɣa yixḍar SIDI, AREBBI nnec. Zi řwesṭ n aytmac ad tegged d ijj n ujeǧid xak, war xak ttegg ca abarrani i war iǧin ca d umac.
\v 16 Maca war iḥeǧeř ad yarni iysan i ixef nnes u war ittarri ca řgens ɣar Miṣra maḥend ad yarni iysan, \add minzi\add* SIDI inna awem: Zi ssa d tsawent war dd-tɛiqqibem ɛemmarṣ x webrid-a!
\v 17 War ikessi ca i ixef nnes aṭṭas n temɣarin, ḥima war ittɣarri wuř nnes. War yarenni ca i yixef nnes nnuqart niɣ ureɣ s waṭṭas.
\v 18 Xmi ɣa iqqim x řɛarc n tgeldit nnes, \add xenni\add* ad yari i yixef nnes ict n uɛawed n tira n Ccariɛa-ya deg ijj n wedlis ittwannḍen zzat i wudem n ikehhanen, Ilawiyyen.
\v 19 Ad ɣares yiři \add uɛawed n tira-ya\add*, ad dayes iɣar marra ussan n tudart nnes, ḥima ad iřmed ad iggʷed SIDI, AREBBI nnes, ad iḥḍa marra awařen n Ccariɛa-ya d tweṣṣa-ya uca ad zzaysent igg,
\v 20 ḥima war issiřiy uř nnes x yaytmas niɣ ad iḥeyyed x webrid n tewṣeyyet, \add war iǧi\add* \add ɣar\add* yefus uřa \add ɣar\add* uzeřmaḍ, maḥend ad izzugart ussan n tgelda nnes, netta d warraw nnes, di řwesṭ n Israil.”
\b
\b
\c 18
\s1 Řmunet n ikehhanen d Ilawiyyen
\m 
\v 1 “War tᵉttiři tesɣart niɣ řwart ak-d Israil i ikehhanen, Ilawiyyen, i marra taqbič n Lawi. Ad ccen tiɣarṣa n wecmaḍ n SIDI u zi teṣɣart nnes. \x ◘ \xo 18:1 \xt Řxř. 18:20; Aɛwd. 10:9; 1 Kur. 9:13\x*
\v 2 War ɣares ittiři d řwart di řwesṭ n aytmas. SIDI d řwart nnes, am mammec d as inna. \x ◘ \xo 18:2 \xt Řxř. 18:20-32.; Aɛwd. 10:9; Ḥiz. 44:28\x*
\v 3 Man aya ad yiři d tasɣart n řḥeqq n ikehhanen qibač i řgens, qibač i yinni iṣeddqen ict n tɣarṣt, ma d afunas niɣ ijjen zeg wuǧi: ad wcen i ukehhan tameṣṣaḍt n zzat, tnayen n iɣesmiren d tekrict.
\m 
\v 4 Asuffuɣ amezwaru \add n ṣṣabet\add* n irden nnec u zi binu n jdid nnec u zi zzect nnec \add n ṭṭri\add* u tamezwarut n waǧas zi \add taḍuft n\add* wuǧi nnec, ad as tewced.
\v 5 Minzi yixḍar i-t SIDI, AREBBI nnec zi jar marra tiqebbař nnec, ḥima ad ikkar, ad isexxar di ṭṭweɛ n Yisem n SIDI, netta d arraw nnes, marra ussan.
\v 6 Xmi dd ɣa yas Ulawi zeg ijjen zi tewwura nnec zi marra Israil, mani izeddeɣ \add am ubarrani\add*, uca yusa-dd s marra řxaḍar nnes ɣar wemcan i ɣa yixḍar SIDI
\v 7 uca ad isexxar \add dinni\add* deg Yisem n SIDI, AREBBI nnes, am marra aytmas, Ilawiyyen, inni din ibedden zzat i wudem n SIDI,
\v 8 \add xenni\add* ad ccen nitni tasɣart anect n wayawya, barra i \add ttaman n\add* min immenzen zeg \add min iǧan nnes\add* ɛlaḥṣab \add jjadira nnes n taddart n\add* řejdud.”
\b
\s1 Aɛřam ɣar řgens x tgezzant
\m 
\v 9 “Xmi ɣa tadfed ɣar temmurt nni i d ac ɣa yewc SIDI, AREBBI nnec, war sseřmad ca i yixef nnec ad tegged am jjɛayef n řegnus-a.
\v 10 War ittwiffi ḥed jar awem wenni i ɣa isseɛdun mmis niɣ yeǧis x tmessi niɣ wenni \add iǧan\add* d aɛezzem, \add niɣ\add* abezgaw, \add niɣ\add* amegzu, \add niɣ\add* aseḥḥar, \x ◘ \xo 18:10 \xt Lawi 18:21; 20:27; 1 Ṣm. 28:7; Ica. 8:19\x*
\v 11 \add niɣ\add* wenni itteggen tira, \add niɣ\add* wenni issawařan ak-d imettan \add niɣ\add* wenni ittgezzan uřa d wenni yarezzun ccwar zeg imettan.
\v 12 Minzi marra wenni itteggen timesřayin-a, aqa-t d jjɛifect ɣar SIDI u zi ssibbet n jjɛayef-a ad zzaysen ikkes SIDI, AREBBI nnec, řwart nsen zzat i wudem nnec.
\v 13 \add Maca\add* cek ad tiřid d addud zzat i SIDI, AREBBI nnec.
\v 14 Minzi řegnus nni i ɣa twarted s uɣiř, ad sřen i ibezgawen d iɛezzamen, maca cek, war d ac isemmeḥ SIDI, AREBBI nnec, \add ad tegged\add* aya.”
\b
\s1 X unabi
\m 
\v 15 “Ad ac igg SIDI, AREBBI nnec, ijj n unabi zi řwesṭ nnec, zeg aytmac, am necc, i netta umi ɣa tesřem, \x ◘ \xo 18:15 \xt Yḥ. 1:46; Řex. 3:22; 7:37\x*
\v 16 \add minzi d man aya\add* am mammec marra min tᵉttared zi SIDI, AREBBI nnec, di Ḥurib deg wass n wegraw \add n řgens\add*, umi tennid: ‘War dd-ddikkwiřeɣ necc ad sřeɣ i tmijja n SIDI, AREBBI inu, uca war ẓarreɣ necc ɛad timessi-ya imɣaren, \add ḥima\add* war ttmettiɣ.’ \x ◘ \xo 18:16 \xt Uf. 20:19; Aɛwd. 5:25; Ɛbr. 12:19\x*
\v 17 \add Xenni\add* inna ayi SIDI: ‘Aqa ggin mliḥ umi kik ssiwřen marra aya.’
\v 18 Ad asen dd-ssekkeɣ ijj n unabi zi řwesṭ n aytmatsen, am cek, uca necc ad ggeɣ awařen inu deg uqemmum nnes uca netta ad awem issiweř x marra min xef d as weṣṣiɣ. \x ◘ \xo 18:18 \xt Yḥ. 4:25\x*
\v 19 Uca ad imsar, ad ttareɣ řeḥsab zeg weryaz nni war isřin i wawařen inu i ɣa issiweř s Yisem inu.
\v 20 Maca anabi nni i ɣa yuffen ḥima ad issiweř ijj n wawař s Yisem inu, wenni necc war umureɣ ca ad zzayes issiweř, d wenni i ɣa issiwřen s yisem n irebbiten nneɣni, aqa anabi nni ad immet. \x ◘ \xo 18:20 \xt Aɛwd. 13:6, Irm. 14:14\x*
\v 21 Mařa teqqared deg wuř nnec: ‘Mammec ɣa negg ad nessen aqa SIDI war issiweř awař nni?’,
\v 22 \add xenni ittxeṣṣa ad tessnem,\add* xmi anabi nni tuɣa issawař s Yisem n SIDI uca \add xenni\add* awař nnes war imsar u war dd-iffiɣ, aqa awař nni war d as ittwanna zi ɣar SIDI. Anabi nni issawař s uɛeffar. War zzayes tteggʷed ca.”
\b
\b
\c 19
\s1 Třata n tneddam n tarewřa
\m 
\v 1 “Xmi SIDI, AREBBI nnec, ɣa iteḥḥa řegnus i zzaysen d ac ɣa iwc, SIDI, AREBBI nnec, tammurt uca \add xenni\add* ad teksid řwart nsen uca ad tzedɣed di tneddam nsen u di tudrin nsen,
\v 2 \add xenni\add* ittxeṣṣa cek ad tḥuzed i yixef nnec \bd třata n tneddam\bd* di řwesṭ n temmurt i d ac ɣa iwc SIDI, AREBBI nnec, maḥend ad tt teksid d řwart. \x ◘ \xo 19:2 \xt Uf. 21:13; Řxř. 35:9-34; Yac. 20:2\x*
\v 3 Ad tɛedřed ijj n webrid uca tammurt, tenni d ac ɣa iwc SIDI, AREBBI nnec, d řwart, ad tt tebḍid x třata n tseqqar. Man aya ḥima kuř aqettař izemmar ad din yarweř.
\m 
\v 4 D wa d amtawi i zi iɛeddeř i uqettař maḥend ad din yarweř, ḥima ad \add iqqim\add* iddar: mařa inɣa jjar nnes břa ma ad as igg řeḥsab, u tuɣa war t icarreh ca iḍennaḍ d fariḍennaḍ.” \x ◘ \xo 19:4 \xt Uf. 21:13; Aɛwd. 4:41,42\x*
\m 
\v 5 “Wenni iruḥen ak-d jjar nnes ɣar wezɣar ḥima ad iqess ticejjura uca isswiẓẓeḍ afus nnes s ccaqur ḥima ad iḥarwec tacejjart uca \add xenni\add* iffeɣ as wuzzař n ccaqur uca iřqef jjar nnes uca wanita immut, aqa wanita izemmar ad yarweř ɣar icten zi n tneddam-a maḥend ad \add iqqim\add* iddar. \f ◼ \fr 19:5 \fk azɣar\ft - niɣ ‘řɣabet’ niɣ ‘tazgant’.\f*
\v 6 Ammu war izemmar uneqqam n idammen, xmi ɣa iɣeřɣeř wuř nnes, ad iḍfar aqettař uca ad xas iḥart, mařa abrid d azirar uca ad t ineɣ am war xas iǧi řeḥkam s řmewt, minzi tuɣa war t icarreh, \add war iǧi\add* iḍennaḍ \add uřa d\add* fariḍennaḍ.
\v 7 X uya necc umureɣ cek, qqareɣ: ‘Ḥuz třata n tneddam i yixef nnec.’
\v 8 Uca mařa SIDI, AREBBI nnec ad iwesseɛ tammurt nnec, am mammec ijjuǧ i řejdud nnec, u ad ac iwc marra tammurt i x inna ad tt iwc i ibabaten nnec, \x ◘ \xo 19:8 \xt Amz. 28:13; Aɛwd. 12:20\x*
\v 9 - mařa ad teḥḍid marra tawṣeyyet-a maḥend ad tt tegged am mammec d ac umureɣ ass-a ḥima ad texsed SIDI, AREBBI nnec, uca ad tuyured deg ibriden nnes i řebda - xenni ad tarnid ɛad třata n tneddam ɣar třata-ya, \x ◘ \xo 19:9 \xt Yac. 20:7\x*
\v 10 ḥima war ttwassizřen idammen imezdagen di řwesṭ n temmurt nnec, tenni i d ac ɣa iwc SIDI, AREBBI, d řwart uca ad xak yiři ddenb.
\m 
\v 11 \add Maca\add* mařa ca n weryaz icarh jjar nnes uca iqabeř i-t uca ikkar ɣares u \add xenni\add* igga as ict n tecti uca immut, xenni yarweř ɣar icten zi tneddam nni, \x ◘ \xo 19:11 \xt Amz. 9:6; Uf. 21:12, 14; Lawi 24:17; Řxř. 35:16\x*
\v 12 \add xenni\add* ad ssekken imɣaren n tendint nnes, ad t ksin t zeg wemcan nni, ad t ggen deg ifassen n uneqqam n idammen uca ad immet.
\v 13 War d ac izziǧiz, \add maca\add* ad temḥid zi Israil idammen n wenni war iggin ddenb ḥima ad tiřid mliḥ.”
\b
\m 
\v 14 “War smuṭṭiy \bd aymir n jjar nnec,\bd* wenni neyycen řejyuř \add n qbeř\add* di tesɣart nnec, tenni i ɣa twarted di temmurt i d ac ɣa iwc SIDI, AREBBI nnec, ḥima ad tt tᵉṭṭfed. \x ◘ \xo 19:14 \xt Awřn. 22:28\x*
\b
\s1 X řechud di řmeḥkama
\m 
\v 15 Ijj n ucehhad \add waha\add* war izemmar ad ikkar \add d acehhad\add* x ca n weryaz di ssibbet n ca n řmuɛṣiyyet niɣ di ca n ddenb nni izemmar ad ittwagg. X \add wawař zeg\add* uqemmum n \bd tnayen\bd* niɣ x \add wawař zeg\add* uqemmum n \bd ṭrata n řechud\bd* ad tᵉttwaḍmen tmesřact. \x ◘ \xo 19:15 \xt Řxř. 35:30; Aɛwd. 17:6; Mt. 18:16; Yḥ. 8:17; 2 Kur. 13:1; Ɛbr. 10:2\x*
\v 16 Xmi ɣa ikkar ijj n ucehhad aqṭaṭɛiy x ca n weryaz ḥima ad zzayes icetca x ca n ddenb,
\v 17 \add xenni\add* ad bedden tnayen n yeryazen, inni ittemmcubbucen zzat i wudem n SIDI, zzat i wudem n ikehhanen d řquḍat nni i din ɣa yiřin deg wussan nni.
\v 18 Uca řquḍat ad arzun mlih \add di tmesřact\add*, u aqa, mařa acehhad d ijj n ucehhad issxarriqen, ad iched s řbaṭeř x umas,
\v 19 \add xenni\add* ad zzayes teggem am mammec tuɣa ittxarreṣ ad igg netta ak-d umas. \add Ammu\add* i ɣa tekksed řɣar zi řwesṭ nnec, \x ◘ \xo 19:19 \xt Awřn. 19:5\x*
\v 20 ḥima inni iqqimen ad sřen, ad ggʷeden, war ddikkʷiren ad ggen řḥajjet taɛeffant di řwesṭ nnec.
\v 21 War d ac izziǧiz: řeɛmar s řeɛmar, tiṭṭ s tiṭṭ, tiɣmest s teɣmest, afus s ufus, aḍar s uḍar.” \x ◘ \xo 19:21 \xt Uf. 21:23; Lawi 24:20; Mt. 5:38\x*
\b
\b
\c 20
\s1 Izerfan i garra
\m 
\v 1 “Mařa teffɣed ɣar umenɣi ak-d řɛedyan nnec uca teẓrid iysan d ikarruten, ijj n řgens ktar zzayek, war zzaysen tteggʷed ca, s minzi SIDI, AREBBI nnec, wenni cek dd-issuffɣen zi temmurt n Miṣra, aqa-t akidek.
\v 2 Xmi ɣa tadsem i umenɣi, ad dd-iqarreb ukehhan uca ad issiweř ɣar řgens,
\v 3 ad asen yini: ‘Seř, Israil, kenniw qarrbem-dd ass-a ɣar umenɣi ak-d řɛedyan nwem. War ssemẓayem uř nwem, war tteggʷdem niɣ ad tarjijem, niɣ \add ɛawed\add* ad tqefqifem zzat i wudem nsen,
\v 4 minzi SIDI, AREBBI nwem, Netta aqa ad kiwem yuyur ḥima ad xawem immneɣ zzat i řɛedyan nwem maḥend ad kenniw issenjem.’
\v 5 Uca imeḥḍayen ad ssiwřen ak-d řgens ad inin: ‘Wi ibnan taddart n jdid uca war dayes izdiɣ ɛad? Ejj i-t ad yuyur, ad dd-idweř ɣar taddart nnes, ḥima war ittmetti deg umenɣi uca ad dd-yas ḥed nneɣni ad dayes izdeɣ.
\v 6 Wi yeẓẓun tizayarin uca war iɣebbi ɛad zi řɣiǧet nnes? Ejj i-t ad yuyur, ad dd-idweř ɣar taddart nnes, ḥima war ittmetti deg umenɣi uca ad zzayes iɣebba ḥed nneɣni. \x ◘ \xo 20:6 \xt Lawi 19:23, 24, 25\x*
\v 7 Wi ixeḍben tamɣart u war tt imřic ɛad? Ejj i-t ad yuyur, ad dd-idweř ɣar taddart nnes, ḥima war ittmetti deg umenɣi uca ad tt yawi weryaz nneɣni. \x ◘ \xo 20:7 \xt Aɛwd. 24:5\x*
\v 8 Imeḥḍayen ad arnin deg wawař ak-d řgens, ad inin: ‘Wi iǧan d aryaz d amaggʷad niɣ ittɣaca? Ejj i-t ad yuyur, ad dd-idweř ɣar taddart nnes, ḥima war tteɣnisen wuřawen n aytmas am wuř nnes.’ \x ◘ \xo 20:8 \xt Řqḍ. 7:3\x*
\v 9 Xmi ɣa kemmřen imeḥḍayen awař ak-d řgens, xenni ad ggen ikumandaren n řɛeskar ɣar uzeǧif n řgens.”
\b
\m 
\v 10 “Xmi ɣa tadsed ca n tendint ḥima ad kides temmenɣed, ittxeṣṣa ad as třaɣid i weṣřaḥ.
\v 11 Mařa tarra-dd xak s weṣřaḥ, \add xenni\add* marra řgens nni dayes ittwaf, ad cek isexxar s uɣiř uca ad cek ixdem.
\v 12 Mařa war kik teggi řehna, maca d amenɣi i tarezzu, \add xenni\add* ad as tennḍed.
\v 13 SIDI, AREBBI nnec, ad ac tt iwc i cek deg ufus nnec u marra \add min iǧan d\add* awtem dayes, ad t tewted s řeqḍeɛ n ssif.
\v 14 Mɣir timeṭṭa d iḥenjiren d řebhayem d marra min dayes di tendint, marra takeccaḍt nnes, ad tt teksid i yixef nnec d tkeccaḍt uca ad tecced zi tkeccaḍt n řɛedyan nnec, inni d ac iwca SIDI, AREBBI nnec.
\v 15 Amenni i ɣa tegged di marra tineddam nni xak iggʷejen aṭṭas, tinni war iǧin zi tneddam n řegnus-a.
\m 
\v 16 Maca tineddam n řegnus nni d ac iwca SIDI, AREBBI nnec, d řwart, war zzaysent tejjid uřa d ca min ɣa yarren nnefs ad iqqim iddar. \x ◘ \xo 20:16 \xt Řxř. 33:52; Aɛwd. 7:1, 2\x*
\v 17 Ad tent tḥarrmed i uteḥḥi: Iḥittiyyen, Imuriyyen, ayt n Kenɛan, Ifiriziyyen, Iḥiwiyyen d Iyabusiyyen, am mammec i d ac yumur SIDI, AREBBI nnec,
\v 18 ḥima nitni war d awem ssřemmaden ad teḍfarem marra jjɛayef nni ggin nitni i irebbiten nsen uca \add xenni\add* ad texḍam ak-d SIDI, AREBBI nwem.
\m 
\v 19 Mařa tennḍed i yict n tendint aṭṭas n wussan řami temmenɣed akides maḥend ad tt tᵉṭṭfed, \add xenni\add* war ttareddaǧ ca ticejjura s teyyita n ccaqur, minzi ad zzaysent tecced. S uya war tent ttqessid, minzi ma tacejjart n yeyyar am bnadem nni dd-ittbanen zzat i wudem nnec umi teḥṣared \add tandint\add*? \f ◼ \fr 20:19 \fk tacejjart\ft - niɣ ‘addag’ (‘iddagen’).\f*
\v 20 Mɣir tacejjart nni tessned war teǧi d tacejjart i zi ɣa tecced, aqa tanita ad tt taredǧed, ad tt tqessed, ad \add zzayes\add* tebnid ijj n ssur x tendint nni akidek ittmenɣan, ař ɣa tɣeḍřed \add tandint nni\add*.”
\b
\b
\c 21
\s1 Aneqqi zeg ijjen i war ittwassnen
\m 
\v 1 “Mařa ittwaf ḥed ittwaneɣ di temmurt nni d ac ɣa iwc SIDI, AREBBI nnec, maḥend ad tt tᵉṭṭfed d řwart, izzeř deg iyyar uca war issin ḥed wi t inɣin,
\v 2 \add xenni\add* imɣaren nnec d řquḍat nnec ad dd-ffɣen uca ad ksin řeɛbar ař tineddam i d as dd-innḍen i wenni ittwanɣen.
\v 3 Zi tendint nni yudsen i wenni ittwanɣen, ad zzayes ksin yemɣaren ict n tɛejmit n tfunasin nni ɛemmarṣ war zzayes crizen ca u tenni war ijbiden ɛad azayřu.
\v 4 Uca imɣaren n tendint nni ad ssehwan taɛejmit \add nni\add* ɣar ict n teɣzurt \add ittazřen\add* řebda \add s waman\add*, ɛemmarṣ war tᵉttwacarz u war tᵉttwaẓẓu uca ad arẓen iri n tɛejmit din di teɣzurt.
\v 5 \add Xenni\add* ad dd-qarrben ikehhanen, ayt n Lawi, minzi SIDI, AREBBI nnec, ixḍar i-ten maḥend ad xas sexxaren u maḥend ad barken s Yisem n SIDI, u ɛlaḥsab awař nsen \add ad ittwaḥkem\add* kuř amcubbec d kuř řexcunet.
\v 6 Uca marra imɣaren n tendint nni yudsen x wenni ittwanɣen, ad ssirden ifassen nsen sennej i tɛejmit nni umi ittwarẓ yiri di teɣzurt.
\v 7 Ad barrḥen, ad inin: ‘Ifassen nneɣ war ssizzřen ca idammen-a u tiṭṭawin nneɣ war t ẓrin.
\v 8 Egg aṣřaḥ i řgens nnec Israil nni tefdid, \add a\add* SIDI, uca war ssrusa idammen imezdagen di řwesṭ n řgens nnec Israil!’ \add Xenni\add* idammen \add ittwassizřen\add* nni ad ttwaḥesben d řefdiyyet i nitni.
\v 9 Ammu i ɣa tekksed idammen imezdagen zi řwesṭ nnec, minzi ittxeṣṣa ad tegged min iǧan nican di tiṭṭawin n SIDI.”
\b
\s1 Tamɣart ittwaḥebbsen di garra
\m 
\v 10 “Xmi ɣa teffɣed ɣar umenɣi ak-d řɛedyan nnec uca SIDI, AREBBI nnec, igga ac ten deg ifassen nnec uca tiyed ten d imeḥbas,
\v 11 uca teẓrid jar imeḥbas ict n temɣart, tecna deg waddud, uca temmeẓred ad tt teksid d tamɣart i yixef nnec,
\v 12 \add xenni\add* ad tt tessidfed ɣar taddart nnec uca ad tḥeff azeǧif nnes, ad tqessed iccaren nnes.
\v 13 Ad tekkes arruḍ n tmeḥbast nnes uca ad teqqim di taddart nnec uca ad tesɣuy i babas d yemmas ijj n uyur ikmeř u awarni man aya tzemmared ad xas tadfed uca ad tiřid d aryaz nnes u nettat ad tiři d tamɣart nnec.
\v 14 Uca mařa war d ac teɛjib, ad tt tejjed ad tuyur ɣar řxaḍar nnes, war tt znuzi s nnuqart. War zzayes tegged axmi sseřɛet \add i teǧa\add*, minzi aqa tesseḥqared tt.” \f ◼ \fr 21:14 \fk ɣar řxaḍar nnes\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘ɣar řeɛmar nnes’.\f*
\b
\s1 Řḥeqq n umenzu
\m 
\v 15 “Mařa aryaz ɣares tnayen n temɣarin, icten ittexs i-tt, tenneɣnit icarreh i-tt, uca tenni icarreh d tenni ittexs urwent as-dd iḥenjiren, maca amenzu tuɣa-t n tenni icarreh,
\v 16 \add xenni\add* deg wass nni i di ɣa ibḍa řwart n min ɣares iǧan i iḥenjiren nnes, war izemmar ad iwc tasɣart n umenzu i mmis n tenni ittexs deg wemcan i ɣa iwc i mmis n tenni icarreh, \add wenni d\add* amenzu \add i yeǧa\add*.
\v 17 Ittxeṣṣa ad inɛem s mmis amenzu n tenni icarreh umi d as ɣa iwc tnayen n tseqqar zi marra min d as dd-ikkaren, minzi netta d amezwar n teryast nnes u tasɣart n tmenzut nnes i teǧa.” \x ◘ \xo 21:17 \xt Amz. 49:3; 1 Im. 5:1; Izhd. 78:51\x*
\b
\s1 Mmis aɣennan
\m 
\v 18 “Mařa ijj n weryaz ɣares mmis d aɣennan d amɣewweɣ nni war ittesřin i wawař n babas niɣ i wawař n yemmas, uca nitni wtint t, \add maca\add* netta war d asen ittesři,
\v 19 \add xenni\add* babas d yemmas ad t ksin uca ad t awyen barra zzat i imɣaren n tendint nnes, ɣar tewwart n wemcan \add mani izeddeɣ\add*.
\v 20 Ad inin i imɣaren n tendint: ‘Wa d mmitneɣ d aɣennan d amɣewweɣ, war ittesři i wawař nneɣ, aqa afus nnes innuqqeb u netta d ameskar.’
\v 21 \add Xenni\add* marra iryazen n tendint ad t arejmen ař ɣa immet. Ittxeṣṣa ad tekksed aɛeffan zi řwesṭ nwem \add ḥima\add* marra Israil ad tseř uca ad teggʷed.”
\b
\s1 Anḍeř n wenni xas řḥukm n řmewt
\m 
\v 22 “Mařa ijj n weryaz igga ijj n ddenb i x \add iǧa\add* řḥukm n řmewt uca ittwaneɣ, tuyřed i-t x ict n teḥnact \add n ukeccuḍ\add*,
\v 23 \add xenni\add* war ttejjim řxecbet nnes ad tessens x teḥnact, maca ad t tneḍřed deg wass nni, minzi wenni ittwayřen aqa-t d amenɛuř zi AREBBI. War sxemmaj tammurt nnec, tenni d ac ɣa iwc SIDI, AREBBI nnec, d řwart.” \x ◘ \xo 21:23 \xt Gal. 3:13\x*
\b
\b
\c 22
\s1 Tiweṣṣa nneɣni
\m 
\v 1 “War iɛeddeř ad txezzared \add waha\add* deg uweddar n ufunas niɣ n ijjen zeg wuǧi n umac, niɣ ad xasen tqeřbed tiṭṭawin, maca ittxeṣṣa ad ac ten-i-dd-tarred nican i umac. \x ◘ \xo 22:1 \xt Uf. 23:4\x*
\v 2 Mařa umac war iǧi ca yudes niɣ war t tessined, ad t tessidfed ɣar daxeř i taddart nnec uca ad ɣarek iqqim ař dd ɣa yas umac ad xas yarzu uca \add xenni\add* ad as \add t-i-\add*dd tarred.
\v 3 Amenni i ɣa tegged s weɣyuř nnes, amenni i ɣa tegged \add ɛawed\add* s warruḍ nnes, \add wah,\add* ammu i ɣa tegged ak-d marra tamesřact n umac, tenni d as iweddaren uca tufid tt cek. War iɛeddeř ad as tennufared. \f ◼ \fr 22:3 \fk War iɛeddeř ad as tennufared\ft - d man aya ixs ad yini ‘War iɛeddeř ad as tenkared aɛawen nnec’.\f*
\v 4 War \add teqqimed\add* ad texzared deg weɣyuř n umac niɣ deg ufunas nnes am wḍan deg webrid, war xasen qeǧeb ca tiṭṭawin. S tidett ad ten tessekkared akides.”
\b
\m 
\v 5 “Tamɣart war tyarreḍ min ittřiqen i weryaz, niɣ aryaz ad yarḍ arruḍ n temɣart, minzi marra wi itteggen aya aqa-tt d jjɛifect i SIDI, AREBBI nnec.
\m 
\v 6 Mařa iban-dd zzat i wudem nnec x webrid ca n řɛucc n wejḍiḍ, di ca n tcejjart niɣ x temmurt, \add s\add* iwarruden niɣ \add s\add* tmeǧařin, uca yemmatsen tessdeř x iwarruden niɣ x tmeǧařin, \add xenni\add* war ttᵉṭṭef yemmatsen ak-d iwarruden. \f ◼ \fr 22:6 \fk tacejjart\ft - niɣ ‘addag’ (‘iddagen’).\f*
\v 7 Ad tejjed ad tuyur yemmatsen, maca ad teksid iwarruden i yixef nnec, ḥima ad tiřid mliḥ, uca ad ac zuggarten wussan \add n tudart\add* nnec.
\m 
\v 8 Xmi ɣa tebnid taddart n jdid, ad tegged taɛmadt x tzeqqa nnec, \add ḥima\add* war ttikkʷiḍen idammen ɣar taddart nnec, mařa iwḍa-dd zzayes ḥed.
\m 
\v 9 War zarreɛ ca amarjeɛ n uḍiř nnec s tnayen n markat n zzariɛet, ḥima war tᵉttwassɛiǧit marra ṣṣabet n zzariɛet nni tzarɛed uřa d řɣiǧet n umarjeɛ n uḍiř. \x ◘ \xo 22:9 \xt Lawi 19:19\x*
\v 10 War carrez ca s ufunas d weɣyuř jmiɛ.
\v 11 War yarreḍ ca arruḍ ittwaggen zi txeǧeḍt n taḍuft d řeqṭen jmiɛ.
\v 12 Ad tegged tcarcifa x arebɛa n iɣemmura n useřham nnec i zi třeḥḥfed.” \x ◘ \xo 22:12 \xt Řxř. 15:38; Mt. 23:5\x*
\b
\s1 Izerfan zi jjihet n řemřac
\m 
\v 13 “Mařa ijj n weryaz yiwi ict n temɣart uca yudef-dd xas, \add xenni\add* ad tt icarh,
\v 14 uca issekkar xas awařen uca yarra isem nnes d aɛeffan, inna: ‘Aqa tamɣart-a iwyeɣ tt, uca \add umi\add* ɣares-dd qarrbeɣ, iwḍeɣ ad ssneɣ aqa war teǧi ca d taɛzarect!’,
\v 15 \add xenni\add* ad isscen babas n tebřiɣt nni d yemmas \add lburhanat\add* n tɣuni n tebřiɣt i yemɣaren ɣar tewwart n tendint.
\v 16 Ad yini babas n tebřiɣt nni i yemɣaren: ‘Necc wciɣ yeǧi i weryaz-a d tamɣart uca netta idweř icarh i-tt,
\v 17 uca aqa netta issekkar xas awařen, inna: War ufiɣ ɣar yeǧic \add lburhanat\add* n tɣuni n tebřiɣt. Aqa aya d \add lburhanat n\add* tɣuni n yeǧi!’ Uca nitni ad bezzɛen ařeḥḥaf zzat i wudem n imɣaren n tendint.
\v 18 \add Xenni\add* ad ṭṭfen imɣaren n tendint aryaz nni uca ad t farcen
\v 19 uca ad as ggen multa n mya \add n uqiyyat\add* n nnuqart uca ad tent wcin i babas n tebřiɣt \add nni\add*, minzi netta yarra isem d aɛeffan x ict n teɛzarect zi Israil. Ad tiři d tamɣart nnes, war iḥeǧeř ad as iǧef marra ussan \add min ɣa yekk iddar\add*.
\v 20 \add Maca\add* mařa iffeɣ man aya d tidett uca war ufin \add lburhanat\add* n tɣuni ɣar tebřiɣt,
\v 21 \add xenni\add* ad ssuffɣen tabřiɣt nni ɣar tewwart n taddart n babas uca ad tt arejmen yeryazen n tendint, \add ař\add* ɣa temmet, minzi tegga řefḍiḥet di Israil umi tessefḍeḥ ixef nnes di taddart n babas. Ittxeṣṣa ad tekksed řɣar zi řwesṭ nnec.”
\m 
\v 22 “Mařa ittwaṭṭef ijj n weryaz umi iṭṭeṣ ak-d ca n temɣart i \add iǧan\add* ak-d weryaz, \add xenni\add* ad mmten s tnayen, aryaz nni iṭṭṣen ak-d temɣart d temɣart \add ɛawed\add*. Ittxeṣṣa ad tekksed řɣar zi Israil. \x ◘ \xo 22:22 \xt Lawi 20:10\x*
\m 
\v 23 Mařa ict n tebřiɣt d taɛzarect tᵉttwaxḍeb zeg ijj n weryaz, uca yufa i-tt ijj n weryaz di tendint uca iṭṭeṣ akides,
\v 24 \add xenni\add* ad ten tessuffɣem barra s tnayen ɣar tewwart n tendint, ad ttwarejmen ař ɣa mmten nitni: tabřiɣt minzi war tessekkar ca tɣuyyit di tendint, aryaz minzi isseḥqar tamɣart n jjar nnes. Ittxeṣṣa ad tekksed řɣar zi řwesṭ nnec.
\m 
\v 25 Mařa ijj n weryaz yufa ict n tebřiɣt ittwaxeḍben deg iyyar uca issexsar i-tt weryaz, iṭṭeṣ akides, \add xenni\add* ittxeṣṣa ad immet weryaz waha, wenni kis iṭṭṣen.
\v 26 War ttegg walu i tebřiɣt. Tabřiɣt war teggi ca ddenb ař řmewt, minzi tamesřact-a am \add tmesřact\add* n weryaz nni ikkaren ak-d jjar nnes uca inɣa i-t,
\v 27 minzi netta yufi tt deg iyyar, tesɣuy tebřiɣt nni ittwaxeḍben, maca war tuɣi din wi tt ɣa issnejmen.
\m 
\v 28 Xmi ca n weryaz yufa ict n tebřiɣt d taɛzarect, war tt ixḍib ḥed, uca netta iṭṭef i-tt, iṭṭeṣ akides uca ttwafen nitni,
\v 29 \add xenni\add* aryaz nni iṭṭṣen akides ad iwc i babas n tebřiɣt xemsin n \add uqiyyat n\add* nnuqart u nettat ad tedweř d tamɣart nnes, umi tt isseḥqar. War izemmar ad as iǧef marra ussan \add n tudart\add* nnes. \x ◘ \xo 22:29 \xt Uf. 22:16\x*
\m 
\v 30 War iɛeddeř i weryaz ad iksi tamɣart n babas u war iɛeddeř ad issɛarra x wafriw \add ittsarran\add* n warruḍ n babas.” \x ◘ \xo 22:30 \xt Aɛwd. 27:20\x*
\c 23
\s1 X yinni war izemmaren ad adfen ɣar tmesmunt
\m 
\v 1 “War iɛeddeř i \bd wenni umi deqfen\bd*, umi ttwaddzen \add imeǧařen\add* niɣ ttwakksen imenyaren ad yadef ɣar wegraw \add n řgens\add* n SIDI.
\m 
\v 2 War iɛeddeř i \bd mmis n řeḥram\bd* ad yadef ɣar wegraw \add n řgens\add* n SIDI. Ɛad ař jjiř wiss ɛecra nnes \add uřa d ijj zzayes\add* war d as iɛeddeř ad yadef ɣar tmesmunt n SIDI.
\m 
\v 3 \bd War iɛeddeř i yijjen n zeg ayt n Ɛammun niɣ i yijjen zeg ayt n Mu’abi ad yadef ɣar wegraw \bdit n řgens\bdit* n SIDI.\bd* Waxxa ař jjiř wiss ɛecra nnes ɛad war iɛeddeř i \add uřa d ijj zzaysen\add* ad yadef ɣar wegraw \add n řgens\add* n SIDI i řebda,\x ◘ \xo 23:3 \xt Naḥ. 13:1\x*
\v 4 minzi nitni war ɣarwem dd-ffiɣen ḥima ad kidwem msagaren ɣar webrid s weɣrum d waman umi dd-teffɣem zi Miṣra uca umi netta xak icra Balɛam, mmis n Baɛur, zi Fatur zi \add temmurt n\add* Aram-Nahrayn, \add aqa-tt d Misuputamya\add*, maḥend ad cek inɛeř. \f ◼ \fr 23:4 \fk Aram-Nahrayn\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘Misuputamiya’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 23:4 \xt Řxř. 22-24\x*
\v 5 \add Maca\add* SIDI, AREBBI nnec, tuɣa war ixs ad iseř i Balɛam uca SIDI, AREBBI nnec, yarra nneɛřet d lbaraka, minzi SIDI, AREBBI nnec, tuɣa ittexs i cek.
\v 6 War tarezzu x řehna nsen d řxar nsen, marra ussan \add n tudart nnec\add*, ař i řebda. \x ◘ \xo 23:6 \xt Ɛiz. 9:12\x*
\m 
\v 7 \bd War carreh Adumi\bd*, minzi netta d umac, \bd war carreh Amiṣri\bd*, minzi tuɣa cek d abarrani di temmurt nnes.
\v 8 Iḥenjiren i d asen ittwarwen iɛeddeř asen ad adfen ɣar wegraw \add n řgens\add* n SIDI zi jjiř wiss třata.”
\b
\s1 Tiweṣṣa nneɣni
\m 
\v 9 “Umi dd ɣa teffɣed s řɛeskar ḍidd i řɛedyan nnec, ad teḥḍid ixef nnec zi marra řɣar.
\v 10 Mařa din ijj n weryaz akidek, war iǧi ca d amezdag ak-d min imsaren s ǧiřet, ad iffeɣ barra i řmargeḥ n řɛeskar. War d as iɛeddeř maḥend ad yadef ɣar daxeř n řmargeḥ.
\v 11 Ɣar uweṭṭu n tmeddit, ad issird ixef nnes s waman u awarni i uɣeǧay n tfuct izemmar ad yadef \add ɛawed\add* ɣar řmargeḥ.
\v 12 Ittxeṣṣa ad ɣarek yiři wemcan barra i řmargeḥ n řɛeskar mani ɣa teffɣed di barra.
\v 13 Ad ɣarek yiři ɛawed jar řeqcuɛ nnec ijj n ujij uca xmi ɣa teqqimed barra, ad zzayes txebced ijj n weḥfur, ad tenqeřbed u ad txemmřed isuffɣan nnec.
\v 14 Minzi SIDI, AREBBI nnec, iggur di řmargeḥ nnec n řɛeskar ḥima ad cek ifekk u ḥima ad \add ac\add* isellem řɛedyan nnec zzat i wudem nnec. Tasqift nnec at tiři tqeddes, ḥima Netta war dayek ittwiři ca n řefḍiḥet uca ad xak inneqřeb awarni ac.”
\b
\m 
\v 15 “Ismeɣ i ɣarek dd-yarewřen zi bab nnes, war tzemmared ad t tsellmed \add ɛawed\add* i bab nnes.
\v 16 Ad kik izdeɣ di řwesṭ nnec, deg wemcan nni ɣa yixḍar ɣar daxeř i yict zi tewwura nnec, mani ɣa yiři mliḥ. War iɛeddeř ad t tḍeřmed.
\m 
\v 17 War tᵉttiři uřa d ict n temɣart n farq-ccɣeř n zzawect jar yessis n Israil uca war ittiři uřa d ijj n umetli \add n zzawect\add* jar ayt n Israil.
\m 
\v 18 Mammec ma yegga wawař nnec, war iɛeddeř ad dd-tawyed i uya řmunet n farq-ccɣeř niɣ ttaman n weqzin ɣar Taddart n SIDI, AREBBI nnec, minzi aqa aten s tnayen d ict n jjɛifect ɣar SIDI, AREBBI nnec.
\m 
\v 19 War ttegg arriba x umac, war iǧi arriba x nnuqart, war iǧi arriba x macca, war iǧi arriba x marra tamesřact nni izemmaren ad dd-tawi arriba. \f ◼ \fr 23:19 \fk arriba\ft - niɣ ‘řfayda’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 23:19 \xt Uf. 22:25; Lawi 25:36; Naḥ. 5:2-13.; Lk. 6:34,35\x*
\v 20 Tzemmared ad tegged arriba x ubarrani, maca war tzemmared ad tegged arriba x umac, ḥima ad ac ibarek SIDI, AREBBI nnec, di marra řxedmet n ifassen nnec di temmurt mani ɣa traḥed ḥima ad tt teksid d řwart.
\m 
\v 21 Xmi ɣa tegged ijj n lwaɛd i SIDI, AREBBI nnec, war teddikkwiřed ca ɣar ḍeffar maḥend ad t tkemmřed, minzi SIDI, AREBBI nnec, ad zzayek ittar \add ad\add* t \add tkemmřed\add*, \add mařa lla\add* ad xak yiři d ddenb. \x ◘ \xo 23:21 \xt Řxř. 30:3\x*
\v 22 Mařa war teggid ijj n lwaɛd, war xak ittiři ddenb.
\v 23 Min dd-iffɣen zi jar iyencicen nnec, ad t tkemmřed s tidett, am mammec ittxeṣṣa ad tkemmřed lwaɛd n tewhibt s řxaḍar nni zi twaɛded SIDI, AREBBI nnec, u wenni x tessiwřed s uqemmum nnec.
\m 
\v 24 Xmi ɣa tadfed ɣar umarjeɛ n uḍiř n umqarrab nnec, tzemmared ad tecced aḍiř ɛlaḥsab meẓri n řeɛmar nnec, maca ittxeṣṣa war tᵉttegged walu di tsuǧet nnec.
\m 
\v 25 Mařa tudfed ɣar imendi ibedden n jjar nnec, tzemmared ad teksid tidrin s ifassen nnec, maca war iɛeddeř ad tewted amjar deg imendi ibedden n jjar nnec.” \x ◘ \xo 23:25 \xt Mt. 12:1\x*
\b
\b
\c 24
\s1 Ijj n řḥař ifarzen n waǧaf
\m 
\v 1 “Xmi ɣa yawi ijj n weryaz ict n temɣart uca imřec akides uca war d as teɛjib umi dayes yufa ca n řefḍiḥet, uca \add xenni\add* ad as yari tabrat n weǧaf, ad as tt iwc deg ufus nnes uca ad tt issufeɣ zi taddart nnes, \x ◘ \xo 24:1 \xt Mt. 5:31; 19:7; Mk. 10:4\x*
\v 2 uca \add xenni\add* teffeɣ nettat zi taddart nnes, truḥ uca tedweř d tamɣart ɣar ijj n weryaz nneɣni,
\v 3 uca aryaz aneggaru icarh i-tt, ad as yari tabrat n weǧaf uca ad as tt iwc deg ufus nnes uca ad tt issekk zi taddart nnes, niɣ aryaz aneggaru nni i-tt yiwyen d tamɣart \add nnes\add*, immut,
\v 4 \add xenni\add* war iɛeddeř i weryaz nnes amezwaru, wenni d as iṭellqen, ad tt yegg \add ɛawed\add* d tamɣart i yixef nnes, awarni umi tᵉttwassexmej nettat, minzi man aya d jjɛifect zzat i wudem n SIDI. War iɛeddeř ad tessiwiḍ ddenb x temmurt i d ac iwca SIDI, AREBBI nnec, d řwart.”
\b
\s1 Tiweṣṣa i uḥeṭṭu x umqarreb
\m 
\v 5 “Xmi ijj n weryaz tuɣa am imřec, \add xenni\add* war itteffeɣ ca ak-d řɛeskar u war xas tᵉttwagg uřa d ict n tmesřact. Ad yiři ijj n useggʷas i taddart nnes waha u ad issfarḥ tamɣart nnes i yiwi \add i yixef nnes\add*.” \x ◘ \xo 24:5 \xt Aɛwd. 20:7\x*
\m 
\v 6 “War iɛeddeř ad teksid iẓra n tsirt s tnayen d aḍman, niɣ \add aẓru\add* nni \add zzaysen\add* ittenhezzan \add waha\add*, minzi aqa \add xenni\add* ad yiři řeɛmar d aḍman.”
\m 
\v 7 “Mařa ittwaf ijj n weryaz yucar ca n yijj zeg wawmaten nnes, zeg ayt n Israil, uca netta yarra i-t d ismeɣ uca izzenz i-t, \add xenni\add* ad immet uceffar \add nni\add*. Ittxeṣṣa ad tekksed řɣar zi řwesṭ nnec.” \x ◘ \xo 24:7 \xt Uf. 21:16\x*
\m 
\v 8 “Xmi \add din teǧa\add* jjriḥect n řbarṣ, ḥḍa ad teḥḍid u ad tegged nican ɛlaḥsab marra min d ac ɣa ssřemden ikehhanen Ilawiyyen. Ad teḥḍam maḥend ad teggem marra am mammec ten umureɣ. \x ◘ \xo 24:8 \xt Lawi 13:2\x*
\v 9 Idar min igga SIDI, AREBBI nnec, ak-d Maryam deg webrid umi dd-teffɣem zi Miṣra.”\x ◘ \xo 24:9 \xt Řxř. 12:10\x*
\m 
\v 10 “Mařa tarḍřed ca i jjar nnec, \add xenni\add* war ttidef ɣar taddart nnes ḥima ad zzayes teksid ca d aḍman \add i yixef nnec\add*.
\v 11 Ad teqqimed barra uca aryaz i umi tarḍřed ad ac dd-yawi ddiyyet ɣar barra.
\v 12 Mařa tuɣa d aryaz d amezřuḍ, \add xenni\add* war ttᵉttnusi deg werhan nnes \add amecnaw i yeǧa d tassut nnes\add*.
\v 13 Ad as dd-tarred ddiyyet nni nican ɣar uɣeǧi n tfuct, ḥima ad iṭṭeṣ di tassut nnes uca ad ac ibarek. Man aya ad ac tiři d tasegda zzat i wudem n SIDI, AREBBI nnec.”\x ◘ \xo 24:13 \xt Uf. 22:26\x*
\m 
\v 14 “War sḥissfem acewwař ameḥdaj amezřuḍ zeg aytmac niɣ zeg ibarraniyyen i izeddɣen di temmurt nnec u daxeř i tewwura nnec. \x ◘ \xo 24:14 \xt Lawi 19:13; Yaɛ. 5:4\x*
\v 15 Ad as tewced řmunet nnes kuř ass. War xas tɣeǧi tfuct x man aya, minzi netta d amezřuḍ uca immeẓri dayes, ḥima netta war ittřiɣi i SIDI di ssibbet nnec uca ad dayek yiři ddenb.”
\m 
\v 16 “Ibabaten war ttwaneqqen di ssibbet n iḥenjiren nsen u iḥenjiren war ttwaneqqen di ssibbet n ibabaten nsen. Kuř ijj ad ittwaneɣ di ssibbet n ddenb nnes.”\x ◘ \xo 24:16 \xt 2 Ij. 14:6; 2 Im. 25:4; Irm. 31:30; Ḥiz. 18:20\x*
\m 
\v 17 “War sfarraɣ řeḥkam n ubarrani d uyujiř niɣ ad teksid arruḍ n tajjač d aḍman.\x ◘ \xo 24:17 \xt Uf. 22:21, 22; Awřn. 22:22; Ica. 1:23; Irm. 5:28; 22:3; Ḥiz. 22:29; Zak. 7:10\x*
\v 18 Ad tɛeqřed belli tuɣa cek d ismeɣ di Miṣra uca aqa SIDI, AREBBI nnec, ifdi cek ssenni. X uya necc ttumureɣ cek ad tegged man aya. \f ◼ \fr 24:18 \fk ifdi\ft - xzar Izhd. 78:35.\f*
\v 19 Xmi tmejjared ṣṣabet nnec deg iyyar nnec uca tᵉttud ca n tqebbiḍt deg iyyar, \add xenni\add* war dd-tᵉddikkʷiřed maḥend ad tt teksid. Ad tiři \add d tasɣart\add* i ubarrani, i uyujiř u i tajjač, ḥima ad cek ibarek SIDI, AREBBI nnec, di marra řxedmet n ifassen nnec.\x ◘ \xo 24:19 \xt Lawi 19:9; 23:22\x*
\v 20 Xmi ɣa tẓewḍed tacejjart nnec n zzitun, war ttic taynit \add ɛad\add* i min iqqimen awarni ac. D man aya i ɣa yiřin i ubarrani, i uyujiř u i tajjač.
\v 21 Awarni řami třeqḍed aḍiř n umarjeɛ nnec n uḍiř, war arezzu ad třeqḍed min iqqimen awarni ac ɛawed. Aqa man aya ad yiři i ubarrani, i uyujiř u i tajjač.
\v 22 Ad tɛeqřed belli tuɣa cek d ismeɣ di temmurt n Miṣra. X uya necc ttumureɣ cek ad tegged man aya.”
\b
\b
\c 25
\s1 Tiweṣṣa nneɣni
\m 
\v 1 “Mařa \add din\add* ijj n umcubbec jar iryazen uca ittxeṣṣa asen ad uyuren ɣar řmeḥkama, ad \add xasen\add* ḥekmen, \add xenni\add* ad barrḥen x wenni ɣar iǧa řḥeqq uca ad ḥekmen x umednub. \f ◼ \fr 25:1 \fk wenni ɣar iǧa řḥeqq\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘amsegged’.\f*
\v 2 Mařa amednub issdaheǧ tiyyita, \add xenni\add* řqaḍi ad yejj ad t ɣeḍřen ɣar temmurt uca ad \add t\add* farcen zzat i wudem nnes anect itturs \add di řeḥsab\add* n řɣecc nnes.
\v 3 Iɛeddeř ad as iwc arebɛin n teyyita, war ɣarsent yarenni ca, minzi mařa ad t ifarc ɛad ktar sennej i tiyyita-ya, aqa umac ad ac dd-iban d ameḥgur jar tiṭṭawin nnec.”\x ◘ \xo 25:3 \xt 2 Kur. 11:24\x*
\m 
\v 4 “War ttegg tacmant i ufunas xmi issarwat.” \x ◘ \xo 25:4 \xt 1 Kur. 9:9; 1 Tim. 5:18\x*
\b
\m 
\v 5 “Xmi zeddɣen wawmaten ak-d wayawya uca immut ijj zzaysen, uca war dd-yejji ca mmis, \add xenni\add* tamɣart n umettin war tmeǧec ca ak-d ca n weryaz barra familiya nnes. Ad xas yadef wařews uca ad tt igg d tamɣart nnes uca ad as yegg xenni \bd lwajib n wařews\bd*. \f ◼ \fr 25:5 \fk ařwes\ft - niɣ ‘umas n weryaz nnes’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 25:5 \xt Mt. 22:24; Mk. 12:19; Lk. 20:28\x*
\v 6 Uca amenzu nni i dd ɣa taruw, ad ixřef isem n umas immuten, \add ḥima\add* isem n wa war imeḥḥi ca zi Israil.
\v 7 \add Maca\add* mařa aryaz war ixs ad iksi tamɣart n umas, ad třah \add xenni\add* temɣart n umas ɣar tewwart, ɣar imɣaren, ad tini: ‘Ařews inu yugi ad ixřef isem n umas di Israil, war ixs ad igg lwajib n wařews.’ \x ◘ \xo 25:7 \xt Raɛ. 4:7\x*
\v 8 \add Xenni\add* imɣaren n tendint nni ad as dd-řaɣan uca ad akides ssiwřen. Mařa netta imneɛ deg wawař nnes uca inna: ‘War xseɣ ca ad tt awyeɣ!’,
\v 9 ad ɣares dd-tqarreb \add xenni\add* tařewst zzat i tiṭṭawin n imɣaren, ad as tekkes sandala nnes zeg uḍar uca ad xas tessusef x uɣembub, ad tbarreḥ, ad tini: ‘Ammu i ittwagg deg weryaz nni war ixsen ad ibna taddart n umas!’ \x ◘ \xo 25:9 \xt Raɛ. 4:5\x*
\v 10 Uca ad as řaɣan di Israil s yisem wanita: ‘Taddart n wenni umi ittwakkes sandala nnes!’”
\b
\m 
\v 11 “Mařa \add din\add* iryazen mcubbucen uca treḥḥeg-dd temɣart n ca n ijj ḥima ad tfekk aryaz nnes zeg ufus n wi t iccaten uca nettat tesswiẓẓeḍ afus nnes uca tᵉṭṭef i-t zi tfulin n useḍḥi nnes,
\v 12 ad as tqessed \add xenni\add* afus nnes, war d am ttezziǧiz.”
\m 
\v 13 “War ɣarek ittiři di txancet nnec ijj n weẓru \add n řewzen\add* d ijj n weẓru \add nneɣni\add*, ijj n weẓru d ameqqran uřa d ijj n weẓru d ameẓyan.
\v 14 War ɣarek ittiři di taddart nnec, \add řmud\add* n ijj n ifa uřa d ijj n ifa \add nneɣni\add*, ijj n ifa d ameqqran uřa d ijj n ifa d ameẓyan.
\v 15 \bd Ijj n weẓru \bdit n řewzen\bdit* iwaṭa, iseggem\bd* ad ɣarek yiři uřa d \bd \bdit ij n řmud n\bdit* yijj n ifa nican, iwaṭa\bd*, ḥima ussan nnec ad zzuggarten x wudem \add n temmurt\add* nni i d ac ɣa iwc, SIDI, AREBBI nnec.
\v 16 Minzi marra wi ɣa iggin man aya, marra wi ɣa iggin řɣecc, aqa netta d nnɛi ɣar SIDI, AREBBI nnec.” \x ◘ \xo 25:16 \xt Awřn. 11:1\x*
\b
\s1 Ateḥḥi n Ɛamaliq
\m 
\v 17 “Idar min zzayek igga \bd Ɛamaliq\bd* deg webrid, umi dd-teffɣed zi Miṣra, \x ◘ \xo 25:17 \xt Uf. 17:8\x*
\v 18 mammec dd-iffeɣ ɣar umsagar akidek deg webrid uca ihjem xak zi ḍeffar \add mani ǧan\add* marra inni iḍeɛfen, umi cek tuɣa tuḥřed, tefnid. Netta war iggʷid ca AREBBI.
\v 19 Ad imsar, xmi SIDI, AREBBI nnec, ad cek issareyyeḥ zi marra řɛedyan i d ac-dd innḍen di temmurt i d ac ɣa iwc SIDI, AREBBI nnec, d řwart, ḥima ad tt teksid, aqa ad temḥid řidaret n Ɛamaliq zi sadu ujenna. War t ttᵉttu!”
\b
\b
\c 26
\s1 Tawhibt n imezwura
\m 
\v 1 “Xmi ɣa tadfed ɣar temmurt nni d ac ɣa iwc SIDI, AREBBI nnec, d řwart, uca ad tt tᵉṭṭfed uca ad dayes tzedɣed,
\v 2 \add xenni\add* ad teksid zi tmezwarut n kuř řɣiǧet i ɣa tessmuned zi temmurt nni d ac ɣa iwc SIDI, AREBBI nnec, ad t tegged di tsuǧet uca ad traḥed ɣar wemcan i ɣa yixḍar SIDI maḥend ad din issezdeɣ Isem nnes. \x ◘ \xo 26:2 \xt Uf. 23:19; 34:26; Lawi 2:14; 23:10; Řxř. 15:17\x*
\v 3 Uca ad dd-tased ɣar ukehhan, wenni \add din\add* ɣa yiřin deg wussan nni, ad as tinid: ‘Aqa ass-a ad barrḥeɣ i SIDI, AREBBI nnec, belli aqa udfeɣ ɣar temmurt nni x ijjuǧ SIDI i řejdud nneɣ ḥima ad aneɣ tt iwc.’
\v 4 Uca ad iksi ukehhan tasuǧet zeg ufus nnec, ad tt issars zzat i uɛalṭar n SIDI, AREBBI nnec.
\v 5 Ad tbarrḥed zzat i wudem n SIDI, AREBBI nnec, ad tinid: ‘Aramiyu nni tuɣa iǧan ɛřaḥař ad ifna aqa tuɣa-t d baba. Netta ihwa ɣar Miṣra uca izdeɣ din am ubarrani ak-d ijj n wuru n yeryazen \add waha\add* uca iyma, idweř d ijj n řgens imɣar, ijhed u deg waṭṭas. \x ◘ \xo 26:5 \xt Amz. 46:1\x*
\v 6 Imiṣriyyen ḍeřmen u ḥṣaren aneɣ u ggin xaneɣ tasmuɣi teqseḥ.
\v 7 Uca nesɣuy ɣar SIDI, AREBBI n řejdud nneɣ, uca isřa SIDI i tmijja nneɣ u iẓra arẓiyyet nneɣ d řeɣben nneɣ d řmeḥnet nneɣ.
\v 8 Issuffeɣ aneɣ-dd SIDI zi Miṣra s ufus ijehden, s uɣiř isswiẓẓḍen, s timegga imɣaren issiggʷiden, s řeɛřamat u s lmuɛjizat,
\v 9 uca issidef aneɣ ɣar wemcan-a uca iwca aneɣ tammurt-a, tammurt ifeyyḍen s uɣi d tamment.
\v 10 Uca řexxu, xzar, iwyeɣ-dd tamezwarut n řɣiǧet n temmurt nni d ayi tewcid, \add a\add* SIDI!’ \add Xenni\add* ad t tegged zzat i wudem n SIDI, AREBBI nnec, ad tbendqed zzat i wudem n SIDI, AREBBI nnec.
\v 11 Ad tfarrḥed zi marra řxař i ɣa iwc SIDI, AREBBI nnec, i cek u i \add aytbab n\add* taddart nnec: cek d Ulawi d ubarrani i iǧan di řwesṭ nnec.”
\b
\s1 Řeɛcur
\m 
\v 12 “Xmi ɣa tkemmřed zeg uɛeccar n marra řeɛcur n řɣiǧet nnec deg useggʷas wiss třata, wenni d aseggʷas n řeɛcur, xenni ad ten tewced i Ulawi, i ubarrani, i uyujiř, i tajjač, \add ḥima\add* ad ccen daxeř i tewwura nnec u ad jjiwnen. \x ◘ \xo 26:12 \xt Lawi 27:30; Řxř. 18:24, Aɛwd. 14:28, 29\x*
\v 13 Uca ad tinid zzat i wudem n SIDI, AREBBI nnec: ‘Aqa ksiɣ min iǧan iqeddsen zi taddart inu uca ɛawed wciɣ t i Ulawi, i ubarrani, i uyujiř, i tajjač, am mammec marra tiweṣṣa i d ayi tweṣṣid. Necc war ɛeddiɣ uřa x icten zi tweṣṣa nnec u war ttuɣ walu. \x ◘ \xo 26:13 \xt Aɛwd. 14:27\x*
\v 14 War zzayes cciɣ deg wecḍan inu u war zzayes ksiɣ umi xemjeɣ uřa war zzayes wciɣ i yijj n umettin. Aqa sřiɣ i tmijja n SIDI, AREBBI inu, u ggiɣ marra min d ayi tumured.
\v 15 Xzar zi Tzeddiɣt nnec iqeddsen, zeg ujenna, ɣar swadday uca barek řgens nnec Israil d temmurt nni d aneɣ tewcid, am mammec tejjuǧed i řejdud nneɣ, tammurt nni ittfeyyḍen s uɣi d tamment.’” \x ◘ \xo 26:15 \xt Ica. 63:15\x*
\b
\s1 Awař aneggaru
\m 
\v 16 “SIDI, AREBBI nnec, aqa yumur i cek ass-a, ad tegged tiweṣṣa-ya d lfarayiḍ-a. Ḥḍa tent uca egg zzaysen s marra uř nnec d marra řeɛmar nnec.
\v 17 Ass-a tennid aqa SIDI ad yiři d AREBBI nnec, ad tuyured deg ibriden nnes, ad teḥḍid tiweṣṣa d řumurat nnes d lfarayiḍ nnes uca ad tesřed i tmijja nnes. \x ◘ \xo 26:17 \xt Amz. 17:7\x*
\v 18 Uca SIDI inna ac ass-a i cek, aqa cek ad ɣares tiřid d ijj n řgens iɣřa aṭṭas, am mammec d awem inna, u ittxeṣṣa ac ad teḥḍid marra tiweṣṣa nnes, \x ◘ \xo 26:18 \xt Uf. 19:5; Aɛwd. 7:6; 14:2\x*
\v 19 ḥima Netta ad cek issuɛřa x marra řegnus i usemɣar d yisem d řɛezz, ḥima ad tiřid d ijj n řgens iqeddsen i SIDI, AREBBI nnec, am mammec tuɣa inna.” \x ◘ \xo 26:19 \xt Aɛwd. 4:7\x*
\b
\b
\c 27
\s1 Adrar n Ɛibal d wedrar n Jirizim
\m 
\v 1 Musa, ak-d imɣaren n Israil, yumur řgens, inna:
\m “Ḥḍam marra tiweṣṣa-ya, tinni d awem umureɣ necc ass-a.
\v 2 Ad imsar deg wass umi ɣa teẓwam iɣzar n L’Urdun ɣar temmurt nni d ac ɣa iwc SIDI, AREBBI nnec, aqa ad tessbedded iẓra imeqqranen uca ad ten tḥennced s jjar. \x ◘ \xo 27:2 \xt Yac. 4:1\x*
\v 3 Ad dayes tarid marra awařen n Ccariɛa-ya, xmi ɣa teẓwid ḥima ad tadfed ɣar temmurt nni d ac ɣa iwc SIDI, AREBBI nnec, ict n temmurt ifeyyḍen s uɣi d tamment, am mammec i d ac inna SIDI, AREBBI n řejdud nnec.
\v 4 Xmi ɣa teẓwam iɣzar n L’Urdun, ad tessbeddem iẓra, inni x d awem umureɣ ass-a x wedrar n Ɛibal uca ad ten tḥennced s jjar.
\v 5 Ad din tebnid ijj n uɛalṭar i SIDI, AREBBI nnec, ijj n uɛalṭar n yeẓra. War xas tessiřiyed \add dduzan n\add* wuzzař zi ssa ɣar da. \x ◘ \xo 27:5 \xt Uf. 20:25; Yac. 8:31\x*
\v 6 Ittxeṣṣa ad tebnid aɛalṭar n SIDI, AREBBI nnec, s yeẓra kemřen \add waha\add* uca ad xas tessbexxared tiɣarṣa n wecmaḍ i SIDI, AREBBI nnec.
\v 7 \add Ɛawed\add* ad as tqeddmed tiɣarṣi nnec n řehna. Ad din tecced uca ad tfarḥed zzat i wudem n SIDI, AREBBI nnec.
\v 8 Ad tarid marra awařen n Ccariɛa-ya deg yeẓra s ijj n wenqac icewwaren icnan.”
\b
\m 
\v 9 Tuɣa Musa issawař ak-d ikehhanen, Ilawiyyen, ɣar marra Israil, inna: “Sqar, sḥess, \add a\add* Israil! Ass-a tiwḍed ad tiřid d ijj n řgens i SIDI, AREBBI nnec.
\v 10 Ad tesřed i tmijja n SIDI, AREBBI nnec, uca ad tegged zi řumurat nnes d tweṣṣa nnes, tinni x cek umureɣ ass-a.”
\b
\m 
\v 11 Iweṣṣa Musa řgens deg wass nni, inna:
\b
\m 
\v 12 “Xmi ɣa teẓwam L’Urdun ad bedden tqebbař aya \bd x wedrar n Jirizim ḥima ad barken řgens\bd*: Cimɛun d Lawi d Yahuda d Issakar d Yusuf d Binyamin.”\x ◘ \xo 27:12 \xt Aɛwd. 11:29\x*
\m 
\v 13 “Uca \add tiqebbař-a\add* ad bedden \bd x wedrar n Ɛibal ḥima ad neɛřen\bd*: Rubin, Jad d Ɛacir d Zabulun, Dan d Naftali.”
\m 
\v 14 “Ad barrḥen Ilawiyyen uca ad inin s tmijja ijehden i marra arraw n Israil:
\b
\m 
\v 15 ‘D amenɛuř aryaz nni iggin ijj n řexyař ineqcen niɣ ifesyen, aqa-t d jjɛifect i SIDI, ict n řxedmet n ifassen n uḥrayfi, uca ad tt igg deg wemcan nnes s tnuffra.’ Uca marra řgens ad dd-yarr ad yini: ‘Amin!’
\m 
\v 16 ‘D amenɛuř wi ɣa isseḥqaren babas niɣ yemmas!’ Uca marra řgens ad yini: ‘Amin!’
\m 
\v 17 ‘D amenɛuř wi ɣa issmuṭṭyen aymir n jjar nnes!’ Uca marra řgens ad yini: ‘Amin!’
\m 
\v 18 ‘D amenɛuř wi ɣa issweddaren adarɣař deg webrid!” Uca marra řgens ad yini: ‘Amin!’
\m 
\v 19 ‘D amenɛuř wi ɣa issfarrɣen tasɣart n ubarrani, n uyujiř u n tajjač!’ Uca marra řgens ad yini: ‘Amin!’
\m 
\v 20 ‘D amenɛuř wi ɣa iṭṭṣen ak-d temɣart n babas, minzi ittɛarra babas’ Uca marra řgens ad yini: ‘Amin!” \x ◘ \xo 27:20 \xt Aɛwd. 23:1\x*
\m 
\v 21 ‘D amenɛuř wi ɣa iṭṭṣen ak-d ca n umuddar!’ Uca marra řgens ad yini: ‘Amin!’
\m 
\v 22 ‘D amenɛuř wi ɣa iṭṭṣen ak-d učmas, yeǧis n babas niɣ yeǧis n yemmas!’ Uca marra řgens ad yini: ‘Amin!’
\m 
\v 23 ‘D amenɛuř wi ɣa iṭṭṣen ak-d tadeggʷač nnes!’ Uca marra řgens ad yini: ‘Amin!’
\m 
\v 24 ‘D amenɛuř wi ɣa inɣen jjar nnes s tnuffra!’ Uca marra řgens ad yini: ‘Amin!’
\m 
\v 25 ‘D amenɛuř wi ɣa iṭṭfen arrecwet maḥend ad inɣa ijj n bnadem, \add mahend ad issizzeř\add* idammen imezdagen!’ Uca marra řgens ad yini: ‘Amin!’
\m 
\v 26 ‘D amenɛuř wi war ittqarran awařen n Ccariɛa-ya maḥend ad ten yegg!’ Uca marra řgens ad yini: ‘Amin!’”\x ◘ \xo 27:26 \xt Gal. 3:10\x*
\b
\b
\c 28
\s1 Lbarakat d nnaɛři
\m 
\v 1 “Ad imsar, mařa tesřid mliḥ i tmijja n SIDI, AREBBI nnec, ad teḥḍid marra tiweṣṣa nnes, tinni d ac ttumureɣ ass-a ḥima ad tent tegged, \add xenni\add* ad cek issuɛřa SIDI, AREBBI nnec, x marra řegnus n temmurt. \x ◘ \xo 28:1 \xt Lawi 26:3\x*
\v 2 Marra \bd lbarakat-a\bd* ad xak dd-asent, ad ac dd-awḍent, mařa tesřid i tmijja n SIDI, AREBBI nnec.
\b
\m 
\v 3 Ad tᵉttwabarked di tendint u ad tᵉttwabarked deg iyyar.
\v 4 Ad tᵉttwabarek řɣiǧet n uɛeddis nnec d řɣiǧet n temmurt nnec d řɣiǧet n řebhayem nnec d twarura n tfunasin nnec d imeẓyanen iɛizzen n wuǧi nnec.
\v 5 Ad tᵉttwabarek tsuǧet nnec d tebqect nnec.
\v 6 Ad tᵉttwabarked ɣar wadaf nnec, ad tᵉttwabarked deg wuffuɣ nnec.”
\b
\m 
\v 7 “SIDI ad isellem řɛedyan nnec, inni xak ɣa ikkaren d ibarḥaḍ zzat i wudem nnec. Ad xak dd-ffɣen deg webrid d ijj uca ad arewřen zzat i wudem nnec x sebɛa n ibriden.
\v 8 SIDI ad ac yumur s lbaraka di tesrafin nnec u x marra min igga ufus nnec. Netta ad cek ibarek di temmurt nni i d ac ɣa iwc SIDI, AREBBI nnec.
\v 9 SIDI ad cek yarr ad tekkared am yijj n řgens iqeddsen i Yixef nnes am mammec i d ac ijjuǧ, xmi ɣa teḥḍid tiweṣṣa n SIDI, AREBBI nnec, uca ad tuyured deg ibriden nnes.
\v 10 Marra řegnus n temmurt ad ẓaren belli Isem n SIDI ittwadenna xak uca ad zzayek ggʷeden.
\v 11 SIDI ad ac iwc řxar s ufeyyeḍ di řɣiǧet n uɛeddis nnec u di řɣiǧet n řebhayem nnec u di řɣiǧet n temmurt nnec, di temmurt nni ijjuǧ SIDI i řejdud nnec ad ac tt-i-dd-iwc. \x ◘ \xo 28:11 \xt Aɛwd. 30:9\x*
\v 12 SIDI ad ac yarzem \add tawwart n\add* wexxam nnes n txubay iṣeřḥen, ijenwan, ḥima ad iwc anẓar i temmurt nnec di řweqt nnes u ḥima ad ibarek marra řxedmet n ufus nnec. Ad tarḍřed i waṭṭas n řegnus, maca cek war \add xasen\add* tareṭṭřed.
\v 13 SIDI ad cek yarr d azeǧif, war iǧi d unewwar, uca cek waha ad tiřid sennej, war tᵉttiřid swadday, mařa tesřid i tweṣṣa n SIDI, AREBBI nnec, wenni i d ac ttumureɣ ass-a ḥima ad tent teḥḍid uca ad zzaysent tegged.
\v 14 War ttḥeyyid ca \add ɣar\add* yefus uřa \add ɣar\add* uzeřmaḍ x marra awařen nni d ac umureɣ ass-a ařami ɣa teḍfared irebbiten nneɣni, ad xasen tsexxared.
\v 15 \add Maca\add* ad imsar, mařa war tesřid i wawař n SIDI, AREBBI nnec, ḥima ad teḥḍid marra řumurat d tweṣṣa nnes i x d ac ttumureɣ ass-a, ḥima ad zzaysent tegged, \add xenni\add* marra \bd nnɛaři\bd*-ya ad xak dd-hwant u ad cek řeqfent:\x ◘ \xo 28:15 \xt Lawi 26:14; Igjd. 2:17; Dan. 9:11, 13; Mal. 2:2 \x*
\b
\m 
\v 16 \add Ad tiřid\add* d amenɛuř di tendint u \add ad tiřid\add* d amenɛuř deg iyyar.
\v 17 Tasuǧet nnec d tebqect nnec \add ad iřint\add* ttwaneɛřent.
\v 18 D tamenɛuřt i ɣa tiři řɣiǧet n uɛeddis nnec d řɣiǧet n temmurt nnec u twarura n tfunasin nnec d imeẓyanen iɛizzen n wuǧi nnec.
\v 19 \add Ad tiřid\add* d amenɛuř ɣar wadaf nnec u \add ad tiřid\add* d amenɛuř deg uffuɣ nnec.”
\b
\m 
\v 20 “Ad ac dd-issekk SIDI nneɛřet d uxarweḍ d uheddi ɣar marra mani isswiẓẓed ufus nnec, ař ɣa tᵉttwamḥid u ad tefnid deɣya zzat i wudem inu di ssibbet n řexdayem nnec tiɛeffanin, minzi tejjid ayi.
\v 21 SIDI ad dayek isseřṣeq ṭṭaɛun ař cek ɣa iqḍa zi temmurt nni ɣar ɣa tadfed ḥima ad tt teksid d řwart.
\v 22 SIDI ad cek iwwet s bu-deǧis, s tmessi \add n arwaḥ\add* d ugeyyeḥ, s řeḥmu d řaẓaɣ, s \add imendi\add* ittwasscemḍen \add zeg usemmiḍ\add* uřa d jjriḥect n wefsu. Ina ad cek ḍfaren ař ɣa thellked. \x ◘ \xo 28:22 \xt Lawi 26:16\x*
\v 23 Ajenna nni \add iǧan\add* tiwa i uzeǧif nnec ad yiři d nnḥas u tammurt nni \add iǧan\add* sadu nnec d uzzař. \x ◘ \xo 28:23 \xt Lawi 26:19\x*
\v 24 Ad yarr SIDI, AREBBI nnec, anẓar n temmurt nnec d \add ijj n useynu n\add* řeɛjaj d \add ibquqen n\add* řeɛjaj. Man aya ad xak dd-ihwa ař ɣa tᵉttwateḥḥid.
\v 25 SIDI ad cek yarr tᵉttwaɣeřbed zzat i wudem n řɛedyan nnec. Deg ijj n webrid ad dd-teffɣed ḍidd i řeɛdu nnec uca ad tarewřed zzat i wudem nnes x sebɛa n ibriden uca ad tiřid d \add ict n řqecɛet\add* n unexřiɛ i marra tigeldiwin n ddunect.
\v 26 Řxecbet nnec ad tiři d macca i ijḍaḍ n ujenna u i marra řmař x temmurt uca uřa d ijj war izemmar ad ten issiggʷed.
\v 27 SIDI ad cek iwwet s tḥebba n Miṣra, s iɛebbuzen, s jdam, s wajjiḍ ař ɣa taf war tzemmared ad teggenfid. \x ◘ \xo 28:27 \xt Uf. 9:9\x*
\v 28 SIDI ad cek iwwet s tubbuheřya, s tuddarɣeč u s arjef n wuř.”
\b
\m 
\v 29 “Deg wezyen n uziř ad tḥadid am uḥadi n udarɣař di taǧest. Ibriden nnec war ttiřin ṣeřḥen, \add wah,\add* ad tiřid tᵉttwaḥṣared u tᵉttwakeccḍed marra ussan \add n tudart nnec\add* uca war ittiři wi cek ɣa issenjmen.
\v 30 Ad txeḍbed ict n temɣart uca ijj n weryaz nneɣni ad tt issnuqqeb, ad tebnid taddart i yixef nnec uca war dayes tzeddɣed, ad teggid ijj n umarjeɛ n uḍiř ad dayes teẓẓud tizayarin maca war zzaysent testenfiɛed.
\v 31 Afunas nnec ad ittwaɣarṣ zzat i tiṭṭawin nnec uca war zzayes tᵉttetted, aɣyuř nnec ad t ucaren zzat i wudem nnec uca war d ac dd-ittɛiqqib. Uǧi nnec ad t wcen i řɛedyan nnec uca war ɣarek ittiři wi ɣa issenjmen.
\v 32 Ad mmewcen iḥenjiren nnec d tḥenjirin nnec i yijj n řgens nneɣni. Tiṭṭawin nnec ad twařant uca ad daysen temmeẓred ass ikmeř uca war ittiři jjehd deg ufus nnec.
\v 33 Řɣiǧet n temmurt nnec d marra řxedmet nnec ad t icc ijj n řgens i war tessined uca ad tiřid teḥṣared u ad třebzed waha marra ussan \add n tudart nnec\add*.
\v 34 Ad tdewřed d abuhaři zi ssibbet n min ɣa tẓared s tiṭṭawin nnec.”
\b
\m 
\v 35 “SIDI ad cek iwwet s tḥebba tiɛeffanin ɣar ifadden u ɣar iḍaren i zi war tzemmared ad zzaysen teggenfid, zi třeqqa n uḍar nnec ař aceqquf \add n uzeǧif\add* nnec.
\v 36 SIDI ad cek yarr \add jmiɛ\add* ak-d ujeǧid nnec, wenni cek ɣa tegged x yixef nnec, ad traḥed ɣar ijj n řgens nni war tessined ca, uřa d řejdud nnec, uca din i ɣa tsexxared i irebbiten nneɣni n ukeccuḍ d weẓru.
\v 37 Ad tiřid d \add ict n řqecɛet n\add* unexřiɛ d ijj n umedya d ict \add n ssibbet i\add* ustehzi iqesḥen jar marra řegnus mani cek ɣa indeh SIDI.
\v 38 Ad tessuffɣed aṭṭas n zzariɛet ɣar yeyyar uca ad třeqḍed drus, minzi tamurɣi ad tt teḥřuw. \x ◘ \xo 28:38 \xt Mixa 6:15; Ḥag. 1:6\x*
\v 39 Ad teggid imarjaɛen n uḍiř ad daysen teẓẓud tizayarin uca ad tent tɛarrṣed, \add maca\add* war tsessed binu uca war třeqqḍed walu, minzi ad tent icc ukecca.
\v 40 Ad ɣarek iřin izemmuren di marra tammurt nnec, \add maca\add* war tdehhned ixef nnec s zzect, minzi ad iwḍa \add zzitun\add* zeg uzemmur nnec \add qbeř řweqt\add*.
\v 41 Ad dd-tejjed iḥenjiren d tḥenjirin, \add maca\add* war ttiřin ca nnec, minzi ad ruḥen di tmeḥbast.
\v 42 Marra ticejjura d řɣiǧet n temmurt nnec ad tent tᵉṭṭef tmurɣi d tasɣart nnes.
\v 43 Abarrani nni \add iǧan\add* di řwesṭ nnec, ad xak issuɛřa ixef nnes, sennej u sennej ɛad, uca cek ad tᵉttwassehwid ɣar temmurt, swadday ɣar wadday.
\v 44 Netta ad ac yarḍeř, \add maca\add* cek war d as tareṭṭřed. Netta ad yiři d azeǧif, cek ad tiřid d anewwar.
\v 45 Uca ad xak dd-hwant marra nnɛaři-ya, ad cek ḍfarent, ad cek řeqfent ař ɣa tᵉttwamḥid, umi war tesřid i tmijja n SIDI, AREBBI nnec, ḥima ad teḥḍid řumurat nnes d tiweṣṣa nnes, inni d ac yumur Netta.
\v 46 Ad iřint d ict n řeɛřamet d ijj n usiggʷid yewɛaren i cek u i zzariɛet nnec i řebda.
\v 47 Minzi war tsexxared i SIDI, AREBBI nnec s řefraḥet d tcuni n wuř zi ssibbet n ufeyyeḍ n marra min din \add iǧan\add*,
\v 48 ad tsexxared i řɛedyan, inni i xak ɣa issekk SIDI, s řaẓ d ufadi, s tuɛɛaryent d řexṣeṣ n marra timesřayin, uca Netta ad igg azayřu n wuzzař x yiri nnec, ař cek ɣa imḥa.
\v 49 SIDI ad xak dd-issgeɛɛed ijj n řgens iggʷej, zeg uneggaru n temmurt, am yijj n ugider iṭṭawen, ijj n řgens i umi war tzemmared ad tfehmed iřes nnes, \f ◼ \fr 28:49 \fk agider\ft - niɣ ‘asiwan’.\f*
\v 50 ijj n řgens ɣares udem iqḍeɛ, war ittweqqar awessar, war yareḥḥem x uḥenjir.
\v 51 Ad yecc řɣiǧet n řebhayem nnec d řɣiǧet n temmurt nnec, ař ɣa tᵉttwamḥid, minzi war d ac ittejji irden, niɣ binu n jdid, niɣ zzect \add n ṭṭri\add*, niɣ twarura n tfunasin nnec niɣ imeẓyanen iɛizzen n wuǧi nnec, ař cek i ɣa yareddeǧ.
\v 52 Ad cek iḥṣar jar marra tewwura nnec, ař ɣa wḍan řeḥyuḍ yuɛřan imetnen, inni x tuɣa tᵉttecřed di marra tammurt nnec. Ad cek iḥṣar jar marra tewwura nnec di marra tammurt nni d ac iwca SIDI, AREBBI nnec.
\v 53 Xmi d ak-dd ɣa innḍen u di řeḥṣaret i zi cek ɣa iḥṣaren řɛedyan nnec, ad tecced řɣiǧet n uɛeddis nnec d weysum n iḥenjiren nnec d tḥenjirin nnec nni d ac ɣa iwc SIDI, AREBBI nnec. \x ◘ \xo 28:53 \xt Lawi 26:29; 2 Ij. 6:29; Igjd. 4:10\x*
\v 54 Aryaz nni i yareḍben u wenni iḍebɛen aṭṭas ad tiři tamuɣři nnes d taɛeffant ɣar umas u ɣar temɣart n wuř nnes u ɣar min d as iqqimen zeg iḥenjiren nnes,
\v 55 maḥend war ittic uřa i yijj zzaysen ca n weysum n iḥenjiren nnes, inni i ɣa yecc umi war d as iqqim ca \add zi\add* marra \add man aya\add* di řeḥṣaret u di ḍḍiqa i zi xak ɣa ibezzez řeɛdu nnec di marra tiwwura nnec.
\v 56 Tamɣart i yareḍben u tenni iḍebɛen aṭṭas, ɛemmarṣ war teggi třeqqa n uḍar nnes x temmurt di ssibbet n warḍab u n weḍbeɛ nnes, ad tiři tmuɣři nnes d taɛeffant ɣar weryaz n wuř nnes u ɣar mmis d yeǧis,
\v 57 di ssibbet n llufan nni dd-iffɣen jar iḍaren nnes u di ssibbet n iḥenjiren nni turuw, minzi ad ten tecc s tnuffra di ssibbet n řexṣeṣ n marra di řeḥṣaret u di ḍḍiqa i xak ɣa ibezzez řeɛdu nnec di marra tiwwura nnec.”
\b
\m 
\v 58 “Mařa war teḥḍid marra awařen n Ccariɛa-ya nni yuran deg wedlis-a ittwannḍen maḥend ad teggʷeded Isem-a iɛuǧan, issaggʷaden, SIDI, AREBBI nnec,
\v 59 \add xenni\add* ad yarr SIDI jjrayeḥ nnec d jjrayeḥ jar zzariɛet nnec d ijj n arjef ař ṭṭarf. Ad iřint d jjrayeḥ mɣarent, ad dument, uca ad iřin řehřacat iɛeffnen i ɣa iqqimen ɣar zzat.
\v 60 Netta ad ɣarek dd-yarr marra řehřacat n Miṣra i zi tuɣa teggʷded uca ad dayek řeṣqent.
\v 61 Amenni ad ɣarek dd-yarr SIDI marra řehřacat d marra jjrayeḥ nni war yurin deg wedlis ittwanḍen n Ccariɛa-ya, ař ɣa tᵉttwamḥid.
\v 62 Ad teqqimed ak-d ijj n wuru n yeryazen deg wemcan i di ɣa tiřim am yitran n ujenna deg waṭṭas, umi war tesřid i tmijja n SIDI, AREBBI nnec.
\v 63 Am mammec zzaywem ifarḥ SIDI ḥima ad daywem igg tcuni u ad awem ittmarni, ammu zzaywem i ɣa ifarḥ SIDI maḥend ad kenniw ihellek u maḥend ad kenniw iteḥḥa uca kenniw ad tᵉttwaqeřɛem zi temmurt nni ɣar ɣa tadfed ḥima ad tt teksid d řwart. \x ◘ \xo 28:63 \xt Ica. 1:24\x*
\v 64 SIDI ad ac ibezzeɛ x marra řegnus, zeg ujemmaḍ n ddunect ař ujemmaḍ nneɣni n ddunect uca din ad tsexxared i irebbiten nneɣni \add n\add* ukeccuḍ d weẓru nni war tessined cek niɣ řejdud nnec. \x ◘ \xo 28:64 \xt Aɛwd. 4:27; Naḥ. 1:8\x*
\v 65 War tᵉttifed řhudnet jar řegnus-a uca tařeqqa n uḍar nnec war tᵉttif areyyaḥ, \add minzi\add* SIDI ad ac iwc din uř yarejfen d tmuɣři txessi d ijj n řeɛmar isřawen.
\v 66 Tudart nnec ad ac tiři am tuyeř zzat nnec, ad tiřid teggʷeded ǧiřet d wass uca war ittiři weḍman x tudart nnec.
\v 67 Ɣar ṣṣbeḥ ad tinid: ‘A, iři ad tiři d ǧiřet!’ u di ǧiřet ad tinid: ‘A, iři ad yiři d ṣṣbeḥ!’ zi ssibbet n tiggʷudi deg wuř nnec i d ac issiggʷiden u zi ssibbet n min ɣa twařint tiṭṭawin nnec.
\v 68 SIDI ad cek yarr ɣar Miṣra deg iɣurruba x webrid min xef d ac nniɣ: ‘War t tẓarred ɛemmarṣ!’, uca din ad tezzenzem ixef nwem i řɛedyan nnec d isemɣan d tiyya, \add maca\add* war ittiři wi kenniw i ɣa isɣen.”
\b
\m 
\v 69 Ina d awařen n Řɛahd nni yumur SIDI i Musa ḥima ad t igg ak-d ayt n Israil di temmurt n Mu’ab, sennej i Řɛahd i kidsen igga ɣar Ḥurib.
\b
\b
\c 29
\s1 Ttiqqet d ṭṭaɛet
\m 
\v 1 Iřaɣa-dd Musa x marra Israil, inna asen:
\m “Kenniw aqa teẓrim marra min igga SIDI di temmurt n Miṣra zzat i tiṭṭawin nwem di firɛun d marra imsexxaren nnes d marra tammurt nnes, \x ◘ \xo 29:1 \xt Uf. 19:4\x*
\v 2 tiqeǧuba timeqqranin, tinni teẓrim s tiṭṭawin nwem, řeɛřamat d lmuɛjizat nni imɣaren. \x ◘ \xo 29:2 \xt Aɛwd. 4:34; 7:19\x*
\v 3 Ař ass-a SIDI war d awem iwci uř ḥima ad tfehmem uřa d tiṭṭawin ḥima ad tẓarem uřa d imezzuɣen ḥima ad tesřem.
\v 4 Ssnedheɣ kenniw arebɛin n iseggʷusa di řexřa. Arruḍ nwem war idwiř d řbaři u tisiřa nwem war dduysarent x iḍaren nwem.
\v 5 War teccim aɣrum, war teswim binu uřa d ccrab, ḥima ad tessnem belli Necc d SIDI, AREBBI nwem.”
\m 
\v 6 “\add Řami\add* treḥḥgem ɣar wemcan-a, iffeɣ-dd Siḥun, ajeǧid n Ḥacbun, ak-d Ɛuj, ajeǧid n Bacan, ḥima ad kidneɣ imsagar i umenɣi uca neɣřeb i-ten \x ◘ \xo 29:6 \xt Řxř. 21:24,33; Aɛwd. 2:32; 3:1\x*
\v 7 uca neṭṭef tammurt nsen uca newc i-tt d řwart i Irubiniyyen d Ijadiyyen u i wezyen n teqbič n Manassa. \x ◘ \xo 29:7 \xt Řxř. 32:33; Aɛwd. 3:12; Yac. 13:8\x*
\m 
\v 8 Ḥḍam awařen n Řɛahd-a, teggem ten, ḥima ad tawḍem s řeɛqeř ɣar marra min ɣa teggem.
\v 9 Ass-a marra kenniw tbeddem zzat i wudem n SIDI, AREBBI nwem - izeǧifen n tqebbař nwem d imɣaren nwem d imeḥḍayen nwem, marra iryazen n Israil,
\v 10 imeẓyanen nwem, d temɣarin nwem, ibarraniyyen nni izeddɣen di řwest n řmargeḥ n řɛeskar nwem, zeg wenni ittqessen akeccuḍ ař wenni dd-ittaymen aman -
\v 11 ḥima ad yadef \add kuř ijj zzaywem\add* ɣar Řɛahd n SIDI, AREBBI nnec nni i ɣa iqqen SIDI, AREBBI nnec ass-a akidek, u ɣar nneɛřet \add i iǧan d uɣezdis nnes nneɣni\add*,
\v 12 ḥima ad ac yegg ass-a ad tekkared am řgens nnes uca Netta ad ac yiři d AREBBI, am d ac inna u am ijjuǧ i řejdud nnec Ibrahim d Isḥaq d Yaɛqub. \x ◘ \xo 29:12 \xt Amz. 17:7\x*
\v 13 War iǧi akidwem waha i ɣa ggeɣ Řɛahd-a d nneɛřet-a \add i iǧan d uɣezdis nnes nneɣni\add*,
\v 14 ak-d yinni da ɣarneɣ iḥḍaren ass-a zzat i wudem n SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ, \add maca ɛawed\add* ak-d yinni war da ɣarneɣ iǧin ass-a.
\v 15 Minzi kenniw tessnem mammec tuɣa nzeddeɣ di temmurt n Miṣra, u mammec neẓwa di řwesṭ \add n temmura\add* n řegnus nni x dd-tekkem uřa d kenniw,
\v 16 uca teẓrim nnɛawat nsen n l’aṣnam d imeyḍa \add n l’aṣnam nsen\add* nni ɣarsen n weẓru d ukeccuḍ d nnuqart d wureɣ.”
\m 
\v 17 “War ittiři jar awem aryaz niɣ tamɣart niɣ řaǧ niɣ taqbič ad issiggʷej ass-a uř nnes x SIDI, AREBBI nwem, ḥima ad isexxar i irebbiten n řegnus nni u war ittiři jar awem aẓwar nni i ɣa ittarwen arrhaj niɣ cciḥ, \x ◘ \xo 29:17 \xt Řex. 8:23; Ɛbr. 12:15\x*
\v 18 \add uca\add* ad imsar, umi ɣa iseř awařen n nneɛřet-a, aqa netta ad iseggem ixef nnes deg wuř nnes, ad yini: ‘Ad ɣari yiři řehna, waxxa ggureɣ di řeqsaḥet n wuř inu, ař ɣa ihellek min issun ak-d min iffuden.’
\v 19 SIDI war d as isemmeḥ, maca aɣḍab n SIDI d tusmi nnes \add iqeddsen\add* ad dduxxnen deg weryaz nni, u marra nneɛřet nni yurin deg wedlis-a ittwannḍen ad xas tiři uca SIDI ad imḥa isem nnes zi sadu ujenna.
\v 20 SIDI ad t iḥuz x marra tiqebbař n Israil i řɣar, ɛlaḥsab marra nnɛaři n Řɛahd nni yurin deg wedlis-a ittwanḍen n Ccariɛa-ya.
\v 21 \add Xenni\add* jjiř i dd ɣa yasen, iḥenjiren nwem, inni ɣa igeɛɛden awarni awem, uřa d ubarrani nni i dd ɣa yasen zeg ict n temmurt tiggʷej, \add marra\add* nitni ad inin \add ammu\add* xmi ɣa ẓaren jjrayeḥ n temmurt-a d řehřacat i zi issehřec SIDI tammurt:
\v 22 ‘Řecbariyyet d tmeǧaḥt, aqa tecmeḍ marra tammurt, war tᵉttwaẓẓu niɣ tessɣemmi \add ɛad\add* u war issgeɛɛid afsu \add aziza\add*, am mammec \add imsar\add* deg uneqřeb n Sadum d Ɛamurra d Adma d Ṣabuyim nni issneqřeb SIDI deg weɣḍab nnes d wesɛar nnes!’,
\v 23 uca \add ɛawed\add* marra řegnus ad inin: ‘Mayemmi igga SIDI man aya i temmurt-a? Mana řḥaduq n weɣḍab-a imɣaren?’ \x ◘ \xo 29:23 \xt Irm. 22:8\x*
\v 24 \add Xenni\add* ad dd-arren: ‘Minzi nitni jjin Řɛahd n SIDI, AREBBI n řejdud nsen, \add Řɛahd\add* nni iqqen Netta akidsen umi ten dd-issuffeɣ zi temmurt n Miṣra.
\v 25 Uyuren ɛebden i irebbiten nneɣni uca bendqen asen, \add i\add* irebbiten nni war ssinen nitni, war d asen tent-i-dd-iwci Netta.
\v 26 Aɣḍab n SIDI yarɣa x temmurt-a maḥend ad ɣares indeh marra nneɛřet nni yurin deg wedlis-a ittwannḍen.
\v 27 SIDI iqřeɛ i-ten zi temmurt deg weɣḍab d wesɛar d uduqqez \add n weɣḍab\add* imɣar uca inḍar i-ten ɣar temmurt nneɣni, am \add teǧa\add* ass-a.’
\v 28 Timesřayin innufaren aqa tent i SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ, maca \add timesřayin\add* ttwassaregbent aqa tent i neccin u i iḥenjiren nneɣ i řebda, maḥend ad negg marra awařen n Ccariɛa-ya.”
\b
\b
\c 30
\s1 Aqarru n Řɛahd
\m 
\v 1 “Xmi xak dd ɣa yasent marra tmesřayin-a, lbaraka d nneɛřet nni ggiɣ zzatek, uca ad tent tarred ɣar wuř \add nnec\add* jar marra řegnus ɣar mani SIDI, AREBBI nnec, xak yuẓẓeř,
\v 2 uca ad tɛeqbed ɣar SIDI, AREBBI nnec, ad tesřed i tmijja nnes s marra uř nnec u s marra řeɛmar nnec anect n marra min x cek umureɣ ass-a, cek \add jmiɛ\add* ak-d iḥenjiren nnec,
\v 3 \add xenni\add* SIDI, AREBBI nnec, ad ibḍeř aḥebbes nnec uca ad xak yarḥem uca ad cek issmun zi jar marra řegnus ɣar mani cek ibezzeɛ SIDI, AREBBI nnec. \x ◘ \xo 30:3 \xt Naḥ. 1:8; Izhd. 106:45; Irm. 32:37\x*
\v 4 Waxxa inni x yuẓẓřen zzayek, aqa aten ɣar uneggaru n ujenna, aqa SIDI, AREBBI nnec, ad cek issmun uca ad cek dd-indeh ssenni. \x ◘ \xo 30:4 \xt Naḥ. 1:9\x*
\v 5 SIDI, AREBBI nnec, ad cek issidef ɣar temmurt nni warten řejdud nnec uca ad tt teksid \add ɛawed\add* d řwart. Netta ad dayek igg tcuni u ad dayek yarni \add ɛad\add* ktar zi řejdud nnec.
\v 6 SIDI, AREBBI nnec, ad ixten uř nnec d wuř n tarwa nnec ḥima ad texsed SIDI, AREBBI nnec, s marra uř nnec d marra řeɛmar nnec, ḥima ad teddared.\x ◘ \xo 30:6 \xt Aɛwd. 10:16; Irm. 32:39; Ḥiz. 11:19; 36:26\x*
\v 7 SIDI, AREBBI nnec, ad yarr marra nnɛaři nni x řɛedyan nnec u x yinni cek icarrhen, inni xak dd-idarrcen \add ɛawed\add*.
\v 8 Ad tɛeqbed, ad tesřed i tmijja n SIDI uca ad tegged marra řumurat nni xef ac ttumureɣ ass-a.
\v 9 SIDI, AREBBI nnec, ad ac iwc afeyyeḍ di marra řxedmet n ifassen nnec, di řɣiǧet n uɛeddis nnec, di řɣiǧet n řebhayem nnec u di řɣiǧet n temmurt nnec, \add aya ad yiři\add* i řxar nnec, minzi SIDI ad iɛqeb ḥima ad zzayek ifarḥ i řxar nnec, am mammec tuɣa ifarḥ i řejdud nnec, \x ◘ \xo 30:9 \xt Aɛwd. 28:11\x*
\v 10 Xmi ɣa tesřed i tmijja n SIDI, AREBBI nnec ḥima ad teḥḍid řumurat nnes d tweṣṣa nnes, tinni yurin deg wedlis-a ittwanḍen n Ccariɛa uca xmi dd ɣa tdewřed ɣar SIDI, AREBBI nnec, s marra uř nnec, s marra řeɛmar nnec.”
\m 
\v 11 “Minzi řumur-a i x cek ttumureɣ necc ass-a, war iǧi yuɛřa xak u war iggʷij ca.
\v 12 War iǧi deg ujenna, ḥima ad tinid: ‘Wi ɣa igeɛɛden ɣar ujenna di ṭṭweɛ nneɣ ḥima ad aneɣ t-i-dd-yawi i neccin uca ad as nseř, \add ḥima\add* \add nzemmar\add* ad zzayes negg?’ \x ◘ \xo 30:12 \xt Rum. 10:6-8\x*
\v 13 War iǧi x ujemmaḍ n řebḥar, ařami \add ɣa tzemmared\add* ad tinid: ‘Wi ɣa iẓwan ɣar ujemmaḍ n řebḥar ḥima ad aneɣ t-i-dd-yawi i neccin uca ad as nseř, \add ḥima\add* nzemmar ad zzayes negg?’,
\v 14 minzi awař-a yudes i cek aṭṭas, aqa-t deg uqemmum nnec, aqa-t deg wuř nnec, ḥima ad zzayes tegged.”
\m 
\v 15 “Xzar, necc ggiɣ zzatek ass-a tudart d řxar uřa d řmewt d řɣar,
\v 16 minzi necc ttumureɣ cek ass-a ḥima ad texsed SIDI, AREBBI nnec, ad tuyured deg ibriden nnes uca ad teḥḍid řumurat nnes d tweṣṣa nnes d lfarayiḍ nnes maḥend ad teddared u ad tᵉttwammarnid, uca SIDI, AREBBI nnec, ad ac ibarek di temmurt nni ɣar ɣa tadfed ḥima ad tt tᵉṭṭfed d řwart.
\v 17 \add Maca\add* mařa uř nnec ittaggʷej u war tᵉttesřid uca ad tᵉttwassuffɣed \add zeg webrid\add*, ad tbendqed zzat i irebbiten nneɣni uca ad asen tɛebded,
\v 18 \add xenni\add* necc ttbarrḥeɣ awem ass-a belli s tidett ad temmtem. War tarennyed ca ussan nnec x temmurt mani ɣa tadfed awarni řami teẓwid L’Urdun, ḥima ad tt tᵉṭṭfed d řwart.
\v 19 Ass-a necc řaɣiɣ x ujenna d temmurt, maḥend ad iřin d řechud xawem: ggiɣ zzatek tudart d řmewt, lbaraka d nneɛřet! Ixḍar \add xenni\add* tudart, ḥima ad teddared, cek d zzariɛet nnec, \x ◘ \xo 30:19 \xt Aɛwd. 4:26\x*
\v 20 maḥend ad texsed SIDI, AREBBI nnec, uca ad tesřed i tmijja nnes, ad as třeṣqed, minzi Netta d tudart nnec uřa d tuzzegart n wussan nnec, ḥima tzemmared ad tzedɣed x temmurt nni x ijjuǧ SIDI i řejdud nnec ad asen tt-i-dd-iwc, i Ibrahim d Isḥaq d Yaɛqub.”
\b
\b
\c 31
\s1 Yacuwa iksi amcan n Musa
\m 
\v 1 Iruḥ Musa uca issiweř s wawařen-a ak-d marra Israil,
\v 2 inna asen: “Ass-a necc ɣari mya u-ɛicrin n iseggʷusa. War zemmareɣ ɛad ad ffɣeɣ uřa ad adfeɣ uca SIDI inna ayi: ‘War tẓekkʷid \add iɣzar-a n\add* L’Urdun!’ \x ◘ \xo 31:2 \xt Řxř. 27:12; Aɛwd. 3:26\x*
\v 3 SIDI, AREBBI nnec, ad iẓwa zzat i wudem nnec. Netta ad yareddeǧ řegnus-a zzat i wudem nnec uca ad tᵉṭṭfed řwart nsen. Yacuwa ad iẓwa zzat i wudem nnec, am mammec inna SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 31:3 \xt Řxř. 27:18\x*
\v 4 SIDI ad kisen igg am mammec igga ak-d Siḥun d Ɛuj, ijeǧiden n Imuriyyen, inni yareddeǧ Netta s tnayen, u am mammec igga ak-d temmurt nsen. \x ◘ \xo 31:4 \xt Řxř. 21:24,33\x*
\v 5 \add Xmi\add* ten ɣa isellem SIDI zzat i wudem nwem, ad kisen teggem ɛlaḥsab marra tawṣeyyet nni zi kenniw weṣṣiɣ\x ◘ \xo 31:5 \xt Aɛwd. 7:1, 2\x*
\v 6 Iřim d iryazen u iřim tmeḥḍem, war tteggʷedem, war ttarjijem ca zzat i wudem nsen, minzi SIDI, AREBBI nnec, d wenni akidek igguren. Netta war dayek isemmeḥ niɣ cek ittejji.” \x ◘ \xo 31:6 \xt Yac. 1:5; Ɛbr. 13:5\x*
\m 
\v 7 Iřaɣa Musa i Yacuwa, inna as zzat i tiṭṭawin n marra Israil: “Iři d aryaz u iři tmeḥḍed, minzi ad tadfed ak-d řgens-a ɣar temmurt nni ijjuǧ SIDI i řejdud nsen ad asen tt-i-dd-iwc uca cek ad ten tejjed ad tt ṭṭfen d řwart.
\v 8 SIDI, d wenni yuyuren zzat i wudem nnec, d Netta i ɣa yiřin akidek, war cek ittettu ca niɣ ad dayek ismeḥ. War tteggʷed u war ttarjiji.” \x ◘ \xo 31:8 \xt Yac. 1:9\x*
\b
\s1 Musa iwca Ccariɛa i ayt n Lawi
\m 
\v 9 Yura Musa Ccariɛa-ya uca iwca i-tt i ikehhanen, ayt n Lawi, inni yarbun Ttabut n Řɛahd n SIDI, u i marra imɣaren n Israil.
\v 10 Musa yumur i-ten, inna: “Awarni sebɛa n iseggʷusa, di řweqt ittwaggen n useggʷas n ufekki n imerwusen di Řɛid n Iɛuccuten,
\v 11 xmi ɣa imun marra Israil maḥend ad iḥḍar zzat i wudem n SIDI, AREBBI nnec, deg wemcan nni i ɣa yixḍar Netta, ad tɣared s jjehd Ccariɛa-ya zzat i marra Israil deg imezzuɣen nsen. \x ◘ \xo 31:11 \xt Ɛiz. 8\x*
\v 12 Ejj ad imun řgens, iryazen d temɣarin d iḥenjiren d ibarraniyyen nni iǧan ɣar daxeř n tewwura nnec ḥima ad sřen u ḥima ad řemden ad ggʷeden SIDI, AREBBI nwem uca ad ḥḍan marra awařen n Ccariɛa-ya
\v 13 u ḥima iḥenjiren nsen, inni war tt issinen, ad sřen uca ad řemden ad ggʷeden SIDI, AREBBI nwem marra ussan nni i ɣa teddarem x wudem \add n temmurt\add* nni ɣar ɣa teẓwam x L’Urdun maḥend ad tt tᵉṭṭfem d řwart.”
\b
\s1 Abarreḥ x řmuɛṣiyyet i dd ɣa yasen
\m 
\v 14 SIDI inna i Musa: “Aqa iwḍen-dd wussan nnec i di ɣa temmted. Řaɣa i Yacuwa u sbeddem ixef nwem deg Uqiḍun n Umsagar ḥima ad t umureɣ.” Musa d Yacuwa ruḥen, bedden deg Uqiḍun n Umsagar.
\v 15 \add Xenni\add* iban-dd SIDI deg Uqiḍun, deg ijj n uqellij n useynu, uca ibedd uqellij n useynu sennej i wadaf n Uqiḍun.
\v 16 SIDI inna i Musa: “Aqa cek ad tᵉttwassmuned ak-d řejdud nnec uca \add xenni\add* řgens-a ad ikkar ad issefsed ixef nnes am ɣa yuyur awarni i irebbiten n ibarraniyyen n temmurt nni ɣar ɣa yadef \add řgens\add* ař řwesṭ nnes uca \add řgens\add* ad dayi ismeḥ, ad yarẓ Řɛahd inu wenni kidsen ggiɣ.
\v 17 Deg wass nni ad yareɣ weɣḍab inu x \add řgens\add* uca ad ten jjeɣ, ad zzaysen ffareɣ udem inu uca ad ittwaṣarḍ \add řgens\add* uca ad xas dd-asen waṭṭas n iceřwawen d řeḥṣarat, ař ɣa yini \add řgens\add* deg wass nni: ‘Ma war xafi dd-usin iceřwawen-a, minzi AREBBI war kidi iǧi?’ \f ◼ \fr 31:17 \fk war kidi iǧi\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘war iǧi di řwest inu’.\f*
\v 18 Deg wass nni ad ffareɣ udem inu marra di ssibbet n řɣar nni igga umi idweř ɣar irebbiten nneɣni.
\v 19 Řexxu xenni, ari tizřit-a i yixef nwem uca seřmed i-tt i ayt n Israil, egg i-tt deg uqemmum nsen, ḥima tizřit-a ad tiři d acehhad di ṭṭweɛ inu ḍidd i Israil,
\v 20 minzi Necc ad ssidfeɣ řgens-a ɣar temmurt nni x jjuǧeɣ i řejdud nsen \add ad asen tt wceɣ\add*, \add ict n temmurt\add* ifeyyḍen s uɣi d tamment, uca ad ccen, ad jjiwnen, ad dewřen qbubbzen. \add Xenni\add* ad dewřen ɣar irebbiten nneɣni, ad xasen sexxaren uca ad ayi ssduqzen, ad arẓen Řɛahd inu.
\v 21 Uca ad imsar umi d as dd-usin \add i řgens-a\add* aṭṭas n iceřwawen d řeḥṣarat, aqa \add xenni\add* izři-ya ad dd-tarr deg wudem nnes am yijj n ucehhad, minzi war tᵉttiři tᵉttwattu zeg uqemmum n tarwa nnes, minzi Necc ssneɣ axarreṣ nni iḥeṭṭa \add ɛad\add* ass-a \add di daxeř nnes\add*, qbeř ma ad t ssidfeɣ di temmurt nni x jjuǧeɣ \add ad asen tt wceɣ\add*.” \f ◼ \fr 31:21 \fk tarwa\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘zaad’.\f*
\m 
\v 22 Deg wass nni yura Musa tizřit-a uca isseřmed i-tt i ayt n Israil.
\v 23 Uca Netta yumur i Yacuwa, mmis n Nun, inna: “Iři d aryaz, iři tmeḥḍed, minzi ad tessidfed ayt n Israil di temmurt nni x d asen jjuǧeɣ \add maḥend ad asen tt wceɣ\add* uca Necc ad akidek iřiɣ.” \x ◘ \xo 31:23 \xt Yac. 1:6\x*
\m 
\v 24 Uca imsar umi ikemmeř Musa tira n wawařen n Ccariɛa-ya deg ijj n wedlis ittwannḍen, ař aneggar nsen,
\v 25 aqa Musa yumur Ilawiyyen nni yarbun Ttabut n Řɛahd n SIDI, inna:
\v 26 “Ksim adlis-a ittwanḍen n Ccariɛa uca teggem t zzat i Ttabut n Řɛahd n SIDI, AREBBI nwem, maḥend ad din yiři d acehhad ḍidd nwem, \x ◘ \xo 31:26 \xt 2 Ij. 22:8\x*
\v 27 minzi necc ssneɣ aɣewweɣ nwem d tɣennant nwem. Xzar, umi necc ddareɣ ɛad akidwem ass-a, kenniw aqa tɣewwɣem x SIDI, mecḥař ɛad ktar i ɣa teggem awarni i řmewt inu!
\v 28 Smunem-dd ɣari marra imɣaren n tqebbař nwem d imeḥḍayen nwem, \add xenni\add* ad ssiwřeɣ awařen-a deg imezzuɣen nsen uca ad ggeɣ ajenna d temmurt d řechud ḍidd nsen.
\v 29 minzi necc ssneɣ aqa awarni řmewt inu ad tfesdem ař ṭṭarf uca ad teffɣem x webrid nni x kenniw umureɣ. Deg uneggar n wussan, ad teggem řɣar di tiṭṭawin n SIDI ař ɣa t tesɛarem s řxedmet i teggim s ifassen nwem.”
\m 
\v 30 \add Xenni\add* issiweř Musa deg imezzuɣen n marra agraw \add n řgens\add* n Israil s wawařen n tizřit-a ařami ten ikemmeř.
\b
\b
\c 32
\s1 Izři n Musa
\m 
\v 1 “Sřem, \add a\add* ijenwan, ad ssiwřeɣ!
\m Ejj tammurt ad tseř
\m i wawařen n uqemmum inu!
\m 
\v 2 Ejj taɣuri inu ad tudem am wenẓar,
\m ad hwant tiwařin inu am nnda,
\m am ict n thiḍurt x uɣemmuy aziza
\m u am tnecnacin x wefsu,
\m 
\v 3 minzi necc ad barrḥeɣ Isem n SIDI,
\m arrem-dd řemɣaret i AREBBI nneɣ!
\m 
\v 4 \add Netta\add* d Taṣḍart, řxedmet nnes nican,
\m minzi marra ibriden nnes ttwaseggden,
\m ijj n Arebbi d amtiqqi břa řɣecc,
\m aqa-t d amsegged, nican i yeǧa.
\m 
\v 5 \add Řgens\add* aqa issefsed ixef nnes,
\m nitni war ǧin ca d iḥenjiren nnes,
\m \add maca\add* d řefḍiḥet,
\m \add aqa-t\add* d ijj n jjiř ifarɣ, ixnunnes.
\m 
\v 6 Ma texsem ad teggem aya i SIDI,
\m \add a\add* řgens abuhaři d wefɣur!
\m Ma war iǧi Netta d Babac nni cek isɣin,
\m d wenni cek iggin
\m u d wenni cek ikewwnen?
\m 
\v 7 Idarem ussan iɛdun,
\m xemmem iseggʷusa n jjiř ař jjiř,
\m seqsa babac u netta ad ac t iɛawed
\m \add seqsa\add* imɣaren u nitni ad ac t inin.
\m 
\v 8 Umi iwca Umɛuǧi x kuřci
\m tasɣart \add nsen\add* i marra řegnus,
\m umi ibḍa tarwa n bnadem,
\m issgeɛɛed iymiren n řegnus
\m ɛlaḥsab řqedd n ayt n Israil.
\m 
\v 9 Minzi tasɣart n SIDI d řgens nnes,
\m Yaɛqub d afiřu \add n řeɛbar\add* n tesɣart nnes.
\m 
\v 10 Yufa i-t di temmurt n řexřa,
\m di tnezruft ixřan \add ak-d řewḥuc\add*
\m ittzun, issɣuyyun.
\m Inneḍ as-dd, isseřmed i-t,
\m iḥḍa i-t am mummu n tiṭṭ nnes.
\m 
\v 11 Am ugider nni issfaqen řɛucc nnes,
\m iṭṭaw sennej i warrud nnes zi ssa ɣar da,
\m ittbezzeɛ afriwen nnes,
\m iksi i-t uca yarebbu t x wafriwen nnes,
\m 
\v 12 \add ammu\add* i indeh i-t SIDI waha
\m uca war tuɣi din akides
\m ca n arebbi d aɣrib.
\m 
\v 13 Issenya i-t x tɛuřař n temmurt
\m uca icca řɣiǧet n yeyyar.
\m Ijja i-t ad iẓemm tamment zi jjarf,
\m d zzect zeg weẓru n teṣḍart, \x ◘ \xo 32:13 \xt Aɛwd. 33:26, Ica. 58:14\x*
\m 
\v 14 d trussi n tfunasin d uɣi n wuǧi
\m s tadunt n izmaren d icarriyyen,
\m \add inni iǧan am\add* tarwa n Bacan,
\m \add u s tadunt n\add* iɣayḍen,
\m s mummu n waren n irden.
\m \add Ɛawed\add* cek teswid zeg idammen n uḍiř,
\m ak-d ukuffu nnes xas.
\b
\m 
\v 15 Idweř Yacurun iqbubbez
\m uca iẓẓeɛbeḍ
\m - ‘Aqa tmesřed u teqbubbzed,
\m wah, s tadunt tᵉttwadřed!’ -
\m uca ismeḥ di Arebbi
\m nni i-t dd-ixeřqen
\m uca isseḥqar Taṣḍart n usenjem nnes.
\m 
\v 16 S irebbiten iɣriben
\m ssekkaren nitni tusmi nnes,
\m s jjɛayef sɛaren t.
\m 
\v 17 Nitni qeddmen tiɣarṣa i ccwaṭen,
\m war iǧi i Arebbi,
\m i irebbiten nni war ssinen,
\m \add irebbiten\add* n jdid,
\m inni dd-yusin ɛad mammec,
\m war zzaysen ttarjijen řejdud nwem.
\m 
\v 18 Taṣḍart nni i cek dd-yejjin,
\m tsemḥed dayes
\m u tᵉttud Arebbi
\m nni i cek dd-yurwen s řewjeɛ.
\b
\m 
\v 19 Iẓra SIDI \add man aya\add* uca issehqar i-ten,
\m zi ssibbet n usduqqez
\m n iḥenjiren nnes d yessis.
\m 
\v 20 Netta inna:
\m ‘Ad zzaysen ffareɣ udem inu,
\m ad ẓareɣ mammec ɣa yiři
\m \add zzman\add* uneggaru nsen,
\m minzi nitni d ijj n jjiř ittneqřab,
\m d tarwa i di war iǧi řmanet.
\m 
\v 21 Nitni ssekkaren tusmi inu
\m s min war iǧin d Arebbi,
\m sɛaren ayi s \add l’aṣnam\add* nsen ibeṭṭřen.
\m Necc ad ssekkareɣ tusmi nsen
\m s \add min\add* war iǧin d řgens,
\m s yijj n řgens d abuhaři ad ten sɛareɣ. \x ◘ \xo 32:21 \xt Rum. 10:19\x*
\m 
\v 22 Minzi s weɣḍab inu tekkar tmessi,
\m ad tecmeḍ ař řaxart \add din\add* swadday,
\m uca ad tecc tammurt d řɣiǧet nnes,
\m u ad tessecmeḍ tisi n idurar. \x ◘ \xo 32:22 \xt Irm. 15:14\x*
\m 
\v 23 Necc ad asen arniɣ iceřwawen,
\m ad xasen neyyceɣ fřitcat inu.
\m 
\v 24 Ad ttwaheyyfen s řaẓ
\m uca ad ttwaṣarḍen s ṭṭaɛun
\m u s wareddeǧ amerzag
\m u Necc ad daysen ssekkeɣ
\m tiɣmas n řmař
\m s ssem ineqqen n \add ifiɣran\add*
\m inni ittmuǧuɣen di tɛejjajt.
\m 
\v 25 Zi barra ad ikkes ssif \add tarrawt\add*,
\m u zeg wexxam n daxeř
\m \add ad teřqef\add* tiggʷudi:
\m am ubřiɣ am teɛzarect,
\m aseymi ak-d umeccaybu.
\b
\m 
\v 26 Tuɣa xseɣ ad iniɣ:
\m ‘Am usemmiḍ ad ten faretkeɣ,
\m ad ssbeddeɣ řidaret nsen jar iwdan!’,
\m 
\v 27 mři war ǧiɣ tteggʷideɣ
\m zeg wesɛar n řeɛdu,
\m ḥima iɣrimen nsen war t nekkaren
\m uca ad inin:
\m ‘Ifassen nneɣ,
\m inni ittwassgeɛɛden ammu \add s jjehd\add*,
\m ggin aya marra, \add war iǧi\add* d SIDI.’
\m 
\v 28 Minzi nitni d ijj n řgens břa array
\m u war daysen řefhamet.
\m 
\v 29 Mři ggin tiɣit,
\m \add xenni\add* iggur ad fehmen aya
\m u ad wcen taynit i uneggar nsen.
\m 
\v 30 Mammec izemmar ad iḍfar
\m ijj \add n bnadem\add* ařef \add n iwdan\add*
\m u \add mammec zemmaren\add* tnayen
\m ad arren ɛecra-ařaf ad arewřen,
\m mařa war d asen temmenz teṣḍart nsen
\m uca \add war d asen\add* isellem SIDI i nitni?
\m 
\v 31 Minzi taṣḍart nsen
\m war teǧi am Taṣḍart nneɣ.
\m Ejj ad ḥekmen řɛedyan nneɣ \add s ixef nsen\add*.
\b
\m 
\v 32 Minzi tazayart nsen
\m \add teǧa\add* zi tzayart n Sadum
\m u zeg iyyaren n Ɛamurra.
\m Aḍiř nsen d aḍiř n ssem,
\m ɣarsen izekkunen \add ccuren s\add* tarzugi. \f ◼ \fr 32:32 \fk tazayart\ft - niɣ ‘ḍiřect’.\f*
\m 
\v 33 Binu nsen
\m \add amecnaw asuḍi n\add* tmessi n řhaycat,
\m \add amecnaw\add* ssem ineqqen n třefsiwin.
\m 
\v 34 Ma \add marra\add* aya war ɣari ittwaxzen,
\m ittwacemmeɛ deg ixxamen n txubay inu?
\m 
\v 35 D Necc i yeǧan x nneqmet d řexřaṣ,
\m xmi ɣa iḥřuǧeḍ uḍar nsen.
\m Ass n uḍeyyeɛ nsen aqa yudes,
\m uca min xasen i ɣa yiři, ad imsar deɣya. \x ◘ \xo 32:35 \xt Rum. 12:19; Ɛbr. 10:30; 1 Bṭ. 2:23\x*
\b
\m 
\v 36 Minzi SIDI ad igg s řḥeqq
\m di ṭṭweɛ n řgens nnes,
\m Netta ad iḥenn x imsexxaren nnes
\m xmi ɣa iẓar belli jjehd immeksi,
\m uca war din iqqim \add ɛad\add*
\m wenni ittwaṭṭfen d wenni ijjin. \f ◼ \fr 32:36 \fk jjehd\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘afus’ wenni d řeɛřamet n jjehd d tzemmar n bnadem.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 32:36 \xt Izhd. 135:14; Izhd. 90:13\x*
\m 
\v 37 \add Xenni\add* ad yini:
\m ‘Mani ǧan irebbiten nsen,
\m \add mani\add* taṣḍart i ɣares ufin adurri?
\m 
\v 38 \add Mani ǧan irebbiten\add* nni zi
\m ccin tadunt n tɣarṣa nsen,
\m inni zi sessen binu
\m n tewhibin n useyyeb nsen?
\m Ejj i-ten ad kkaren, ad cek ɛawnen
\m u ejj i-t ad xawem issduri.’
\b
\m 
\v 39 Xzarem řexxu,
\m aqa d \bd Necc, \bdit wah\bdit* d Necc\bd*,
\m u war \add din\add* ca uřa d ijj n arebbi akidi.
\m Necc neqqeɣ u Necc sseddareɣ,
\m Necc řebbzeɣ u ssgenfiɣ
\m u war din wi ɣa ifekken zeg ufus inu. \x ◘ \xo 32:39 \xt Aɛwd. 4:35; 1 Ṣm. 2:6; Ica. 45:5, 18, 22\x*
\m 
\v 40 Minzi Necc ad sswiẓẓḍeɣ afus inu
\m ɣar ujenna,
\m ad iniɣ: ‘Necc aqa ddareɣ i řebda!’
\m 
\v 41 Mařa ssqeḍɛeɣ ssif inu ittwessgen
\m uca afus inu ad iṭṭef di řḥukm,
\m \add xenni\add* Necc ad ntaqmeɣ zi iɣrimen inu
\m u zeg inni d ayi icarrhen.
\m 
\v 42 Ad ssᵉscareɣ fřitcat \add n řqews inu\add*
\m s idammen,
\m uca ssif inu ad isarḍ aysum,
\m idammen n wenni ittwanɣen
\m u n wenni ittwaḥebbsen
\m azeǧif n řeɛdu
\m ak-d \add ijeṭṭayen n\add* ucuwwaf nnes. \x ◘ \xo 32:42 \xt Izhd. 68:22 \x*
\m 
\v 43 Sřiwřewem, \add a\add* řegnus!, \add ak-d\add* řgens nnes,
\m minzi Netta ad intaqem
\m i idammen n imsexxaren nnes,
\m ad yarra nneqmet x iɣrimen nnes,
\m uca ad igg weṣřaḥ
\m i temmurt nnes d řgens nnes.” \f ◼ \fr 32:43 \fk igg weṣraḥ\ft - xzar Izhd. 78:35: ifdi, amefdi.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 32:43 \xt Rum. 15:10\x*
\b
\m 
\v 44 Yusa-dd Musa uca issiweř marra awařen n tizřit-a x imezzuɣen n řgens, netta \add jmiɛ ak-d\add* Huciɛa, mmis n Nun. \f ◼ \fr 32:44 \fk Huciɛa\ft - ijj n yisem nneɣni i Yacuwa.\f*
\v 45 \add Umi\add* ikemmeř Musa marra awařen-a i zi issiweř ɣar marra Israil,
\v 46 inna asen: “Arrem marra awařen-a nni x d awem nniɣ ass-a ɣar wuř nwem, ḥima ad ten tumurem i iḥenjiren nwem maḥend ad ḥḍan marra awařen n Ccariɛa-ya ad zzaysen ggen,
\v 47 minzi war iǧi d awař n baṭeř i kenniw, maca d tudart nwem. S wawař-a ad tezzuggartem ussan nwem x temmurt i ɣar ɣa teẓwim x L’Urdun, maḥend ad tt tᵉṭṭfem d řwart.”
\b
\m 
\v 48 Issiweř SIDI ak-d Musa deg wass nni, inna:
\m 
\v 49 “Geɛɛed adrar n Abarim, \add aqa-t\add* d adrar n Nabu nni \add iǧan\add* di temmurt n Mu’ab arendad n Ariḥa, uca xzar tammurt n Kenɛan nni i ɣa wceɣ d řwart i ayt n Israil, \x ◘ \xo 32:49 \xt Řxř. 27:12\x*
\v 50 uca mmet x wedrar nni ɣar ɣa tgeɛɛded. Ad tdewřed ad tᵉmmarnid ɣar řgens nnec, am mammec immut umac Harun x wedrar n Hur uca immarni ɣar řgens nnes, \x ◘ \xo 32:50 \xt Řxř. 27:13; 33:38\x*
\v 51 minzi kenniw teɣdařem zzayi di řwesṭ n ayt n Israil ɣar waman n Mariba-Qadac di řexřa n Ṣin, minzi kenniw war d ayi tessqeddsem di řwesṭ n ayt n Israil. \x ◘ \xo 32:51 \xt Řxř. 20:12\x*
\v 52 \add Xenni řexxu\add* ad ṭẓared tammurt zzatek, maca war ttidfed ca ɣar temmurt nni i ɣa wceɣ i ayt n Israil.”
\b
\b
\c 33
\s1 Lbaraka n Musa
\m 
\v 1 D ta d lbaraka nni zi ibarek, Musa, aryaz n SIDI, ayt n Israil qbeř řmewt nnes.
\v 2 Inna:
\m “SIDI yusa-dd zeg \add wedrar n\add* Sina, igeɛɛed-dd ittwesseg arendad nsen zi Saɛir, tuɣa ittissiq umi dd-iban zeg wedrar n Faran uca iffeɣ-dd zi \add jar\add* ɛecra-ařaf n imqeddasen. Zeg ufus nnes afusi issberbic s wassamen arendad nsen. \x ◘ \xo 33:2 \xt Ḥab. 2:3, 4 \x*
\v 3 Wah, Netta ittexs řegnus! Marra imqeddasen \add iǧan\add* deg ufus nnec, aqa aten ɣar iḍaren nnec, \add wah,\add* ad ikkar \add kuř ijjen zzaysen\add* zeg wawařen nnec.
\v 4 Musa yumur aneɣ x Ccariɛa, aqa-tt d řwart n tmesmunt n Yaɛqub.
\v 5 Tuɣa Netta d Ajeǧid di Yacurun umi nyarwen izeǧifen n řgens, jmiɛ ak-d tqebbař n Israil.”
\b
\m 
\v 6 “Iři ad iddar \bd Rubin\bd*, war itmetti, uca iři war ttiřin iryazen nnes udrusen!”
\m 
\v 7 D man aya i inna x \bd Yahuda\bd*: “\add A\add* SIDI, seř ɣar tmijja n Yahuda uca yarr i-t ɣar řgens nnes. S ifassen nnes immneɣ di ṭṭweɛ nnes uca iři Cek ad as iwc afus ḍidd n iɣrimen nnes!” \f ◼ \fr 33:7 \fk di ṭṭweɛ nnes\ft - ixs ad yini ‘di ṭṭweɛ n Israil’.\f*
\m 
\v 8 U x \bd Lawi\bd* inna: “Tummim nnec d Urim nnec \add ad iřin\add* i weryaz nni d ameddukkeř nnec d amtiqqi, wenni tqeǧbed di Massa, ak-d wi tqacḥed ɣar waman n Mariba, \x ◘ \xo 33:8 \xt Uf. 17:7\x*
\v 9 wenni innan x babas d yemmas: ‘War ten ttwiřiɣ!’, d wenni war issɛizz x yaytmas niɣ war ixs ad issen iḥenjiren nnes, minzi nitni ṭṭfen di min tennid Cek uca ḥḍan Řɛahd nnec.
\v 10 Nitni ad ssřemden lfarayiḍ nnec i Yaɛqub u Ccariɛa nnec i Israil. Ad ssuyusen řebxur zzat i wenzaren nnec uřa d taɣarṣt \add n wecmaḍ\add* ikemmřen x uɛalṭar nnec.
\v 11 Barek tizemmar nnes di min igga, \add a\add* SIDI, uca ṭṭef arḍa s řxedmet n ifassen nnes, ɣḍeř timeṣṣaḍin n yinni akides ittemɛařan d n yinni t icarrhen ḥima ɛemmarṣ war ttbeddin ɛad!”
\m 
\v 12 U x \bd Binyamin\bd* inna: “Amɛizz n SIDI, netta ad ɣares izdeɣ di řaman, ass marra ad t ideř uca ad izdeɣ jar tiɣarḍin nnes!” \f ◼ \fr 33:12 \fk ad izdeɣ jar tiɣarḍin nnes ... \ft - min ixs ad yini ‘Binyamin ad izdeɣ s ttiqqet x Arebbi uca Arebbi ad iderr Binyamin u Binyamin ad izdeɣ jar tɣarḍwin n SIDI’.\f*
\m 
\v 13 U x \bd Yusuf\bd* inna: “Ad ibarek SIDI tammurt nnes s min iǧan iɣřan qaɛ zeg ujenna, s nnda, u s \add waman\add* ihewřen, inni \add din\add* iǧan swadday, \x ◘ \xo 33:13 \xt Amz. 49:25\x*
\v 14 u s řɣiǧet iɣřan n tfuct u s min iǧan iɣřan i ittic uyur,
\v 15 u s řqimet n idurar tiqdimin u s min iɣřan n tewririn n řebda,
\v 16 u s min iɣřan aṭṭas n temmurt d uɛemmar nnes, u s tcuni n wenni tuɣa izeddɣen di cbarq ak-d isennanen. Iři ad dd-yas x uzeǧif n Yusuf u x tuccent n ucuwwaf n wenni yarebbun ttaj \add n weɛzař\add* jar aytmas. \x ◘ \xo 33:16 \xt Amz. 49:26; Uf. 3:3-6. \x*
\v 17 Amenzu n ufunas nnes d ucewwar nnes u accawen nnes am waccawen \add iziraren\add* n iɣayḍ n řexřa, ad zzaysen iwwet řegnus marra jmiɛ ař tineggura n ddunect. Ina d ɛecra n řuřuf n Ifrayim u ina d řuřuf n Manassa!” \x ◘ \xo 33:17 \xt Lawi 22:27; Řxř. 18:17;\x*
\m 
\v 18 U x \bd Zabulun\bd* inna: “Farḥ, a Zabulun, s wuffuɣ nnec, u cek, \add a\add* \bd Issakar\bd*!, \add farḥ\add* s iqiḍan nnec.
\v 19 Ad řaɣan i řegnus ɣar wedrar. Din i ɣa ɣarṣen tiɣarṣa n tsegda, minzi ad ẓemmen afeyyeḍ n řebḥur d txubay innufaren deg ijdi.”
\m 
\v 20 U x \bd Jad\bd* inna: “Ad ittwabarek Wenni iggin ttasiɛ i Jad! Netta izeddeɣ \add din\add* am teyradt uca icarreg aɣiř, \add wah,\add* uřa d aceqquf n uzeǧif.
\v 21 Iksi tammurt icnan i yixef nnes, minzi aqa din tᵉttwaḥḍa tesɣart n umgewwad \add s weḍman\add*. Yusa-dd ak-d izeǧifen n řgens, ikemmeř tasegda n SIDI d řeḥkamat nnes, \add jmiɛ\add* ak-d Israil.”
\m 
\v 22 U x \bd Dan\bd* inna: “Dan d ijj n mmis n wayrad nni i ineggzen ɣar zzat zi Bacan.”
\m 
\v 23 U x \bd Naftali\bd* inna: “\add A\add* Naftali, iři tejjiwned s tcuni u teccured s lbaraka n SIDI. Ksi lɣarb d ljanub d řwart.”
\m 
\v 24 U x \bd Acir\bd* inna: “Aqa ittwabarek Acir ak-d iḥenjiren nnes. Iři ad yaf arḍa zeg aytmas uca ad issur aḍar nnes di zzect.
\v 25 Zzekrunat nnec \add aqa aten\add* zeg wuzzař d nnḥas, ad yiři jjehd nnec am wussan nnec!”
\b
\m 
\v 26 “War \add din\add* iǧi am Arebbi, \add a\add* Yacurun, wenni innayen x ujenna ḥima ad ac iwc afus, \add wenni innayen\add* x iseynuten s lɛaḍama nnes. \x ◘ \xo 33:26 \xt Aɛwd. 32:13, Ica. 58:14\x*
\v 27 AREBBI n řebda d tazeddiɣt \add i udurri\add*, u swadday \add ttɛawanen\add* iɣaǧen nnes n řebda. Netta ad yaẓẓeř x řeɛdu zzat i wudem nnec, ad yini: ‘Aredeǧ!’
\v 28 Israil ad izdeɣ weḥḥḍes di řaman. Ad yiři wanu n Yaɛqub deg ict n temmurt \add iccuren\add* n irden d binu n jdid, \add wah,\add* ijenwan nnes ad udmen s nnda. \x ◘ \xo 33:28 \xt Irm. 23:6; 33:16; Izhd. 68:27\x*
\v 29 Sseɛd nnec, \add a\add* Israil! Wi iǧan am cek? Ijj n řgens ittwassnejmen zi SIDI. Aqa Netta d aseřqi i uɛawen uřa d ijj n ssif n lɛaḍama nnec. Řɛedyan nnec ad ssniɛmiřen ad sswaḍɛen i cek uca cek ad tɛefsed x idemrawen nsen!”
\b
\b
\c 34
\s1 Řmewt n Musa
\m 
\v 1 \add Xenni\add* igeɛɛed Musa zi řewḍat n Mu’ab ɣar wedrar n Nabu, ɣar tqiccet n Fisja nni iwejjhen Ariḥa uca isscen as SIDI marra tammurt, zi Jilɛad ař Dan, \x ◘ \xo 34:1 \xt Aɛwd. 3:27\x*
\v 2 marra Naftali d temmurt n Ifrayim d Manassa d marra tammurt n Yahuda ař řebḥar d min din awarni as,
\v 3 d \add Temmurt n\add* Ljanub d udewwar n řewḍa n Ariḥa, Tandint n Tcejjura n Tini ař Ṣuɣar.
\v 4 Uca inna as SIDI: “Ta d tammurt nni x jjuǧeɣ i Ibrahim, d Isḥaq d Yaɛqub, nniɣ: ‘I zzariɛet nnec, ad tt wceɣ!” Jjiɣ cek ad tt tẓared s tiṭṭawin nnec, \add maca\add* war tẓekkʷid ca diha.” \x ◘ \xo 34:4 \xt Amz. 12:7; 13:15; 15:18; 26:4; 28:13\x*
\m 
\v 5 \add Ammu\add* i dinni immut Musa, amsexxar n SIDI, di temmurt n Mu’ab, am mammec \add awař i dd-iffɣen\add* zeg uqemmum n SIDI.
\v 6 Uca Netta inḍeř i-t di teɣzurt di temmurt n Mu’ab qibač i Bayt-Faɣur uca uřa d ijj issen amcan n wenḍeř nnes ař ass-a.
\v 7 Tuɣa Musa ɣares mya u-ɛicrin n iseggʷusa umi immut. Tiṭṭ nnes war teɣri ca, war d as iruḥ řemɛezz.
\v 8 Sɣuyyen ayt n Israil x Musa di řewḍat n Mu’ab třatin n wussan uca \add ammu i\add* ttwakemmřen ussan n iɣuyyan d wecḍan n Musa.
\b
\m 
\v 9 Yacuwa, mmis n Nun, tuɣa iccur s buḥbeř n tiɣit, minzi Musa tuɣa issars xas ifassen nnes u ayt n Israil sřin ɣares uca ggin am mammec \add t\add* yumur SIDI i Musa. \x ◘ \xo 34:9 \xt Řxř. 27:18\x*
\v 10 Ɛemmarṣ ɛad war dd-ikkar anabi di Israil am Musa, wenni tuɣa issnen SIDI udem ɣar wudem,
\v 11 s marra řeɛřamat nni zi t issekk SIDI, ḥima ad tent igg di temmurt n Miṣra, zzat i firɛun d marra imsexxaren nnes d marra tammurt nnes,
\v 12 u s marra afus nni ijehden u s marra \add timegga\add* imɣaren issaggʷaden, tinni igga Musa zzat i tiṭṭawin n marra Israil. 
